* Preorder costume bonus may be released as paid DLC in the future.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9zs6.jpg', '2025-04-21', '{4}', 'IGDB', 100, 327461, 1, 85.99, '[{"id":209898,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":209899,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":209895,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":209896,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":209897,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":209900,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":209901,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174816.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166386.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445691.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445692.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445693.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445684.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445685.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445686.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445687.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445688.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445689.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1445690.jpg"]', '{89550,103269,109277,101608,76852,113895,114145,350279,325598,7036}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lHjjlpCoBOQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=53qyNPNrksE}', 'SNK', '3', null, '{791}'), (813, 'Guilty Gear: Strive - Nintendo Switch Edition', 'The critically acclaimed Guilty Gear Strive arrives on Nintendo Switch for the first time, complete with the first three season passes of DLC to make for a total of 28 playable characters!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co963y.jpg', '2025-01-23', '{4,33}', 'IGDB', 100, 315335, 1, 79.99, '[{"id":193899,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":197279,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/149738.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429203.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429204.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429202.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1429206.jpg"]', '{89550,103369,87728,10605,43367,96452,103269,109277,101608,76852}', '{}', 'Arc System Works', '3', null, '{827}'), (814, 'Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader - Void Shadows', '“Void Shadows” is the first DLC for Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader, offering a massive amount of content with about 15 hours of gameplay and a new romanceable companion.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co88ms.jpg', '2024-09-24', '{12,15,16,24,31,32}', 'IGDB', 100, 302168, 1, 64.99, '[{"id":202614,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":202619,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":202615,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":202616,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":202617,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":202618,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137340.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1321292.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1321293.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1321294.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1321295.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1321296.jpg"]', '{25311,26845,28182,13196,113402,105269,109339,35994,102057,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_pwCNWrK0co,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iNMLdJZSrH8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obmD2wU9lAs}', 'Owlcat Games', '1', null, null), (815, 'Vampire Survivors: Emergency Meeting', 'The Survivors are desperate to hunt vampires, but are running out of places to look. Only one option remains: Be the bullet hell... in space!

Gather your most trusted Crewmates, prepare to eject the Impostors, and try to survive while mowing down thousands of extra-terrestrial foes in this expansion for Vampire Survivors. Turn classic Among Us tasks into outrageous weapons, upgrading your abilities after every roguelite run to overcome impossible odds with ease. Be alert to subterfuge as you explore the vast weirdness of the Polus Replica and keep your wits about you, as suspicious eyes are always watching.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7gzu.jpg', '2023-12-18', '{25,32}', 'IGDB', 100, 279377, 1, 63.99, '[{"id":161764,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":179608,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":179611,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":179612,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":179609,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":179610,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/128027.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204980.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204981.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204982.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204983.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204987.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204984.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204985.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204986.jpg"]', '{113895,111130,54775,106987,37419,28309,96217,25646,80916,32902}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4e1EkVaC0H8}', 'Poncle', '1', null, null), (816, 'Resonite', 'Enter a novel digital universe with infinite possibilities. Whether you resonate with people around the world in a casual conversation, playing games and socializing or you riff off each other when creating anything from art to programming complex games, you''ll find your place here.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co75ut.jpg', '2023-10-06', '{32}', 'IGDB', 100, 269473, 1, 68.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166084.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157169.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157170.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157171.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157172.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157173.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157174.jpg"]', '{10776,55689,37419,29173,51577,9243,34823,117717,55888,38967}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppYPAX31Zbk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I1kaE_wPuSM}', 'Yellow Dog Man Studios', '0', null, null), (817, 'Bloodthief', 'Bloodthief is an ultra-fast melee dungeon-runner where you use momentum to parkour through hazardous dungeons and brutally slash through enemies. Speed-run through medieval dungeons and castles and learn what dark secrets lie beneath the surface.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9eo5.jpg', '2025-09-22', '{32}', 'IGDB', 100, 260402, 1, 82.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/114231.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1110424.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1110429.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1110432.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1110435.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1110438.jpg"]', '{113895,111130,106987,37419,28309,96217,25646,80916,36553,105269}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=90GPXUZWscM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MHQLPjFT6JE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sll06gaCYhY}', 'Blargis', '0', null, null), (818, 'Dawnfolk', 'Minimalist and relaxing survival builder perfect for short gaming sessions. Rebuild and manage your realm, collect resources and decide the fate of your people. Explore the darkness and unveil the secrets of the black monoliths to bring back light to the world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co94jk.jpg', '2025-02-13', '{9,12,15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 100, 245754, 1, 91.99, '[{"id":221338,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":220599,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/105977.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/138692.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1032094.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1032096.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1032097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1032098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1032100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1332646.jpg"]', '{26574,79134,113402,109339,25311,35994,24426,19404,28182,26145}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaclbiv7d6Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xCB-JrcixkM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJS3GzVEB8E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uP8dRlZ3Hfc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BlDl5QQq2sA}', 'Darenn Keller', '0', null, null), (819, 'Viticulture: Essential Edition - Tuscany Expansion', 'The Tuscany Expansion includes 3 new features: An extended game board, special workers and structures. Choose which features you want to play with or simply play with all of them!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8sf9.jpg', '2023-02-20', '{15,32}', 'IGDB', 100, 236970, 1, 66.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989818.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989816.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989814.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989822.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989821.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/989820.jpg"]', '{65827,111043,36269,19404,31515,33603,115539,33646,51577,17519}', '{}', 'DIGIDICED', '2', null, null), (820, 'Planet Zoo: Aquatic Pack', 'Expand your zoo into a marine menagerie with Planet Zoo''s Aquatic Pack! Adopt five magnificent new animals including King Penguins and Giant Otters, construct beautiful scenery from 170+ new pieces, and master the aquatic-themed challenge zoo set in Oregon, USA.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6b17.jpg', '2020-12-08', '{13,15}', 'IGDB', 100, 226995, 1, 57.99, '[{"id":182594,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":182596,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":182597,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":182599,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":182595,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":182598,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143357.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935404.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935405.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935406.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935407.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935408.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935409.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935410.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935411.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935412.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935414.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935418.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935416.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935420.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/935422.jpg"]', '{17613,112754,36346,65827,76340,24620,36269,31515,33603,33646}', '{}', 'Frontier Developments', '13', null, null), (821, 'Portal: Companion Collection', 'Break the laws of spatial physics in the hilariously mind-bending adventures of Portal and Portal 2! Including Portal and Portal 2, the Companion Collection comes with all the groundbreaking gameplay, dark humor, and exploration that earned the series hundreds of awards.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4hap.jpg', '2022-06-28', '{8,9,31}', 'IGDB', 100, 191406, 1, 66.99, '[{"id":100843,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":77319,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":118416,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":189680,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/79197.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738290.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738291.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738292.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738293.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738294.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738295.jpg"]', '{28070,20342,55173,24426,55190,56033,89597,25646,55038,105269}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wMQASUA_1Do}', 'Valve', '3', null, null), (822, 'Blake: The Visual Novel', 'Graphic Novel meets Visual Novel in this sci-fi/thriller interactive story. As incriminating events start to revolve around him, experience the dark, mind-bending journey of Blake and his pivotal transformation into a vigilante.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3mcj.jpg', '2021-08-31', '{32}', 'IGDB', 100, 163826, 1, 72.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46150.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/583733.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/583734.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/583735.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/583736.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/583737.jpg"]', '{115539,38967,55984,113895,51528,11668,79994,111130,22690,51485}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?