Craft a unique deck, encounter bizarre creatures, and discover relics of immense power in Slay the Spire 2 - featuring new characters, cards, events, alternate acts, and more!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co82c5.jpg', '2026-03-05', '{15,32,35}', 'IGDB', 97.3941055214523, 296831, 1, 91.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/135078.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257427.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299503.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299507.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299498.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299500.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299501.jpg"]', '{116992,19404,40477,117605,65827,9472,88223,31515,36269,106987}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=krDFltgjLtE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J2NJ9vvvSds,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6NgLqPWqDss,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PW22jwFNxU8}', 'Mega Crit Games', '0', null, '{9750}'), (898, 'Voices of the Void', 'You work as a scientist in the isolated research lab in the mountains of Switzerland. Your task is to gather signals from space, analyze them, process them and sell them to get points.

You can get regular signals and objects like dwarf planets and stars, or you can get something "unusual" or even "strange" and "unexplainable".', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8uks.jpg', null, '{13,32}', 'IGDB', 97.3311276537083, 224415, 2, 79.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/161254.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1436888.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1436889.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1436890.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1436891.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1436892.jpg"]', '{17548,26574,37419,111187,34823,17479,28070,113360,114455,18020}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izeY7Wtk6z0}', 'EternityDev', '0', null, null), (899, 'Lurkers', 'Lurkers is a chaotic 2D multiplayer sandbox where you can build, battle, and survive! Fight zombies, conquer game modes like Bedwars, and unleash your creativity in a world that’s yours to shape and destroy.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9hgu.jpg', '2019-04-19', '{5,8,12,13,25,31,32}', 'IGDB', 97.3039739449146, 117526, 1, 47.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/158492.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474145.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474146.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474147.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474149.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1474150.jpg"]', '{17379,26574,44076,10776,17548,102584,19561,13210,24765,113360}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DO1JCgHwNDo}', 'Bergice Productions', '0', null, null), (900, 'Jurassic Park', 'Jurassic Park is a top-down action-adventure game based on the blockbuster film. Players take on the role of Dr. Alan Grant, exploring the island, rescuing stranded workers, and battling escaped dinosaurs. The game features maze-like levels, limited ammo, and key-based progression, combining exploration and survival in a challenging prehistoric setting.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2zpb.jpg', '1993-12-31', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 97.2264316024013, 25880, 1, 16.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170268.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170269.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/442768.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547351.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547348.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547349.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547350.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547353.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547352.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547354.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1547355.jpg"]', '{106805,87622,105269,55038,19164,107318,103301,76877,75242,111130}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ze5TNG488XE}', 'Ocean Software', '0', null, '{3239}'), (901, 'Bloodborne: Game of the Year Edition', 'With new story details, learn the tale of hunters who once made Yharnam their hunting grounds, meet new NPCs, and discover another side of the history and world of Bloodborne. Includes:
The Original Bloodborne Experience / Bloodborne: The Old Hunters Expansion / Bloodborne: The Old Hunters', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4vui.jpg', '2015-11-27', '{12}', 'IGDB', 97.1252879082519, 42931, 1, 12.99, '[{"id":24579,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":86196,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/108766.jpg"]', '{54775,106987,96217,113636,116530,81249,55038,19164,103168,55199}', '{}', 'Sony Computer Entertainment', '3', null, null), (902, 'Mafioso', 'Mafia Mobster Gangs have taken the control of all the cities in the world. It''s time for you and granny to make your own Mafia family. Hire the best mobsters and show who is the boss!

Mafiozo is a multiplayer turn-based strategy game, narrating a course of events when Mafia groups seized control of different city districts.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9ya3.jpg', '2019-04-28', '{16,35}', 'IGDB', 97.0967741935484, 348499, 1, 36.99, '[{"id":213291,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172604.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172867.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172868.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265159.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1555279.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1555280.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1555281.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1555282.jpg"]', '{32510,60693,64902,80213,28182,14394,58958,27209,56135,94772}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L6bgBBjzwRs}', 'Paeezan', '0', null, null), (903, 'Catan Universe', 'After a long, hardship filled journey you have reached the coast of an unknown island! However, other explorers have also landed on Catan: The race for colonisation has begun! Build roads and towns, trade skilfully and become ruler over Catan!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co22ve.jpg', '2017-04-25', '{15,26,35}', 'IGDB', 97.0539075684938, 28278, 1, 40.99, '[{"id":83128,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":83129,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/32556.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/42273.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/42276.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/42277.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/42275.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/42274.jpg"]', '{17130,33153,28113,11544,8746,51279,19083,19082,32510,10774}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9LQdidVUa1U}', 'United Soft Media Verlag GmbH', '0', null, '{4869}'), (904, 'Life Force', 'Life Force is an action-packed shooter where there are six levels which alternate between side and vertical scrolling, each of them ending with a powerful guardian. Throughout the game, destroying certain enemies will release power ups which can be used to equip your ship with more powerful weapons, extra speed, and shields. Gameplay is for one player or two players simultaneously.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4qvn.jpg', '1988-08-26', '{5,33}', 'IGDB', 96.9895850800797, 174945, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":79978,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":90567,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":82699,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":64834,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/73629.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115028.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/657910.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/657909.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/657911.jpg"]', '{43367,55038,105269,68286,107318,103301,111846,113362,12539,68287}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gzc_tdiHcB4}', 'Playtronic', '11', null, '{3548}'), (905, 'Dig Island', 'Dig Island is a 4-player co-op digging game. As you dig deeper, discover new resources, upgrade your equipment, and work with your friends to repair the plane and escape the island.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobet5.jpg', '2026-01-30', '{13,31,32}', 'IGDB', 96.9230769230769, 372930, 1, 91.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/242959.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/242960.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753326.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753327.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753328.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753329.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753330.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753331.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753332.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753333.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753334.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753335.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753336.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753337.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753338.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753339.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753340.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753341.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753324.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1753325.jpg"]', '{106279,79134,3225,29348,25311,9243,35994,109339,17130,38967}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=99sK6chFcco}', 'FiftyEight Studios', '0', null, null), (906, 'Battlefield 3: Premium Edition', 'Take your Battlefield 3 multiplayer experience to the next level with Battlefield 3: Premium Edition! Containing a staggering amount of content, Battlefield 3 Premium offers all expansion packs with early access, new soldier and weapon camos, and a number of exclusive in-game items all for a one-time fee. Battlefield 3: Premium Edition includes expansion packs Back to Karkand, Close Quarters, Armored Kill, End Game, and Expansion Pack #5.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaoaj.jpg', '2012-09-11', '{5}', 'IGDB', 96.6547553121753, 41888, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":117059,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":117057,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":117352,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":117055,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":117056,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":117058,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/179785.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/207579.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/207580.jpg"]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,17446,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9VZUcLgtDM4}', 'EA Digital Illusions CE', '3', null, '{34}'), (907, 'Animal Company', 'Enter the chaotic and fun world of Animal Company, where survival meets pure chaos in this multiplayer VR adventure. Whether you’re exploring eerie environments, customizing your character in the Lab, or braving the terrors that await you and your friends, the excitement never stops. With weekly updates, there’s always something fresh to experience.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coauu2.jpg', '2024-07-01', '{31}', 'IGDB', 96.6346114498506, 318395, 1, 57.99, '[{"id":211857,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/204511.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1661321.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1661322.jpg"]', '{111130,26658,25646,11668,19164,68271,13210,102584,120201,26574}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDLFB-yXY7U,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h8rMRow2eQo}', 'Wooster Games', '0', null, null), (908, 'Captain Tsubasa Vol. II: Super Striker', 'Captain Tsubasa Volume II: Super Striker is a continuation of the "Cinematic Soccer" series of soccer games. It''s the direct sequel to Captain Tsubasa and is fairly similar to its predecessor but with some slight graphical improvements. The game features an original new story and original characters, starting after the three-year time skip.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob3uv.jpg', '1990-07-20', '{11,12,14,15,24}', 'IGDB', 96.6113482514813, 102254, 1, 24.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400065.jpg"]', '{13196,119598,10243,19404,58075,26845,55029,103232,99043,113402}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GJ1WFM-p0AM}', 'Tecmo', '0', null, '{792}'), (909, 'Creatures', 'The inhabitants of the pretty but insignificant planet Blot decided to leave to find a trendier planet, and escape being called the Blotians, a most unhip name. Until they such a planet, they call themselves the Fuzzy Wuzzies.

Their colony ship collides with an asteroid, and crash lands in the Pacific Ocean, near an unchartered island, which they colonise, calling it "The Hippest Place in The Known Universe". Unfortunately the island is also home to rather nasty demons, who can''t stand the commotion caused by the happy Fuzzies, or their silly name for the island.

The demons kidnap the Fuzzy Wuzzies by hosting a massive party, then capturing them in a net, and dragging them off to the torture chambers. The only Fuzzy not caught is Clyde Radcliff, who was already being sick in the bushes. He wakes up in the morning with a really bad headache, and fiery halitosis, and sets out to destroy the demons, and rescue his friends.

The game consists of 3 levels, each made up of 3 of stages. The first two stages of each level are side scrolling platformers, where Clyde must destroy the enemies by firing at them, presumably using his halitosis. At the end of each of these stages, Clyde meets a witch, who can provide him with extra firing patterns, or upgrade those he has, in exchange for ''magic potion creatures'' found during the stages.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9dch.jpg', '1990-12-31', '{5,8}', 'IGDB', 96.5036829625861, 11374, 1, 27.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/17592.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/17591.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,119177,32902,106805,43367,28751,103302,520,105269}', '{}', 'apex computer productions', '0', null, '{1529}'), (910, 'Fate/Hollow Ataraxia', 'Fate/Hollow Ataraxia is a Japanese visual novel game and the sequel to Fate/Stay Night. The word ataraxia in the title is a Greek term for tranquility, giving the title the combined meaning of "empty (or false) tranquility". The plot of Fate/Hollow Ataraxia is based half a year after the events of Fate/Stay Night. Like its preceding counterpart, the story is set in Fuyuki City. Bazett Fraga McRemitz, a member of the Mages'' Association and a master in the Fifth Holy Grail War, wakes on the fourth day of the Fifth Holy Grail War with a new servant, Avenger, and no memory of what happened to her beforehand. She and the Avenger set off to fight and win the Holy Grail War.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob4ah.jpg', '2014-11-27', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 96.4694019817222, 12329, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":105194,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/232432.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/232433.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228716.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228717.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228718.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228719.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228720.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228721.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228722.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228723.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228724.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228727.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1228728.jpg"]', '{106987,96217,81249,115653,26870,55038,19164,103168,55199,22792}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hzsbjo8gg8o,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0JXQdrjS-Ac}', 'TYPE-MOON', '10', null, '{1635}'), (911, 'Mahjong Soul', 'Mahjong Soul lets you experience exciting Mahjong matches versus players from around the world. The game gives you the chance to be accompanied by cute anime girls of your dreams. Looking for a relaxing yet competitive game? Join us on Mahjong Soul!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8wec.jpg', '2018-06-08', '{15,35}', 'IGDB', 96.4285568953022, 117263, 1, 31.99, '[{"id":86535,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":86536,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/54014.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/299301.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/299302.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/299300.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/299303.jpg"]', '{32510,64902,19083,80213,187355,388356,86199,77498,61985,109474}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jxcDtQe_-BE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FYnj03T0lRs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LPl6q63Tdos}', 'Yostar Games', '0', null, null), (912, 'Beast Battle Simulator', 'Beast Battle Simulator is a physics based battle-simulation sandbox game featuring dinosaurs and animals. Kamikaze Zebras VS. T-Rex with laser guns, Lions with machine guns VS. a flock of 50 seagulls; anything is possible! Watch as the beasts dismember and rip each other apart in gory detail!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1mui.jpg', '2017-08-23', '{12,13,14,15,32}', 'IGDB', 96.4117226590422, 55077, 1, 41.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119600.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119602.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119603.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119599.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119601.jpg"]', '{25311,35994,26574,36553,109339,65827,19404,28182,26145,31515}', '{}', 'DOG HOGGLER', '0', null, null), (913, 'Geotastic', 'Geotastic is a free crowd-funded multiplayer geography quiz game. In the classic "random drop" game mode, the players are dropped at a random Google Street View location. The players have to find out where they are and pin-point the most exact location on a map.
It is a free alternative to Geoguessr.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co49cq.jpg', '2020-10-19', '{26}', 'IGDB', 96.3990001562256, 142722, 1, 67.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544836.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1544845.jpg"]', '{112889,37419,144249,81249,115653,342252,341893,268109,246246,246245}', '{}', 'Eduard But', '0', null, null), (914, 'Ghosts of Tabor', 'Ghosts of Tabor is a VR only FPS PVP and PVE survival game where you will use your wits, skills and resources to survive. Inspired by games such as Escape from Tarkov and DayZ, featuring different scenarios from scavenging to looting and crafting. Will you survive long enough to make it out alive?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6tq4.jpg', '2024-02-08', '{5,24}', 'IGDB', 96.3480741797432, 204034, 1, 60.99, '[{"id":215237,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78089.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096338.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096339.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096340.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096341.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096342.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096343.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096344.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096345.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096346.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1096347.jpg"]', '{95340,119177,38030,106805,87622,32902,19549,43367,28751,105269}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tNyvRvua34Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lolq5yaIbWo}', 'Combat Waffle Studios', '0', null, null), (915, 'Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V Tag Force Special', 'Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V Tag Force Special is the seventh installment of the Tag Force video game series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4kot.jpg', '2015-01-22', '{15,35}', 'IGDB', 96.3324341645125, 42791, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":227692,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/236462.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1735472.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1735473.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1735471.jpg"]', '{19404,32510,56967,119156,113201,13196,7615,119188,111187,77498}', '{}', 'Konami', '0', null, '{5166}'), (916, 'The Witness', 'The Witness was the seventh game released by interactive fiction pioneers Infocom.
The player character is a detective who has been summoned to the Cabeza Plana, California office of Mr. Linder, a millionaire. Linder fears that his life is in danger... and indeed, as he sits in his office with the player, he is murdered before the player''s eyes. The player then must solve the murder.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9ibg.jpg', '1983-12-31', '{31}', 'IGDB', 96.2857142857143, 7425, 1, 29.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642544.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642542.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642543.jpg"]', '{55984,103266,12625,80916,27725,26223,107614,24695,81275,27092}', '{}', 'Infocom', '0', null, null), (917, 'Not in the Groove', 'A rhythm game based on StepMania, In The Groove, and other games alike, that provides modding capabilities to charts, and features compatibility with most StepMania and In The Groove charts previously available, uses mods to allow for a different twist on charts, breaking the boundaries for what a playable chart can be.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2gik.jpg', '2011-03-01', '{7}', 'IGDB', 96.2422622852174, 138851, 1, 26.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1811755.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1811756.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1811757.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1811758.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1811759.jpg"]', '{63933,77720,82995,18981,78969,80106,32688,86847,118456,63793}', '{}', null, '12', null, null), (918, 'FiveM', 'FiveM is a modification for Grand Theft Auto V enabling you to play multiplayer on customized dedicated servers, powered by Cfx.re.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8xf0.jpg', '2015-05-05', '{5,10,12}', 'IGDB', 96.1538461538461, 146553, 1, 18.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{105269,55038,19164,107318,76877,109292,68393,47823,59427,23651}', '{}', 'Cfx.re', '5', null, null), (919, 'Super Metroid', 'The Space Pirates, merciless agents of the evil Mother Brain, have stolen the last Metroid from a research station, and once again Mother Brain threatens the safety of the galaxy! Samus Aran must don her awesome array of high-tech weaponry to retrieve the deadly Metroid hidden deep within the cave-riddled planet Zebes. Super Metroid features excellent graphics, with a huge variety of enemies and worlds to explore. The side-view action will be familiar to many players, only now there are new weapons and items, including the Grappling Beam, which allows Samus to swing across large chasms, and the X-Ray Scope, which reveals secret passages.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5osy.jpg', '1994-03-19', '{5,8,31}', 'IGDB', 96.1320699806957, 1103, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":47404,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":28526,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":48829,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":190675,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":192332,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":192333,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":192334,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219366.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265946.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265947.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265948.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265949.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265950.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265951.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265952.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265943.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265944.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/265945.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174860.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174861.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3592.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3594.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174859.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174862.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174855.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174858.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174857.jpg"]', '{3222,1070,1741,1026,1025,18182,1105,55038,26226,19564}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ls5uo4xidwQ}', 'Nintendo R&D1', '0', null, '{243}'), (920, 'Poker Night at the Inventory', 'Almost seven years after the Inventory closed its doors, this underground social club has reopened for business. Play No Limit Texas Hold’em with four video game icons in a high-stakes battle of cards, bets, and trash talk.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobfti.jpg', '2026-03-05', '{16,35}', 'IGDB', 96, 388390, 1, 81.99, '[{"id":230338,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":231725,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":231726,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":231727,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":231728,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/243530.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/243652.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754585.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754576.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754577.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754578.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754579.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754580.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754581.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1754582.jpg","h