ast-paced gunplay, razor-sharp melee combat, and spectacular free-running movement.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co67u3.jpg', '2023-02-16', '{5,12,31,33}', 'IGDB', 96, 237681, 1, 79.99, '[{"id":125202,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":122271,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":122272,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":122273,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":122275,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":122274,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":125203,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102332.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219251.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219249.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219250.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219252.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219253.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219254.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1219255.jpg"]', '{19164,55038,106987,96217,47823,81249,105269,103168,55199,101608}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TyPpXUrq9Hs}', 'Flying Wild Hog', '0', null, '{868}'), (923, 'Headquarters World War II', 'Headquarters World War II is a fast-paced turn-based strategy game where your battlefield tactics are as important as your army management skills. Experience both sides of the war, battling in Europe as the USA, the UK, or Germany. Storm bunkers, occupy houses, win tank duels.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co62nu.jpg', '2024-04-11', '{15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 96, 186895, 1, 68.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/62545.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/708877.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/708878.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/708879.jpg","ht