s://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co570x.jpg', '2020-09-15', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 96, 138784, 1, 58.99, '[{"id":86041,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{106805,19164,119177,38030,87622,81249,103303,105269,55038,118218}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fYZD1oSycRU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cn-OWofb_O4}', 'Ubisoft Paris', '1', null, '{287}'), (926, 'Arma 3: Contact', 'What if humanity suddenly encounters extraterrestrial intelligence on Earth? Bohemia Interactive presents: Arma 3 Contact – a spin-off expansion about the most important discovery in the history of mankind. As a soldier deployed to Livonia’s militarized Nadbór region, you will be among the first to study our alien visitors and determine their intentions. However, amid the tension and chaos, armed conflict inevitably unfolds. Arma 3 Contact’s military science fiction campaign arrives together with a massive new terrain, and introduces new factions, weapons, vehicles, outfits, equipment, and more to the wider Arma 3 sandbox.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1nby.jpg', '2019-07-25', '{13,15}', 'IGDB', 96, 121163, 1, 39.99, '[{"id":25195,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/322850.jpg"]', '{36553,25311,35994,17613,36346,65827,26574,112754,24620,31515}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xeyf4Xf0eYU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ds7RoCrhUyk}', 'Bohemia Interactive', '2', null, null), (927, 'Mallow Drops', 'Mallow Drops is a gravity puzzle where two kiwis regather their eggs in a shattered world. Help Marsh and Mallow rescue their eggs and get to the exit! Turn everything upside down as you slide, shift and move through the tricky world of Mallow Drops, a mix of platformer and a sliding block puzzle. Getting to where you need to go half the fun - just be sure to have a safe landing!

With Wooly Jumpers hopping about and Dirty Underbears surprising you suddenly, it won''t be easy, and if you''re not careful, the dreaded Dropbears may get the drop on you!

CHANGE YOUR WORLD BY CHANGING YOUR PERSPECTIVE
You move in straight lines. Your world turns upside-down.

When you turn the world of Mallow Drops, things shift in unexpected ways and new paths are revealed.

Mallow Drops is a meditative mix of platformer and a sliding block puzzle coming to Steam in 2016', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/it58smbpvhqhbbubqsj5.jpg', '2016-11-03', '{9,32}', 'IGDB', 96, 25910, 1, 50.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/82795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/82797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/82796.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/82799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/82798.jpg"]', '{27266,89132,26223,25646,25222,115539,81275,77529,22360,106992}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p6tNeByYmzY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0uTdvNjjwbg}', 'Gritfish', '0', null, null), (928, 'Mario Kart 8: DLC Pack Two', 'This DLC Pack adds Villager, Isabelle, and Dry Bowser as well as the Bell and Crossing cups and the Streetle, P-Wing, City Tripper, Bone Rattler, and Crossing Kite vehicle parts.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa5xe.jpg', '2015-04-23', '{10}', 'IGDB', 96, 22146, 1, 28.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/31061.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,6214,4537,80382,55192,104983,27553,63232,27378}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zwiodIbH3yc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IsD2lVsUn5U,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yfVTC2uTHYA}', 'Nintendo EAD Software Development Group No.1', '1', null, null), (929, 'Assassin''s Creed III: Deluxe Edition', 'The year is 1775. The American colonies are about to revolt. You are Connor, an assassin who has sworn to secure liberty for his people and his nation. To do so, you will hunt your enemies across a staggeringly large, open, and realistic world. You will unleash your lethal skills in a violent quest that will take you from chaotic city streets to blood-soaked battlefields in the hostile American wilderness and beyond. You will meet legendary heroes of American history, and together you will conspire to annihilate those who threaten Liberty itself.

Whether you use your predatory instincts to kill silently, or your fearsome arsenal to kill openly, one thing is clear: the world that the Assassins live in has become far more deadly. And so have you.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8jbp.jpg', '2012-09-30', '{25,31}', 'IGDB', 96, 21695, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":10714,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":10715,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29438.jpg"]', '{81249,79134,103303,115653,103168,19164,103054,34155,115283,26574}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gZrklEy9ohQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-pUhraVG7Ow}', 'Ubisoft Montreal', '0', null, null), (930, 'Stargate SG-1: Unleashed - Episode 1', 'The first instalment of an episodic mobile game series based on the Stargate franchise, released on iOS and Android devices. The game featured an all-new storyline featuring the original cast and characters of the Stargate SG-1 television series, written by Stargate novelist Sally Malcolm.

The series was originally intended to comprise three episodes, but the third game was never released. The game was eventually delisted from app stores.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8i9t.jpg', '2013-03-14', '{31}', 'IGDB', 96, 1984, 1, 19.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2271.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2272.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2273.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2274.jpg"]', '{68286,28751,55038,105269,25311,108797,107318,103301,115283,28070}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CKtFnmkZApA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pxHChoOelyY}', 'MGM', '0', null, '{10305}'), (931, 'The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past', 'Venture back to Hyrule and an age of magic and heroes. The predecessors of Link and Zelda face monsters on the march when a menacing magician takes over the kingdom. Only you can prevent his evil plot from shattering the land of Hyrule.

In your quest, you''ll venture into twisting mazes, dungeons, palaces and shadowy forests. Test your mettle with mighty swords and magical weapons. Or heft a boulder and hurl it at your enemies. If the going gets tough, dive into a river - you can swim to escape! Learn powerful spells, locate magical artifacts and solve the mysteries of the evil magician and the hidden realm of Hyrule.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3vzn.jpg', '1991-11-21', '{9,31}', 'IGDB', 95.995285997404, 1026, 1, 18.99, '[{"id":226941,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":90794,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":189812,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":82546,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":210590,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":49238,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84536.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84545.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84541.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84538.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84542.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84543.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84537.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84544.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172475.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172474.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172473.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84540.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84539.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52607.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176243.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176244.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176245.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176246.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176248.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176247.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176249.jpg"]', '{1035,1029,1036,1032,3349,1041,533,1034,1028,1025}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OLSQ8K1jSWw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7yjfTQ009ms,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wg1MXUZC2_E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CGXys7rkq5A}', 'St. GIGA', '0', null, '{106,9849}'), (932, 'Super Mario All-Stars + Super Mario World', 'Put quite simply, this is the amalgamation of the previously released Super Mario All-Stars compilation with Super Mario World added. While games already in the All-Stars bundle have major graphical and audio improvements, the only change made to Super Mario World is a slight tweak of Luigi''s graphic sprites, making him slightly thinner and taller (rather than being the same height and stature of Mario) which does not affect gameplay.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co98uf.jpg', '1994-12-01', '{8}', 'IGDB', 95.970481201072, 77378, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":50772,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":50773,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103613.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103606.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103608.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103607.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103609.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103612.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103610.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103611.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56867.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384860.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/407794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/407795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/407796.jpg"]', '{20342,24426,55173,55190,28070,56033,115276,89597,37001,19150}', '{}', 'Nintendo Entertainment Analysis & Development', '3', null, null), (933, 'Star Control II', 'Star Control II, the sequel to the original Star Control, is a space adventure game that features role-playing elements alongside a 2D space ship melee combat system. The player assumes the role of The Captain of a single starship wandering a detailed environment of solar systems, gradually gathering information and resources in order to defeat a mysterious and implacable enemy.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2d9l.jpg', '1992-11-17', '{13,15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95.9671764333817, 1046, 1, 14.99, '[{"id":124095,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35160.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132841.jpg"]', '{25311,35994,26574,13200,79134,36553,21564,34823,105269,109339}', '{}', 'Toys for Bob', '0', null, '{234}'), (934, 'Victoria: Revolutions', 'Victoria: Revolutions is the expansion pack for Victoria: An Empire Under the Sun. It features 15 extra years of gameplay, an expanded tech tree to cover the interwar period, a doomsday converter, a revamped election and politics system, a new ideology (fascism), an overhauled military system and a new economic system that brings more realism through various economic models.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4h8f.jpg', '2006-08-17', '{15}', 'IGDB', 95.9542730021932, 11035, 1, 21.99, '[{"id":7660,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":7659,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102519.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102518.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102517.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102516.jpg"]', '{18623,23345,55590,55029,3700,79134,102163,36553,19376,6985}', '{}', 'Strategy First', '2', null, '{1482}'), (935, 'Suikoden II', 'Experience An Epic Tale of Warfare, Magic, Friendship And Betrayal

-New tactical map battles add a whole level of strategy
-Fantastic spells with stunning animation sequences and specialized attacks
-Over 108 different characters can join your party and help you on your quest
-Unlock hidden storylines using your memory card data from the original Suikoden
-Build up your castle during the game to a thriving virtual community', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1y6a.jpg', '1998-12-17', '{12,15,16}', 'IGDB', 95.8595242219963, 1454, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":63628,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":230981,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1482.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1481.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1480.jpg"]', '{14394,10388,13196,7615,26845,26940,115653,2365,30229,19404}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RRXzw5XcSy8}', 'Konami', '0', null, '{304}'), (936, 'Super Mario World', 'A 2D platformer and first entry on the SNES in the Super Mario franchise, Super Mario World follows Mario as he attempts to defeat Bowser''s underlings and rescue Princess Peach from his clutches. The game features a save system, a less linear world map, an expanded movement arsenal and numerous new items for Mario, alongside new approaches to level design and art direction.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8lo8.jpg', '1990-11-21', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 95.8523009070526, 1070, 1, 9.99, '[{"id":33716,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":47151,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":47393,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":190203,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":50775,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67905.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67903.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67908.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67906.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67900.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67898.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67904.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67902.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67899.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170150.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170153.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170152.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67907.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170154.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67901.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391463.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391464.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391465.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391462.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391466.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/391467.jpg"]', '{1022,358,19150,1741,1074,55190,1103,56033,36198,24426}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vxg5eOPmzHI}', 'Nintendo Entertainment Analysis & Development', '0', null, '{6118,6128,240}'), (937, 'Mass Effect: Genesis', 'Mass Effect: Genesis is a downloadable "interactive backstory comic". Genesis fills the role of Mass Effect for new players by introducing them to the story of the original game and allowing them to make six of the major plot decisions that players could make. If downloaded, the comic appears between the opening level and character customization. There are two versions of the comic, one each for a male and female Commander Shepard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa9vn.jpg', '2011-01-18', '{34}', 'IGDB', 95.7359865249199, 202311, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":90241,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1046002.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1046003.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1046004.jpg"]', '{290187,275804,267604,256361,229003,209728,198365,176773,159335,141753}', '{}', 'Dark Horse Comics', '1', null, '{25}'), (938, 'My Racing Career', 'Start your engines and make your career as a world-class racing driver in one of the most established motorsport management games.

Launched in 2012, My Racing Career has grown into a deep, competitive racing sim with a passionate community. From open-wheel racing to stock cars, motorbikes to rally — your path is yours to create. Begin in Formula 4 and work your way up to the big leagues like Formula 1, IndyCar, or Formula E. Or take a different route through touring cars, GT, prototypes, MotoGP, superbikes, or rally series.

You control your future. Develop your driver and race strategy in a world where your decisions matter.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9o2e.jpg', '2012-09-17', '{10,13,15}', 'IGDB', 95.6902356902357, 253735, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":208433,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":231182,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160317.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502564.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502565.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502566.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502567.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502568.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502569.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502570.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1502571.jpg"]', '{29173,36346,31515,35463,55590,17519,117717,55888,55689,40470}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lVQoJCjCXWs}', 'F&L Creative', '0', null, null), (939, 'Polity', 'Polity is a casual cross-platform MMORPG set in a dynamic, player-driven world. Players have the opportunity to govern colonies, join other colonies, explore the world, uncover the lore or master diverse skills such as farming, forestry, fishing etc. With a wide variety of features such as quests, achievements, puzzles, mini-games, and crafting, along with extensive customization options, Polity encourages players to forge their own path and create their own unique journey within its expansive virtual realm.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8fui.jpg', '2024-06-27', '{2,9,12,13,32}', 'IGDB', 95.6880227688091, 149228, 1, 67.99, '[{"id":179188,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/33344.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350037.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350030.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350031.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350033.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350034.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350035.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350036.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350032.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1350038.jpg"]', '{26574,9243,44242,10776,109339,17379,10032,26145,17111,17548}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DoOnP4dW1dU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZPMk2fof528,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1o0OTsjV3o,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=whkqWpBKfsY}', 'Jib Games', '0', null, null), (940, 'Kirka.io', 'Kirka.io is a first-person multiplayer shooter in the voxel world. Here you can play with your friends in different modes, maps, create clans, beat the leaderboard, and participate in CHAMPIONS LEAGUE.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3c5d.jpg', null, '{5}', 'IGDB', 95.6560471726127, 152476, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1442674.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,43367,28751,103302,520}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5vV-1_c7lc}', null, '0', null, null), (941, 'Heroes of Might and Magic III: Horn of the Abyss', 'Heroes of Might and Magic III: Horn of the Abyss also known as HotA is a fan-made full scale add-on for Heroes of Might and Magic III, designed to continue the classical Heroes 3 add-on series of RoE/AB/SoD.
The aim of the project is to create an add-on for Heroes of Might and Magic III: The Shadow of Death with lots of new features. The main focus of add-on is the quality of every single aspect of the modded game. This includes the careful fixes of the original game balance, removal of the graphical imperfections left by the developer, and of course, a huge amount of new content, like new campaigns, new map objects and even a new playable faction - The Cove. The project pretends to be fully lore-wise and keeps connection with the original Might and Magic universe.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co99tg.jpg', '2011-12-31', '{12,15,16,24,32}', 'IGDB', 95.6545716805959, 14173, 1, 5.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184026.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564160.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564162.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564164.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564165.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564166.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564167.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564168.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564169.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564170.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564161.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1564163.jpg"]', '{13196,19404,9472,26268,7615,26845,93694,28182,106987,96217}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EzMVhuAvxfc}', 'HotA Crew', '5', null, '{194}'), (942, 'NHL 96', 'NHL 96 was the first EA Sports game to feature Virtual Stadium technology, which resulted in a 3D feel and multiple camera angles. The NHL license ensures that real teams and players of the era are included, with a full league and playoff system. Many game options can be toggled - the infamous fighting is option, as are the penalties and offsides. The control system makes it possible to execute one-touch passes, and several special trick moves to quickly advance the ball. As a bonus feature, it included ''Hockey Card'' profiles of every player on CD, and interviews with the stars of the game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2gox.jpg', '1995-10-01', '{14}', 'IGDB', 95.6405932171009, 11650, 1, 18.99, '[{"id":7278,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{114286,109606,114287,116353,103500,102122,96209,206295,875,824}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=35kKl4GmU6E}', 'EA Sports', '0', null, '{3001}'), (943, 'Melty Blood Act Cadenza Ver. B', 'Melty Blood Act Cadenza Ver. B is an arcade port of Melty Blood Act Cadenza with various changes and upgrades, the most notable of which is the inclusion of White Len as a playable character, with a significantly weakened moveset. It also introduced a fifth button that served as a contextual action depending on the situation and the direction held on the joystick when pressed, such as dodging or throwing. This version can be identified by a dual silhouette of Len and White Len in the logo and the phrase "Through the Looking-Glass, Northern Light transparently".', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2wp1.jpg', '2006-12-26', '{4}', 'IGDB', 95.6208460866082, 39601, 1, 19.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/428895.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/428896.jpg"]', '{89550,390785,389426,373371,370597,364814,350197,350196,350194,348232}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QBwyOoV_M2g}', 'French Bread', '10', null, '{6874}'), (944, 'Population: One', 'Fly anywhere, climb anything, build defenses... All in a VR Battle Royale.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2hxt.jpg', '2020-10-22', '{5,33}', 'IGDB', 95.5675675675676, 139377, 1, 71.99, '[{"id":60411,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/90025.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/417610.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/417611.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/417612.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/417613.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/417614.jpg"]', '{43367,117939,95340,119493,119177,38030,106805,87622,32902,87728}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2QZCaoIUywY}', 'BigBox VR', '0', null, null), (945, 'Action Fighter', 'Take to the streets or take to the skies. Because Action Fighter is the incredible, transformable combat vehicle.

You start out on a customized cycle. Built with enough speed and power to jump over water and overtake enemies. Then, by finding the right parts along the way, you''ll change your cycle into a supercharged, state-of-the-art sports car. Next, add two turbojets to make your car airborne. And take to the skies. Down hyped-up helicopters and jet spaceships from above.

And no matter which vehicle you''re manning- or who you''re after- get ready to stand by for action!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coacwf.jpg', '1986-08-17', '{5,10,33}', 'IGDB', 95.5282193660064, 11885, 1, 9.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150777.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150778.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/16999.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15563.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13541.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/19113.jpg"]', '{3772,55038,105269,107318,103301,43367,68286,111846,7333,119207}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0SdZVPbkwoQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lo6pteCRE_I}', 'Sega Enterprises, Ltd.', '0', null, null), (946, 'Tomoyo After: It''s a Wonderful Life - Memorial Edition', 'From renowned visual novel studio Key, this is the sequel to the highly acclaimed visual novel Clannad. Featuring a truly memorable continuation to Tomoya and Tomoyo''s journey, Tomoyo After promises to draw you even further into Clannad''s world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co44qe.jpg', '2010-04-30', '{12,15,31,34}', 'IGDB', 95.4616363134223, 33000, 1, 8.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30203.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56717.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56713.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56714.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56715.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56716.jpg"]', '{103232,113402,109339,19164,25311,35994,27092,28182,26574,26145}', '{}', 'Key', '0', null, null), (947, 'Final Fantasy XIV: Complete Edition', 'The complete edition includes the award-winning FINAL FANTASY XIV: A Realm Reborn and the Heavensward and Stormblood expansion packs.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9heg.jpg', '2017-06-20', '{12}', 'IGDB', 95.4439203146529, 106819, 1, 46.99, '[{"id":22956,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":187949,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348650.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348654.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348655.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348652.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348653.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348657.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/348656.jpg"]', '{81249,115653,19164,23651,49414,113360,19404,54775,37382,17548}', '{}', 'Square Enix', '3', null, null), (948, 'Rooftop Rascal: The Alley Cat', 'In "Rooftop Rascal: The Alley Cat," you control a clever alley cat navigating city buildings'' fire escape stairs to the rooftop goal.
The gameplay centres on precise jumps, avoiding (possible) obstacles, and quick thinking.
Your goal is to climb as high as you can, reach the rooftop, and beat the game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8i5b.jpg', '2024-06-30', '{8,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95.4285714285714, 308323, 1, 63.99, '[{"id":181272,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/141208.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/141209.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356634.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356633.jpg"]', '{20342,77529,55173,111130,24426,28070,55282,89597,55190,29348}', '{}', 'chroda.eu', '0', null, '{12821}'), (949, 'iRacing', 'From NASCAR, rallycross, and Aussie Supercars to sports cars and Grand Prix racing, iRacing has it all. All you need is a computer, a gaming wheel or game pad that simply plugs into the USB port of your computer and an Internet connection. iRacing centrally organizes all of the racing for you with over 150 cars and tracks, 40 official series , or you can choose to host your own race or race in one of over 800 private leagues.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2sjw.jpg', '2008-08-26', '{10,13,14}', 'IGDB', 95.3887461782715, 8204, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":225114,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30603.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7535.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7537.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7538.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7539.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7536.jpg"]', '{78511,38967,197936,119422,118871,114286,5597,103218,44242,110411}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rLfkPntDlO8}', 'iRacing.com Motorsport Simulations', '0', null, null), (950, 'Castlevania Advance Collection', 'Castlevania Advance Collection includes three legendary Castlevania games that were first released in the early 2000s: Circle of the Moon, Aria of Sorrow, and Harmony of Dissonance. In addition, this collection also includes Castlevania: Dracula X and some never-before-seen sketches and artwork from the games!

All four games are enhanced with newly added modern features such as Rewind, Save/Load, and Replay, making this the best way possible to experience these classics or discover them for the first time! This collection also boasts a handy Encyclopedia, a Music Player with all soundtracks; and you can even change the ROM Region to play all games in different versions.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob9xj.jpg', '2021-09-23', '{8,12,31}', 'IGDB', 95.3804440810504, 152765, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":67424,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":56025,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":50738,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":125850,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":92708,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":190610,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":231011,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52836.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642578.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642579.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642580.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642573.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642574.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642575.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642576.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/642577.jpg"]', '{116530,106987,24426,96217,81249,28168,55038,19164,103168,55199}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKZWrHU8hhA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fXVARrPgGDM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dXkA6RGW0l8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wmZF2C1MmbM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r-hN1UvSJm8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EtdJho8vfUs}', 'M2', '3', null, null), (951, 'The Last of Us Remastered', 'The Last of Us Remastered is an updated release of the PS3 game The Last of Us. It is identical to the PS3 version but runs at a 1080p resolution and incorporates character models with a higher resolution. There are also improved shadows and lighting, upgraded textures, 60 frames per second and other types of improvements. In addition to the base game, two map packs and the expansion The Last of Us: Left Behind are included.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5zks.jpg', '2014-07-26', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 95.3772942941535, 6036, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":47775,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":47777,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":47776,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":47774,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":47778,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":188089,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":44202,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6200.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6199.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6201.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9466.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9467.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9464.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9463.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9465.jpg"]', '{105049,19561,102584,19564,37016,13210,44076,111130,101211,26658}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UNn6EIRsL0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z2RlTvdNjzQ}', 'Naughty Dog', '9', null, '{864}'), (952, 'Dragon Quest VIII: Journey of the Cursed King', 'This is a portable version of the classic RPG, with added content and other 3DS enhancements.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2xc0.jpg', '2015-08-27', '{12,15,31}', 'IGDB', 95.2801434046983, 145528, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":75240,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":216702,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":190838,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":34454,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/73669.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/430490.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/430491.jpg"]', '{27092,26765,19404,106987,96217,25921,115653,26845,103232,19164}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AmIR60Jws88}', 'Nintendo', '10', null, '{7988}'), (953, 'Elden Ring', 'Elden Ring is an action RPG developed by FromSoftware and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment, released in February 2022. Directed by Hidetaka Miyazaki, with world-building contributions from novelist George R. R. Martin, the game features an expansive open world called the Lands Between. Players assume the role of a customisable character known as the Tarnished, who must explore this world, battle formidable enemies, and seek to restore the Elden Ring to become the Elden Lord.

The game builds on the challenging gameplay mechanics familiar from the Dark Souls series but introduces a more open-ended structure with vast exploration, dynamic weather, and a day-night cycle. It offers deep lore, complex characters, and an interconnected world filled with secrets, dungeons, and powerful bosses.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4jni.jpg', '2022-02-25', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 95.2384314372848, 119133, 1, 71.99, '[{"id":57167,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":57169,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":213790,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":57164,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":57168,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":57165,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":57170,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168540.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168541.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168539.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52129.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487786.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487787.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487788.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487789.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487790.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487791.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/487792.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703441.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1406912.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1406913.jpg"]', '{2155,2368,23733,1942,103329,119171,7346,472,19560,3025}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D1mDo1CEMuE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3Huy2cdih0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qqiC88f9ogU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D8YkCHkWRyk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DbPbQMuEyX8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l6pCyV7PnqI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e5wwSxl0atc}', 'Bandai Namco Entertainment', '0', null, '{10964}'), (954, 'Troubleshooter: Abandoned Children', 'Troubleshooter: Abandoned Children is the first season of a turn-based strategy SRPG that takes place in the world of Troubleshooter, wherein the Valhalla government granted civilians the right to investigate and arrest criminals in order to lower the rising crime rate. People call these civilians Troubleshooter.

10 years have passed since the introduction of the troubleshooter system. Albus, a 20-year-old young man, becomes an official troubleshooter. Albus first starts his company on his own but soon takes in many colleagues as he solves more cases. All these new members of the company have their own motivations and stories. You will be experiencing a variety of missions in Valhalla through their stories.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21q6.jpg', '2020-04-23', '{12,15,16,32}', 'IGDB', 95.2364382448269, 80002, 1, 63.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/22904.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143602.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143603.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143600.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143601.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143599.jpg"]', '{25311,13660,19404,28182,9472,13200,113402,13196,7615,34823}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0q1SqOMYXE}', 'Dandylion', '0', '{144452,224997}', null), (955, 'The House in Fata Morgana: A Requiem for Innocence', 'A Requiem for Innocence main episode is a prequel to the original "The House in Fata Morgana", comes with several sub episodes that are companions to the game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co43un.jpg', '2015-08-16', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 95.1809476246574, 56006, 1, 27.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/85880.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238654.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238650.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238655.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238652.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238653.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/238656.jpg"]', '{103266,55984,18011,107614,55322,111130,116530,121533,55282,13189}', '{}', 'NOVECT', '0', null, '{2997}'), (956, 'Orchard Odyssey: Cherry Chase', 'In Orchard Odyssey: Cherry Chase, you guide Aurora through a single vibrant orchard level to collect cherries. You can run, jump, and unlock new abilities like double jump or enhanced map vision. The map is semi-procedural being shuffled every time you enter the Orchard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coalil.jpg', '2025-09-29', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 95.1807228915663, 370257, 1, 93.99, '[{"id":221515,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203035.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203034.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1656207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1656208.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1656209.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1656210.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1656211.jpg"]', '{20342,55173,24426,37001,28070,89597,395582,393624,391146,390781}', '{}', 'chroda.eu', '0', null, '{13030}'), (957, 'Fate/Stay Night Remastered', 'A remastered version of Fate/Stay Night, a fantasy action drama visual novel and TYPE-Moon''s first-ever commercial release in 2004. Based on the 2012 release of Réalta Nua, it features a series-first adaptation into languages such as English and Simplified Chinese, as well as graphics and animations rendered in full HD.

Experience in vivid detail the story of Shirou Emiya, a teenage boy with dreams of becoming a Hero of Justice, and his battle revolving around the omnipotent wish-granting vessel, the Holy Grail.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8mt8.jpg', '2024-08-07', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 95.1612903225806, 284570, 1, 79.99, '[{"id":183731,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":183349,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/143788.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375802.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375803.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375796.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375800.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1375801.jpg"]', '{106987,34218,96217,81249,115653,105060,103168,26870,55038,101608}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K_hHrpAp8rU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IeHShG5Bv-8}', 'fuzz', '9', null, '{1635}'), (958, 'Hunter Moonstrike', 'Hunter Moonstrike is the first survival game integrated with artificial intelligence. In this game, all npc have their own unique story and you can see the story of the game from their point of view. Talk to any person, ask any question you like, they will answer and think they are alive', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co96tr.jpg', '2025-01-23', '{5,12,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95.1424287856072, 305296, 1, 83.99, '[{"id":177474,"rating_category":{"id":1,"rating":"RP"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139450.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139452.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139453.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139451.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139449.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/151252.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339373.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339372.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339379.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339380.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339375.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339376.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339377.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339378.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1343398.jpg"]', '{102584,26574,17379,19164,17548,44076,105269,19561,25300,10776}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KKw12UPAdJs}', '10nstudio', '0', null, null), (959, 'The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild', 'The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild is the first 3D open-world game in the Zelda series. Link can travel anywhere and be equipped with weapons and armor found throughout the world to grant him various bonuses. Unlike many games in the series, Breath of the Wild does not impose a specific order in which quests or dungeons must be completed. While the game still has environmental obstacles such as weather effects, inhospitable lands, or powerful enemies, many of them can be overcome using the right method. A lot of critics ranked Breath of the Wild as one of the best video games of all time.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3p2d.jpg', '2017-03-03', '{9,31}', 'IGDB', 95.0977765463026, 7346, 1, 35.99, '[{"id":226927,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":32771,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":47171,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":91197,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"