{106,8988}'), (960, 'tModLoader', 'tModLoader (TML) is an open-source, community-driven modification and expansion of the Terraria game that makes it possible to make and play mods.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co48gu.jpg', '2020-05-17', '{8,12,13,15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95.0939556584325, 134157, 1, 76.99, '[{"id":28177,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":189219,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/20936.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481813.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481829.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481816.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481819.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481822.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481824.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481827.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481828.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481831.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481832.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481834.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481836.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/481845.jpg"]', '{26574,25311,35994,109339,24426,106987,29348,37419,28182,28309}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hg2A2dTQjAw}', 'Re-Logic', '5', null, '{555}'), (961, 'Baldur''s Gate III', 'An ancient evil has returned to Baldur''s Gate, intent on devouring it from the inside out. The fate of Faerun lies in your hands. Alone, you may resist. But together, you can overcome.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co670h.jpg', '2023-08-03', '{12,15,16}', 'IGDB', 95.0854442730875, 119171, 1, 62.99, '[{"id":204993,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":162025,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":204994,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":213789,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":161963,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":148088,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":162028,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169875.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169876.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169877.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/178125.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375103.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375101.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375099.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375105.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375102.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375107.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/375106.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1381715.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581034.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581035.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581036.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577635.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577636.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577632.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577633.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577634.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581048.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581049.jpg"]', '{14394,26845,19560,10297,1887,2365,103298,105049,9243,111253}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jNY7AEQ59-8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5xpbAsly48,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tavPnYeFrV4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zTX79cgruXE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t0uYhTLPGLQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XuCfkgaaa08,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OcP0WdH7rTs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ks-KF9iueE0}', 'Wushu Studios', '0', null, '{7}'), (962, 'Bad End Theater', 'Welcome to Bad End Theater! Select your protagonist and explore a variety of terrible fates! The decisions you make in one story will affect the others. you can toggle these behaviors to open up new paths! unfortunately, every path leads to a bad ending... Can you find a way to save this unlucky cast? Playtime: 2-3 hours to see all endings (it''s a puzzle game, so this varies widely).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co44y4.jpg', '2021-10-26', '{9,13,31,32,34}', 'IGDB', 95.0559987973918, 178264, 1, 69.99, '[{"id":214521,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":215002,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56862.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56861.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56860.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672017.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672018.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672019.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672020.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672021.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672022.jpg"]', '{24426,38045,26226,28070,17906,36198,28277,111253,96217,18182}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-4lJhUd0qpQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xyw1-jnXfnE}', 'NomNomNami', '0', null, null), (963, 'Umineko When They Cry: Answer Arcs', 'This is the second half of the Umineko When They Cry sound novel series, featuring episodes 5 through 8. This version features multi-language options, swappable renewed character sprites, as well as the original BGMs and un-cut content.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co78v5.jpg', '2017-11-17', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 95.048048048048, 75081, 1, 40.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/39035.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132199.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132200.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132197.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132198.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/132201.jpg"]', '{18011,116530,75948,111130,18225,55047,80916,54678,25646,25222}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KYd-qSK9ktM}', 'MangaGamer', '3', null, '{1622}'), (964, 'Mewgenics', 'From the creator of The Binding of Isaac, Super Meat Boy and The End is Nigh comes... Mewgenics! A game where you hoard, breed, train and set cats out on epic adventures through a sprawling world of complete chaos.
Level up your team as you venture further and further from your home, collect unique items, defeat epic bosses, gain mutations and return home so you you can breed and further your bloodline, in this turn based legacy roguelike draft sim about cats!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9n5k.jpg', '2026-02-10', '{12,13,16,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95.016522500176, 8042, 1, 80.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/91634.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/244166.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/245375.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758667.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758668.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758669.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758670.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758671.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758672.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758673.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758674.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758675.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1758676.jpg"]', '{19150,29348,51945,25311,35994,109339,26574,33153,26145,15409}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXCp8xS0YzI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YyWcrDKg9hA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FhxmMH8VohA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ruLQ1Hmhjs}', 'Edmund McMillen', '0', null, null), (965, 'Raccoin: Coin Pusher Roguelike', 'A coin-pushing dopamine machine. RACCOIN is a roguelike deckbuilder where you combine special coins with powerful items to trigger wildly satisfying combos. Stack shiny towers, spin the lucky wheel, and shake the machine until all the coins drop.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaa0s.jpg', '2026-03-31', '{13,15,32,33}', 'IGDB', 95, 360748, 1, 79.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/187294.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/187295.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611847.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611848.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611849.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611850.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611851.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611852.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611853.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1611854.jpg"]', '{76263,23733,17000,81680,82090,14593,25076,17130,55042,18182}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yy1FcT6sfIo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=df8ykBDZ8k0}', 'Doraccoon', '0', null, null), (966, 'Clone Drone in the Hyperdome', 'Cut robots apart in VR. Feel your sword disintegrate their metal bodies. Now you live and die in the Crashloop, a roguelike tournament to the death. Lock swords! Shoot shurikens from your wrist! This is CLONE DRONE... in the HYPERDOME!!!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co91ic.jpg', '2024-12-12', '{4,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 322126, 1, 78.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148659.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420094.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420088.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420089.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420090.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420091.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420092.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420093.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420095.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1420096.jpg"]', '{113895,21642,111130,106987,37419,89550,28309,96217,25646,105011}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lak9cQqVsrM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=54ug3ytfh_Q}', 'Doborog Games', '0', null, '{11810}'), (967, 'Vampire Survivors: Ode to Castlevania', 'The Vampire Survivors have come a long way in their honorable hunt, and after joining forces with the Belmont Family, they are the closest they''ve ever been. Finally, within their grasp... A vampire. Possibly, at least.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8zb0.jpg', '2024-10-31', '{12,32,33}', 'IGDB', 95, 320770, 1, 62.99, '[{"id":207732,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":207733,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":207734,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":207735,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":207736,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":193518,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/149279.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414109.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414110.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414111.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414112.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414113.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414114.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414115.jpg"]', '{106987,96217,17548,19150,24426,26574,47823,19404,54775,28309}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aGAlK-DIeAE}', 'Poncle', '1', null, null), (968, 'Vampire Survivors: Operation Guns', 'Grab your blaster, join Contra Force, and be the bullet hell in Vampire Survivors: Operation Guns

Assemble a squad of classic Characters and arm yourself with an explosive arsenal of arcade weaponry in this action packed expansion for Vampire Survivors. Blast through thousands of fearsome foes and bonkers bosses from throughout the lauded lineage of Contra games. Persist determinedly through prodigious stages inspired by iconic Konami series, but be prepared for a bullet-hell of a fight, because if your trigger finger lacks stamina, Earth may lack a future.

The DLC adds 11 characters, 22 weapons, 1 large stage, 1 bonus stage, 30 in-game unlocks and a 6 chapter adventure.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co82cf.jpg', '2024-05-09', '{12,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 296834, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":208275,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":208276,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":208277,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":208278,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":208279,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":173209,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/136169.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299496.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299497.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299510.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299511.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299502.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299504.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299506.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299508.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1299509.jpg"]', '{113895,106987,28309,96217,80916,30245,105269,56036,25311,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JL-73l_hCMg}', 'Poncle', '1', null, null), (969, 'Remnant II: The Awakened King', 'The One True King has awakened and is out for blood. Corrupted by the Root during his near-death slumber, the mad king sees betrayal at every turn and is on a rampage of revenge. Since his castle first arrived in a Dran coastal town, the tides are angry and the weather is chaotic, surfacing all manner of creatures from the depths and leaving many mysteries in its wake.

This DLC adds the Ritualist archetyp, a new storyline, dungeons and area based in the world of Losomn. It includes a wide array of new weapons, modifications, amulets, and rings along with new bosses, characters and fearsome creatures to encounter.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7bud.jpg', '2023-11-14', '{5,12,31}', 'IGDB', 95, 274832, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":174975,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":174976,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":174977,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":159155,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":159156,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":159157,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":159158,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/122758.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185745.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185747.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185741.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185742.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185743.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185744.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185746.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185740.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1185739.jpg"]', '{55038,105269,19164,107318,106987,96217,47823,81249,103168,25311}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9h7RPuu4MWM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yUtFAI6PxZY}', 'Gunfire Games', '1', null, null), (970, 'Subpar Pool', 'A whimsical adventure of playful pocket antics at the intersection of golf and pool, from the developer behind holedown, twofold inc & rymdkapsel.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co786e.jpg', '2023-10-12', '{9,13,14,33}', 'IGDB', 95, 269204, 1, 65.99, '[{"id":155061,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":154608,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119137.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155986.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155987.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155988.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155989.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155990.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1155991.jpg"]', '{112078,118871,15851,114285,25905,103218,90788,56033,121036,37419}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9H3Z8U5zfJY}', 'grapefrukt games', '0', null, null), (971, 'Dicefolk', 'Wield magical dice and build a team of powerful Chimeras to stop a mysterious evil in this tactical roguelite adventure. As a Chimera Summoner, recruit and create your perfect team of mythical beasts and command them to victory using unique dice mechanics.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6mcg.jpg', '2024-02-27', '{15,16,24,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 251938, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":174368,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":174697,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/109163.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064040.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064043.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064044.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064032.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064036.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064045.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1064042.jpg"]', '{40477,13660,28182,9472,65827,117417,19404,31515,24765,18623}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gb4NB4l5vg0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5QpseqnV6c}', 'LEAP Game Studios', '0', '{324415}', null), (972, 'Asgard’s Wrath II', 'Awaken, Cosmic Guardian – The fate of reality lies in your hands. Travel across vast realms inhabited by the gods in pursuit of the Trickster God Loki, who threatens to undo the threads of the universe. It’s up to you to battle gods and monsters alike as you take on one of the biggest and most epic scale Action RPGs ever experienced in VR. Alongside legendary Egyptian gods, you’ll fight deadly warriors and awe-inspiring mythical creatures through physics-based, visceral combat with unique weapons and playstyles. Possess unique mortal heroes and convert loyal animals into your own warrior followers as you explore a massive, free-roaming and living world and solve mind-bending god-scale puzzles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co95kf.jpg', '2023-12-15', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 95, 251569, 1, 60.99, '[{"id":140975,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/109288.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1061809.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1061811.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1061810.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1061812.jpg"]', '{106987,28309,96217,115280,81249,80916,30245,103168,105269,55038}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSGbejtHEL0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1fmrPW6wEdc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bAlg73UA8kA}', 'Oculus Studios', '0', null, '{8824}'), (973, 'Sektori', 'Sektori is an intense, fast paced twin-stick shooter where every run is unique. Choose your upgrades carefully and create powerful builds to take on numerous enemies and epic bosses on a constantly evolving battlefield.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8ygz.jpg', '2025-11-18', '{5,32,33}', 'IGDB', 95, 217363, 1, 82.99, '[{"id":221519,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/87139.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/881184.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/881190.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/881192.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/881194.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/881195.jpg"]', '{43367,105269,32902,113895,119493,107318,47823,56033,111130,25901}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VWr9XhWHjYY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yGWsLyZ0KPU}', 'Kimmo Factor', '0', null, null), (974, 'Ash of Gods: The Way', 'A turn-based tactical story-driven card game set in a fantasy world of Ash of Gods. Two decks, three lines, six factions and a great deal of possibilities to create your own unique strategy.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co692t.jpg', '2023-04-27', '{9,12,15,16,24,31,32,35}', 'IGDB', 95, 192439, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":136146,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":136145,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":134411,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":117051,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":136147,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":136148,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/69065.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743587.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743588.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743589.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743578.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743582.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743579.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743580.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743581.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743583.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743584.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743585.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/743586.jpg"]', '{13196,26845,40477,19404,24426,106987,14394,28182,96217,115653}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aGVuiAdWQxs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXU-Nupjtng,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CytheVNQXZs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=et_0_woAj8c}', 'AurumDust', '0', null, null), (975, 'Final Fantasy: Pixel Remaster Collection', 'The Final Fantasy: Pixel Remaster series will comprise FINAL FANTASY I through FINAL FANTASY VI, with each game releasing individually. For long-term fans that will be hugely exciting news - a chance to revisit some of their most beloved RPGs of all time in a way that perfectly captures the spirit of those original game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6nzk.jpg', '2021-07-28', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 95, 159253, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":169016,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":191881,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":191880,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":191884,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":191885,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":191887,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":191891,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/129198.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/551943.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/551942.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/551941.jpg"]', '{106987,96217,81249,115653,103168,23651,55038,101608,49414,19164}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIgWhs-mq5g,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2n4CnfChxg8}', 'Tose', '3', null, null), (976, 'Henchman Story', 'A visual novel where you play as a beleaguered henchman working for a bumbling supervillain, and a slice of superhero satire packed with colorful characters and meaningful choices. Even henchmen have bills to pay, and sometimes, even henchmen can make choices that change everything.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4ar1.jpg', '2021-10-14', '{12,13,31,32,34}', 'IGDB', 95, 151303, 1, 52.99, '[{"id":109684,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":136464,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":136803,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":136801,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":136800,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":136802,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30175.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/482695.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/482691.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/482698.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/482703.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/482709.jpg"]', '{25311,35994,26574,96217,106987,19164,28309,80916,29348,105011}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i32_QprdKFw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-BIpeei6pDU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=87r55sxINiI}', 'Silken Sail Entertainment', '0', null, null), (977, 'Shindig', 'Shindig is a short point-and-click adventure that celebrates the low-key heroism of helping. Explore a cosy hand-drawn world, solve the boggles of your animal friends, and bring the whole community together for a joyous party!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3s6d.jpg', '2021-09-02', '{31,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 149250, 1, 52.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30831.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/466066.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/466070.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/466076.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/466079.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/466083.jpg"]', '{55282,111130,87975,29348,13189,27266,26223,118637,106987,113402}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (978, 'Caves (Roguelike)', 'A turn-based tactical Dungeon-delving game with perma-death. Each run can help you find blueprints or new armor to aid you in the caves.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2mvx.jpg', '2015-11-14', '{12,16,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 141828, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":31459,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414513.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414514.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414511.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414512.jpg"]', '{109339,28182,26574,26145,120201,9472,19404,29348,17548,106987}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfytSAj1jsA}', '36dev', '0', null, null), (979, 'Night Reverie', 'Night Reverie is a Puzzle/Adventure game in which a child must solve the mystery behind the distortion of his house. Explore puzzle-filled environments and discover strange creatures living in the house as you reach the truth behind of what looks like a bizarre nightmare.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ixu.jpg', '2021-10-08', '{9,31,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 139598, 1, 63.99, '[{"id":148123,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":148124,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":148126,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":148122,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":148121,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":148125,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34160.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405388.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405389.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405390.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405391.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405392.jpg"]', '{236,26223,81275,18011,28070,80916,25646,25222,11737,27266}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ymbshw6M-ug}', 'Somber Pixel', '0', null, null), (980, 'Read Only Memories: Neurodiver', 'Return to the vibrant cyberpunk world of Neo-San Francisco from 2064: Read Only Memories, filled with friendly and familiar faces. Neurodiver will introduce new characters, locations, and mechanics, including the ability to dive into and change other characters'' memories, as well as overhauled art and an unsolved case to crack with multiple endings.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co97eu.jpg', '2024-05-16', '{31,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 119401, 1, 58.99, '[{"id":175433,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":173780,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":173672,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":175430,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":175425,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":175428,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/50383.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388649.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388648.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388652.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388650.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388647.jpg"]', '{105269,25311,107318,24426,28070,111130,28277,29348,106987,22210}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N5zmbVxW6pc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q8e-XeA40KA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eSzYVaRSGHk}', 'MidBoss', '0', null, '{10999}'), (981, 'Jack Jeanne', 'Jack Jeanne is an opera-themed otome game, produced and illustrated by Sui Ishida (Tokyo Ghoul) and co-written by Ishida and Shin Towada (Tokyo Ghoul light novels). Protagonist Kisa Tachibana is given an opportunity to fulfill her dream of going to the All Boys Univeil Drama School where she must develop bonds and rivalries with her classmates while hiding her identity as a girl.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6mye.jpg', '2021-03-18', '{7,13,31,34}', 'IGDB', 95, 117675, 1, 69.99, '[{"id":98607,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":137221,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":137305,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8769.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401452.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401453.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401454.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074010.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074009.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074011.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074012.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074013.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074014.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1074015.jpg"]', '{114150,17906,19075,38045,12151,147272,147996,147734,125276,117265}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=THJenp3CLTk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0nGPmHuVm_w,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZWeKZRCPAg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRW9WE6N-y4}', 'Broccoli', '0', null, null), (982, 'Oblivion', 'A action game developed by Simon Morris and published by Alpha-Omega Software for ZX Spectrum.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ifh5lt57hoz2wlubnkd9.jpg', null, null, 'IGDB', 95, 77199, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{100800,113895,57296,25636,57372,105233,95340,87728,65672,111835}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (983, 'Path of Exile: The Fall of Oriath', 'This is the next free update/expansion to the game Path of Exile.
This update will, among other improvements and additions, change the games main story and level progression. It will be changed from a 4 act story campaign being repeated over 3 difficulties to a single story campaign across 10 acts with new enemies and bosses in each area.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/akbxkxkbfmunhgdphzyo.jpg', '2017-08-04', '{12,25,31}', 'IGDB', 95, 51543, 1, 35.99, '[{"id":88486,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":88485,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/125408.jpg"]', '{103168,54775,106987,96217,81249,103303,55038,19164,55199,101608}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lgWzr0Vxyrw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b6lZl9t_I-g,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YFAPw_F3jyg}', 'Grinding Gear Games', '2', null, null), (984, 'Stardew Valley: Collector''s Edition', 'Chuckle Fish teamed up with 505 Games and ConcernedApe to produce this Collector’s Edition, which includes:

- A copy of Stardew Valley for Xbox One or PlayStation 4.
- A disc containing the Collector’s Edition Soundtrack featuring 33 hand-picked tracks.
- Exclusive fold-out map of Stardew Valley, illustrated by Kari Fry.
- A Mini-Guidebook created by the artist and author of the full guidebook, Kari Fry.

Fangamer teamed up with ConcernedApe to produce the Collector’s Edition for Nintendo Switch, which includes:

- A physical copy of Stardew Valley for Nintendo Switch with 18-page, full-color illustrated instruction manual and double-sided cover.
- A soft polyester-nylon blend cleaning cloth.
- A Collector''s Edition box made from high-quality materials featuring artwork by the artist and author of the full guidebook, Kari Fry.
- A deed to your farm featuring gold-foil details on paper made from 30% recycled straw.
- A 14-page Junimo comic by the artist of the ''Before the Farmer'', Chihiro Sakaida.
- A wooden lapel pin.
- A deluxe six-piece wooden standee.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27vj.jpg', '2017-04-11', '{12,13,32}', 'IGDB', 95, 42895, 1, 41.99, '[{"id":85527,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/499374.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/838680.jpg"]', '{111187,19404,29348,106987,37419,26574,47823,96217,29173,51577}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=knnwoPvL784}', '505 Games', '0', null, null), (985, 'HEX: Shards of Fate - Chronicles of Entrath', 'Chronicles of Entrath introduces an extensive single-player campaing to HEX: Shards of Fate.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1jry.jpg', '2016-01-28', '{35}', 'IGDB', 95, 24352, 1, 56.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6774.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/421181.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/421182.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/421183.jpg"]', '{77498,68045,23651,49414,383108,320421,267507,266566,233293,206867}', '{}', 'Hex Entertainment', '2', null, null), (986, 'Crusader Kings II: The Reaper''s Due', 'Little remains of those settlements where the Black Death has passed through. Hasty burials make a mockery of the sacraments and set a feast for the crows. Once prosperous provinces have been laid waste, and the lord of the land hides away – secluded in his hilltop fortress, hoping the plague will pass him by. Wiser princes took precautions, and didn’t waste the revenues from more prosperous years.

But, in time, all must pay The Reaper’s Due.

The Reaper’s Due adds a host of new mechanics centered on the Black Death and other world shaping epidemics. Lock your gates to keep the plague from infecting your court, even if it means cutting yourself off from your suffering citizens. Peace and good management will see your provinces reward you with greater wealth and manpower, but constant war and disease may depopulate your countryside.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1yxi.jpg', '2016-08-25', '{12,13,15}', 'IGDB', 95, 23850, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":11156,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":11155,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/109800.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/37388.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/37390.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/37389.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/37391.jpg"]', '{18623,23345,36553,55590,103232,102163,79134,109339,111187,3700}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u08K9uvRM3E}', 'Paradox Development Studio', '2', null, '{540}'), (987, 'LittleBigPlanet: Game of the Year Edition', 'If you were to stand on LittleBigPlanet and try to imagine a more astounding, fantastic, and creative place, full of enthralling adventure, uncanny characters, and brilliant things to do... you couldn’t. All imagination is here, and what you do with it all is entirely up to you.
Build new levels and expand the environment, collect the many and varied tools and objects to make your mark on this world, or just simply enjoy the people and puzzles they’ve set.
LittleBigPlanet is the manifested embodiment of your perfect dream world...

Winner of over 80 prominent awards, including several Game of the Year awards, LittleBigPlanet returns with its signature "Play, Create and Share" experience plus irresistible new bonus content valued over $30! With the new Game of the Year Edition, players can play 18 brand new levels, create their own experiences with bonus costume and level packs--including the Metal Gear Solid Level Pack--then go online to share their levels with other players around the world or play over 1 Million user generated levels that have been uploaded since the launch of the original game release. There is no better time to join the world of LittleBigPlanet!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3kps.jpg', '2009-09-08', '{8,9}', 'IGDB', 95, 21846, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":28983,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":28982,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393666.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393667.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393668.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393669.jpg"]', '{89132,77529,20342,55173,24426,28070,55190,56033,1058,89074}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HY7XrBQZUyo}', 'Sony Computer Entertainment', '10', null, '{238}'), (988, 'Baldur''s Gate: Siege of Dragonspear - Collector''s Edition', 'The Collector''s Edition features a limited-edition collector''s box that will be shipped to you as soon as it is ready from the manufacturer. You will also receive a digital copy of Baldur''s Gate: Enhanced Edition and Baldur''s Gate: Siege of Dragonspear to play immediately upon ordering.

The Collector''s Box includes:

DRM-free copy of Baldur''s Gate: Enhanced Edition and Baldur''s Gate: Siege of Dragonspear on DVD.

Complete soundtrack of Baldur''s Gate, Baldur''s Gate: Enhanced Edition, and Baldur''s Gate: Siege of Dragonspear.

Cloth map of the Sword Coast.

Full-color copy of Bence Duncan''s Field Report with removable, collectible coin.

Spiral-bound copy of the official Baldur''s Gate Adventurer''s Guide with updated rules and mechanics.

Metal dragon''s head amulet on a strap necklace.

Collection of 7 Siege of Dragonspear-themed collector''s dice, housed in a velvet dice bag.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/eamxoi3281r2e5kuwu1w.jpg', '2016-03-31', '{12}', 'IGDB', 95, 21813, 1, 41.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130296.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/332987.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/332988.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/332989.jpg"]', '{23651,49414,113910,69007,22790,19127,57033,19404,113636,54775}', '{}', 'Overhaul Games', '2', null, null), (989, 'Light in the Dark', 'Light in the Dark is a physics puzzle game for mobile devices from Dreamgate Studios.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/inelxhna3nm2xyu9jixo.jpg', null, '{9}', 'IGDB', 95, 21684, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29474.jpg"]', '{95776,87507,25905,19222,90788,10603,88511,41349,86974,90839}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (990, 'Out of the Park Baseball 15', 'The 2014 installment of the celebrated Out Of The Park Baseball franchise.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xou.jpg', '2014-03-04', '{13}', 'IGDB', 95, 16955, 1, 27.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/31829.jpg"]', '{36346,31515,17519,29173,55590,40470,119235,32457,101573,17130}', '{}', null, '0', null, '{2379}'), (991, 'Towerfall Ascension: Dark World', 'Challenge your friends to fight through TowerFall''s Dark World, with or against you, in this massive expansion for the acclaimed archery brawler.
Team up to challenge the all-new Dark World Mode - a co-op campaign for 1-4 players. Battle your way to hideous boss monsters, and face the brutal challenge of the added Legendary difficulty mode. Expand your roster of playable fighters with the undead pirate Vainglorious Ghoul and 9 more alternate archers.
Dark World also adds a powerful level creation tool, allowing players to create and share their own new Versus towers.

The Dark World Expansion pushes TowerFall further in every direction, a great excuse to revisit the beloved indie fighter.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21hv.jpg', '2015-05-12', '{4,8,31,32,33}', 'IGDB', 95, 14724, 1, 22.99, '[{"id":85416,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/18723.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/18724.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/18725.jpg"]', '{106987,24426,96217,28070,110503,56033,103369,101608,19150,111130}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LpreXmKdsTs}', 'Maddy Makes Games', '2', null, null), (992, 'Witch on the Holy Night', 'Set in 1980s Japan, Witch on the Holy Night tells the story of fan-favorite Type-Moon character Aoko Aozaki as she attempts to navigate the complex world of magecraft while also dealing with the everyday struggles of life as a high school student! Players will experience the thrilling origin story of this much-beloved character, penned by Kinoko Nasu, famed creator of the Fate series, himself.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5rw2.jpg', '2022-12-07', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 94.9932248964927, 201065, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":76722,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":101310,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":101298,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":119133,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/91784.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/91034.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916448.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916450.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916458.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916473.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916476.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/916478.jpg"]', '{65487,96217,106987,5