/image/upload/t_1080p/368770.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/368775.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/368777.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/368779.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/368778.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/368776.jpg"]', '{43367,55042,56033,25901,105269,110503,24426,55190,20342,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=No00F3syet0}', 'The Elephant Crew', '0', null, null), (997, 'Metal Gear Solid 3: Subsistence', 'Metal Gear Solid 3: Subsistence continues the Metal Gear Solid series tradition of follow-up enhanced, international version releases.
Subsistence''s online multiplayer component, titled Metal Gear Online, consists of five tournament-style game modes, each with a capacity of up to eight players. This mode pits players, each playing as a generic soldier against each other in deathmatch battles and variations of capture the flag, using stages, items, maneuvers, and units (such as the KGB, GRU or Ocelot Unit) from the main game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1vd6.jpg', '2005-12-22', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 94.8265316015664, 479, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":72704,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":55688,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":192343,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":192341,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":192342,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26729.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/338717.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/338716.jpg"]', '{19164,55038,105049,27316,47823,106987,96217,37777,55984,68287}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wHzAba66FfA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0XyD2W0yLUI}', 'Konami Computer Entertainment Japan', '10', null, '{2128}'), (998, 'Rayman 2: The Great Escape', 'The PC version of Rayman 2: The Great Escape retains the same level structure from the Nintendo 64 version with higher resolution graphics and a higher frame rate.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co54kj.jpg', '1999-10-29', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 94.8019876717968, 193313, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":59640,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":94656,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":94577,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":123211,"rating_category":{"id":18,"rating":"0"}},{"id":167622,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/70175.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/750970.jpg","https://im