ategy game inspired by XCOM but offers its own unique take on the genre. Meet real life WW2 heroes and choose whether to fight with or against them! It’s time to lead the resistance against the Axis forces and help to liberate Europe!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8ja0.jpg', '2024-11-18', '{15,16}', 'IGDB', 94, 223293, 1, 64.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/90298.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910593.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910594.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910595.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910582.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910584.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910586.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910588.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910590.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/910592.jpg"]', '{36258,10243,31480,18623,32510,115659,23345,55590,55029,102163}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7m8rYRSSDj8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M-c-UINaLsI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FvVK1VGtW1g}', 'MicroProse', '0', null, null), (1020, 'Vivid/Stasis', 'vivid/stasis is a rhythm-mystery game that follows the fate and feelings of a group of girls as they get wrapped up in a mind-bending adventure involving organizations, mysterious disappearances, and the fourth dimension.

The game ties together an immense and interweaving storyline with varying levels of music-based gameplay.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co98hb.jpg', '2025-07-05', '{7,32,34}', 'IGDB', 94, 206513, 1, 80.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/90175.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814335.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814336.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814337.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814338.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814339.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1814340.jpg"]', '{18981,80916,13200,26223,105269,63933,25311,34823,81275,77720}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VaygsqjGya4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r9X6PWvWrp4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJ2ZlErW1XY}', 'SKY HOUR WORKS', '0', null, null), (1021, 'Tales from the Borderlands: Episode 5 - The Vault of the Traveler', 'A new episodic adventure set in the badlands of Pandora. This collaborative brain child, is set after the events of Borderlands 2 and is a part of the franchise'' official lore.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1vct.jpg', '2015-10-20', '{2,31}', 'IGDB', 94, 127038, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":226974,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":26639,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347926.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347923.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347925.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347929.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347927.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347928.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347924.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347930.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/347931.jpg"]', '{62151,105269,55038,25311,107318,103301,115283,111130,28070,103266}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=08Y2dxkMYIw}', 'Telltale Games', '6', null, '{7814}'), (1022, 'Doodle Date', 'Romance, seduce, and even marry your own drawings! Forget about finding true love; In Doodle Date, you create it!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2dly.jpg', '2018-04-19', '{13,32,34}', 'IGDB', 94, 96632, 1, 58.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35437.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235169.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235172.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235168.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235175.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235167.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235166.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235171.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235170.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235165.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235173.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235174.jpg"]', '{19075,111130,65827,91967,31515,36269,29348,18623,55282,37419}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfyXplJCksU}', 'Nicholas Lives', '0', null, null), (1023, 'Derail Valley', 'Drive massive trains and build your career in a vast open railway network. For both PC and VR.

What makes Derail Valley different?

You can feel the physics. Walk without restrictions, in and out of locomotives, changing them as you see fit. Couple and uncouple trains as you complete your deliveries. Choose new deliveries freely. Take many at once if you will. Service your trains after derailing. Do this all spontaneously, and at any point you can save and continue later.

Built from the ground up for Virtual Reality - optional

Derail Valley fully supports playing on a regular PC, using mouse and keyboard on a flat screen, but virtual reality is where it really shines. In VR you can, for the first time ever, truly be inside train cabs and operate controls with your own hands. Derail Valley supports all major PC VR headsets, such as Oculus, Windows Mixed Reality, Valve and HTC.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4avj.jpg', '2019-01-25', '{10,13,31,32}', 'IGDB', 94, 29564, 1, 58.99, '[{"id":147515,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":147514,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/19057.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703947.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703940.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703941.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703945.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703942.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703943.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703944.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/703946.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082993.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082994.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082995.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082996.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082997.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1082998.jpg"]', '{29348,87975,79134,109339,105011,25311,35994,65827,111130,44178}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f_XCdfc-Exk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Htm2HD91Lmk}', 'Altfuture', '0', null, null), (1024, 'Tropico 4: Modern Times', 'Tropico 4 Modern Times is the first expansion to Tropico 4. It takes place years after the main campaign of Tropico 4 and brings us into the current era.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/h9i8ixa3l6ds3jbu2p7j.jpg', '2012-03-29', '{13,15}', 'IGDB', 94, 24234, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":58622,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467152.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467154.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467157.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467159.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467139.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467141.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467143.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467144.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467146.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467149.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/467151.jpg"]', '{36346,31515,29173,55590,17519,19376,17613,17130,65827,18425}', '{}', null, '1', null, '{508}'), (1025, 'LittleBigPlanet 2: Special Edition', 'Exclusive for North America, a Special Edition of LittleBigPlanet 2 was released on November 15th 2011. This edition includes the standard edition of the game, PlayStation Move support, "Move Pack: Rise of the Cakeling" (5 new levels and 7 mini-levels), "Disney/Pixar Toy Story Level" and "Costume" packs, and "Pets Costumes" (the "Dogs", "Cats", and "Even More Animals Costume" packs). The Special Edition was also included as a pack-in game with the 2011 holiday 160GB PS3 system bundles in North America.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3kpu.jpg', '2011-11-15', '{8,9,31}', 'IGDB', 94, 21717, 1, 14.99, '[{"id":28989,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393678.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393679.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393680.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29462.jpg"]', '{77529,20342,55173,24426,55190,28070,56033,89597,105011,109581}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fSyjNMSM5Ls}', 'Media Molecule', '10', null, '{238}'), (1026, 'Dance Dance Revolution Ultramix 2', 'The second installment of Xbox exclusive DDR games.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5txe.jpg', '2004-11-18', '{7}', 'IGDB', 94, 5800, 1, 27.99, '[{"id":3179,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{63933,5801,5802,103315,43483,3891,119256,77720,15190,15177}', '{}', 'Konami', '0', null, '{602}'), (1027, 'Echo', 'When Chase decides to write a college report on a case of mass hysteria that occurred in his old home town of Echo, he uses the opportunity to get his group of childhood friends back together for the week. However, a tragedy from their past weighs heavily on their minds, and the desolate desert town finds itself on the brink of disaster once more in this atmospheric slow-burn visual novel.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2f0c.jpg', '2021-04-02', '{32,34}', 'IGDB', 93.9261313455543, 136715, 1, 69.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396108.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396109.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396110.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396111.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396112.jpg"]', '{110737,18011,19817,117139,114455,111130,27087,90107,80916,54678}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2mWnE5VZLec}', 'Echo Project', '0', null, '{6896}'), (1028, 'Europa Universalis V', 'Use war, trade or diplomacy to satisfy your grandest ambitions and dominate five centuries of history in the newest version of Europa Universalis, Paradox Interactive''s flagship historical grand strategy game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9s5c.jpg', '2025-11-04', '{15}', 'IGDB', 93.8820627547004, 342919, 1, 91.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167722.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526867.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526870.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526868.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526869.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526872.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526873.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526866.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1526871.jpg"]', '{18623,23345,30229,55590,55029,102163,3700,79134,36553,13660}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MKaGSIm9juI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nP59vpuEJx8}', 'Paradox Tinto', '0', null, '{165}'), (1029, 'Super Mario World 2: Yoshi''s Island', 'Super Mario World 2: Yoshi''s Island is a platform video game acting as a prequel to 1990''s Super Mario World. The game casts players as Yoshi as he escorts Baby Mario through 48 levels in order to reunite him with his brother Luigi, who had been kidnapped by Baby Bowser''s minions. As a Super Mario series platformer, Yoshi runs and jumps to reach the end of the level while solving puzzles and collecting items. In a style new to the series, the game has a hand-drawn aesthetic and is the first to have Yoshi as its main character. The game introduces his signature abilities to flutter jump, produce eggs from swallowed enemies, and transform into vehicles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kn9.jpg', '1995-08-05', '{8}', 'IGDB', 93.7642083070254, 1073, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":48823,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":30485,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":50801,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67920.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67916.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67917.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67918.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67922.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67915.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67914.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67919.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67921.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382877.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382874.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382876.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382875.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382878.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382880.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/382879.jpg"]', '{19150,55190,24426,56033,55173,28070,1070,36198,22387,3222}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SbIWiq1pDuw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-101mKbZ624}', 'Nintendo', '0', null, '{6128,7158,240}'), (1030, 'Star Realms', 'Star Realms is a card-based deck building science-fiction tabletop game, designed by Rob Dougherty and Darwin Kastle and published in 2014 by Wise Wizard Games. The game started out as a Kickstarter campaign in 2013. The goal of Star Realms is to destroy your opponent or opponents by purchasing cards using "trade" points and using these cards to attack your opponent''s "authority" using your "combat" points. The game takes place in a distant future where different races compete to gain resources, trade and outmaneuver each other in a race to become ruler of the galaxy.

Star Realms is similar to other deck building games, like Ascension and Dominion.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1xdw.jpg', '2014-08-13', '{15,16,35}', 'IGDB', 93.7514757818244, 21324, 1, 29.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29946.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/60613.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/60614.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/60612.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/60616.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/60615.jpg"]', '{32510,102057,13660,40477,24620,13200,13196,7615,60693,110011}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l0eOvPQncMg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fiffdmHXa5w}', 'Wise Wizard Games', '0', '{163284,163283,163279,163277,163280,163285,163287,163281,163282,163291,163290,163278,163288,163286,163289,292643}', null), (1031, 'Mystery Case Files: Dire Grove', 'Mystery Case Files: Dire Grove is an interactive movie puzzle adventure game developed by Big Fish Studios, and distributed by Big Fish Games. It is the sixth installment in the Mystery Case Files series. The game is available exclusively at Big Fish Games website. The Mystery Case Files franchise is the number one brand in casual games and has sold more than 2.5 million units to date.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5phv.jpg', '2009-11-25', '{2,9,31}', 'IGDB', 93.7349397590361, 5514, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":126959,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":126960,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":126961,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":190744,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166741.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166740.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166742.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/166743.jpg"]', '{55173,55190,56033,27266,27725,25646,25222,26223,87622,81275}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5bDL-Nrqqk}', 'Big Fish Games', '0', null, '{747}'), (1032, 'Kindred Spirits on the Roof', 'Kindred Spirits on the Roof is a Japanese adult-rated visual novel. The game is set around a shy girl named Tomi Yuna, who prefers to eat alone on the roof of her school, the Kokonotsuboshi Girl’s Academy. However, one day she finds out that the roof is haunted by the ghosts of two girls that died, before they could fully realize their love for other girls. MangaGamer is publishing the game in the west and has announced that the game will be available uncensored on Steam.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coavqo.jpg', '2016-02-12', '{13,31,34}', 'IGDB', 93.695977798099, 12151, 1, 31.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/40016.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13151.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13150.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13149.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/13152.jpg"]', '{17906,29348,79134,103232,87975,109339,25311,35994,38045,28129}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J7XNJg2lUJQ}', 'MangaGamer', '0', '{124804}', null), (1033, 'Super Mario Galaxy', 'A 3D platformer and first Wii entry in the Super Mario franchise, Super Mario Galaxy sees Mario jump across planets and galaxies with varying items, enemies, geographies and gravity mechanics in order to reach his enemy Bowser, who has attacked the Mushroom Kingdom and hijacked Princess Peach''s castle with her inside.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21ro.jpg', '2007-11-01', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 93.6914966641494, 1077, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":62694,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":191369,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":62693,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":47145,"rati