ch?v=od0ULrKzylQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4b6hcN5vZsw}', 'Guerrilla Games', '0', null, '{10104}'), (1041, 'Batman: Arkham City - Game of the Year Edition', 'Batman: Arkham City - Game of the Year Edition includes the following DLC:

Catwoman Pack
Nightwing Bundle Pack
Robin Bundle Pack
Harley Quinn’s Revenge
Challenge Map Pack
Arkham City Skins Pack

Batman: Arkham City - Game of the Year Edition packages new gameplay content, seven maps, three playable characters, and 12 skins beyond the original retail release:

Maps: Wayne Manor, Main Hall, Freight Train, Black Mask, The Joker''s Carnival, Iceberg Long, and Batcave
Playable Characters: Catwoman, Robin and Nightwing
Skins: 1970s Batsuit, Year One Batman, The Dark Knight Returns, Earth One Batman, Batman Beyond Batman, Animated Batman, Sinestro Corps Batman, Long Halloween Catwoman, Animated Catwoman, Animated Robin, Red Robin and Animated Nightwing', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kia.jpg', '2012-05-29', '{25,31}', 'IGDB', 93.5514577618896, 21704, 1, 21.99, '[{"id":29763,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":29762,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":124404,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":107145,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30594.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101907.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101908.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101909.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101910.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101911.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201894.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201895.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201896.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201897.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201898.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201890.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201891.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201892.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201893.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201899.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201900.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201901.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201902.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201903.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1201904.jpg"]', '{19164,81249,103168,26574,103054,115283,118218,111130,19564,17548}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=944Ty9YpjEs}', 'Warner Bros. Entertainment Inc.', '3', null, null), (1042, 'SOCOM II: U.S. Navy SEALs', 'SOCOM II is a third-person tactical shooter. There are 12 different single-player missions: split equally between Albania, Algeria, Brazil and Russia. There are five different ranks that can be played in the game: Ensign, Lieutenant, Commander, Captain and Admiral. The player starts with the first three ranks unlocked, but must finish the single player game on Commander to unlock Captain, and on Captain to unlock Admiral. Players can unlock new models for multiplayer, as well as movies, music, concept art, and credits by completing certain objectives.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co99jv.jpg', '2003-11-04', '{5,13,15,24}', 'IGDB', 93.5360753565891, 8240, 1, 27.99, '[{"id":76985,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":192259,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":168210,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":192256,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192257,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192258,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118919.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118920.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118921.jpg"]', '{1294,8241,9495,8422,908,1842,8744,15536,277,10964}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s78E4iZU3yU}', 'Zipper Interactive', '0', null, '{1005}'), (1043, 'Panzer General', 'You are the brightest and best of the new Axis generals in the Second World War. Your tactical skills will be tested in armored assaults, amphibious invasions, paradrops, naval engagements, and fierce aerial combat for control of the skies. Go from triumph to triumph, invading and seizing the capitals of Great Britain, the Soviet Union, and ultimately the United States of America on your way to conquering the whole world! Can you achieve a place in history?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5pbv.jpg', '1994-12-01', '{15}', 'IGDB', 93.530530240394, 4268, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":2499,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148968.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148973.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148965.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148966.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148967.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148970.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148975.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148971.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148974.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148969.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148972.jpg"]', '{77597,17613,112754,36346,65827,111043,76340,24620,36269,95340}', '{}', null, '0', null, '{1829}'), (1044, 'World of Warcraft: Wrath of the Lich King', 'World of Warcraft: Wrath of the Lich King, often referred to as WotLK, or Wrath, is the second expansion set for the massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) World of Warcraft, following The Burning Crusade. It adds a substantial amount of content to the game world, including the continent of Northrend, home of the eponymous Lich King, and a new character "hero" class.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1xv9.jpg', '2008-11-13', '{12}', 'IGDB', 93.5209161662072, 228, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":29549,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":189831,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1584.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1579.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1577.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1580.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1581.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1578.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1583.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1582.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1586.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1576.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1575.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1585.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/243616.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396793.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396796.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396800.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396801.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396802.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396792.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26719.jpg"]', '{115653,19164,81249,17548,37382,19404,23651,106987,54775,49414}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=95vcgv-pK_4}', 'Blizzard Entertainment', '2', null, '{27}'), (1045, 'A Twisted Path To Renown', 'A Twisted Path To Renown: is a Multiplayer, loot-focused, PvEvP extraction shooter, set in the rugged 1899 United States!
Strap on your holster, assemble a posse, and get ready for a rootin''-tooting good time!
Roam the savage lands of the United States during the 1890s and live out your Western dream!
Fight against vicious bandits, or become one yourself as you loot and pillage from the Hills of Tennessee to the Pine forests of Arizona. Fight various factions in an unforgiving land for fame, and fortune!
Stay alert for ferocious wild boars, and bandits who will tan your hide for a chance to steal your precious loot!
Evade the resourceful and cunning Indigenous Peoples of early America to fight another day or attack against all odds for your chance at Legend!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7d0t.jpg', '2024-12-17', '{5,12,13}', 'IGDB', 93.5070325109523, 275923, 1, 73.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/133257.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187603.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187604.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187605.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187606.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187607.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187608.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187609.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187610.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187611.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187612.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187613.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187614.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207220.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207221.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207223.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207224.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207225.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207226.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1207227.jpg"]', '{15536,17379,8422,26574,9243,10776,44076,105049,19564,68287}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0tv6TB3GsSs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8THpS5Lf8ug,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AL0L1hQ5DMY}', 'Game Labs', '0', null, null), (1046, 'Space Station 13', 'Space Station 13 (ss13) is a multiplayer role-playing game. Originally created by one person named Exadv1, development has been continued by members of the fan base.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1of6.jpg', '2003-02-16', '{12,13,32}', 'IGDB', 93.491992694674, 66396, 1, 18.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1182133.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1182131.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1182132.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1182134.jpg"]', '{25311,37419,26574,105269,34823,111187,35994,105011,107318,107169}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nLAHBexJxrE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5THvMMgNNjc}', null, '0', null, null), (1047, 'Jungles of Maxtheria', 'Play as either "Hot Spot" Harvey, his cousin Roxy Roks, Junior or Missy searching for the lost treasure of the infamous "Jaxton Max". Your quest for fortune and glory will not be easy however. This adventure is full of baddies aimed at stopping you dead in your tracks. Use knives to dig through walls, bullets to battle the baddies, grappling hooks to jump over long distances, oxygen tanks to breath under water and torches to see what lurks underground. Collect keys to get past locked doors and to open treasure chests. Avoid the quicksand, tar pits, spikes, fire pits, thumpers and other traps along the way. Few ever return from their expeditions into the deep jungles. So, if you are brave enough, the "Jungles of Maxtheria" awaits!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2i39.jpg', '2020-10-14', '{8,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93.4772182254197, 139403, 1, 58.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/64435.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/402501.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/402502.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/402499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/402500.jpg"]', '{111130,20342,55173,24426,106987,28070,55190,28309,56033,89597}', '{}', 'SlifkerGames', '0', null, null), (1048, 'Mass Effect 2', 'Are you prepared to lose everything to save the galaxy? You''ll need to be, Commander Shephard. It''s time to bring together your greatest allies and recruit the galaxy''s fighting elite to continue the resistance against the invading Reapers. So steel yourself, because this is an astronomical mission where sacrifices must be made. You''ll face tougher choices and new, deadlier enemies. Arm yourself and prepare for an unforgettable intergalactic adventure.

Game Features:

Shift the fight in your favour. Equip yourself with powerful new weapons almost instantly thanks to a new inventory system. Plus, an improved health regeneration system means you''ll spend less time hunting for restorative items.

Make every decision matter. Divisive crew members are just the tip of the iceberg, Commander, because you''ll also be tasked with issues of intergalactic diplomacy. And time''s a wastin'' so don''t be afraid to use new prompt-based actions that let you interrupt conversations, even if they could alter the fate of your crew...and the galaxy.

Forge new alliances, carefully. You''ll fight alongside some of your most trustworthy crew members, but you''ll also get the opportunity to recruit new talent. Just choose your new partners with care because the fate of the galaxy rests on your shoulders, Commander.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co20ac.jpg', '2010-01-26', '{5,12,31}', 'IGDB', 93.4768764355249, 74, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":105829,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":212490,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":105831,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":111311,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":105830,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":79400,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":188421,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168562.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168563.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168561.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168566.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168559.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4522.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6508.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168564.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4519.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4514.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4513.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4512.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168560.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/893.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8206.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8218.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/892.jpg"]', '{2031,1020,16,533,43,20,127,960,1985,116}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ugq9Iv7tFVc}', 'Electronic Arts', '0', '{13794,202312,13798,13790,13885,202310,782,202311,783}', '{25}'), (1049, 'Mortal Kombat 11: Ultimate', 'The definitive MK11 experience! Take control of Earthrealm''s protectors in the game''s TWO critically acclaimed, time-bending Story Campaigns as they race to stop Kronika from rewinding time and rebooting history. Friendships are tested, and new alliances forged, in the battle to save all of existence. MK11 Ultimate features the komplete 37-character roster, including new additions Rain, Mileena & Rambo.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kh5.jpg', '2020-11-17', '{4}', 'IGDB', 93.4375020566848, 139446, 1, 70.99, '[{"id":110819,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":110820,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":106285,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":125107,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46925.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46927.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/408497.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/408498.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/408499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/408500.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/408501.jpg"]', '{89550,103269,109277,76852,113895,101608,100800,114145,57296,103288}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WveIrH4efjg}', 'Shiver Entertainment', '3', null, null), (1050, 'Enigma of Fear', 'Become Mia, a paranormal detective searching for her missing father inside the Perimeter - a place that doesn''t exist. Investigate clues like a real detective and unravel the mysteries behind the Enigma of Fear, defeating the terrible monsters who''ll try to stop you.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co93ft.jpg', '2024-11-28', '{9,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93.408168332142, 140133, 1, 73.99, '[{"id":192767,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/148149.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818703.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818702.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818701.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818700.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818699.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818705.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/818704.jpg"]', '{25646,111130,11668,56033,26658,25222,114455,27266,120201,115304}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OvibI1wQZAA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wr5xLwBOirA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dtqm-m33KYo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hjl6usm5WCo}', 'Dumativa Game Studio', '0', null, null), (1051, 'Pokémon Unbound', 'Pokémon Unbound is a fan-made ROM hack of Pokémon FireRed that offers an enriched and modernized Pokémon experience. Set in the Borrius region—a land with a tumultuous history marked by a past war with the Kalos region—the game follows your journey to prevent the resurgence of a sealed dark force that once threatened the land.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob5bs.jpg', '2020-12-01', '{12,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93.4049389091284, 141663, 1, 50.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414002.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414003.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414004.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/801246.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/801247.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1157987.jpg"]', '{106987,96217,55038,25311,105269,107318,24426,28070,47823,28309}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQFfYti6B-c,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g_oXu357YN4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hXOZpEmAztA}', 'Skeli', '5', null, null), (1052, 'Grand Theft Auto V: Premium Online Edition', 'The Grand Theft Auto V: Premium Online Edition includes the complete Grand Theft Auto V story experience, free access to the ever-evolving Grand Theft Auto Online and all existing gameplay upgrades and content, including The Doomsday Heist, Gunrunning, Smuggler’s Run, Bikers and much more. Players also get the Criminal Enterprise Starter Pack, the fastest way to jumpstart their criminal empire in Grand Theft Auto Online.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1twh.jpg', '2018-04-20', '{5,10,31}', 'IGDB', 93.3925790703405, 98077, 1, 57.99, '[{"id":191460,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":130355,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":94459,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":104929,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/344194.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/344193.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/344196.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/344197.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/344195.jpg"]', '{19164,105011,10776,47823,19561,17379,19249,26574,17548,18290}', '{}', 'Rockstar Games', '3', null, null), (1053, 'Project M', 'Project M is a community-made mod of Brawl inspired by Super Smash Bros. Melee''s gameplay designed to add rich, technical gameplay to a balanced cast of characters while additionally enhancing the speed of play. Project M employs new codes which seamlessly add in new, universal features to the entire cast to add technical variety to all characters.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3z39.jpg', '2013-12-09', '{4,8}', 'IGDB', 93.3362519189679, 127155, 1, 11.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172672.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401949.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401950.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401951.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401952.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401953.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401954.jpg"]', '{96452,89550,112138,101608,20342,55173,24426,28070,55190,56033}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIxskj3UFV0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HFSW_Zq-Xyg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rcJHZCuaG84}', 'Project M Development Team', '5', null, null), (1054, 'Escape Simulator', 'Escape Simulator is a next-gen escape room experience: pick up and examine everything, move furniture, smash pots and melt locks! Play solo or with a friend to solve cryptic puzzles and riddles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co49cc.jpg', '2021-10-19', '{2,9,13,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93.3320400613141, 145439, 1, 76.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/63325.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429923.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429924.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429922.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429925.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429926.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429927.jpg"]', '{81275,18011,27725,25222,26223,54678,29348,13189,27266,25646}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ruCs99We82I}', 'Pine Studio', '0', '{261137,321346,321345,221903,365719,202457,306583,280413,293464}', '{10971}'), (1055, 'Town Star', 'Gala Games'' Town Star, a new game from the creative minds behind Farmville by Zynga, is a masterpiece of town-building, organization and time management.

Through the course of each competitive game, players build towns from scratch by placing buildings such as farms, ranches, production facilities, even power plants. By managing the automatic flow of their town''s workers, players are able to farm resources that are refined into goods, which are then crafted into commodities by buildings of increasing cost and workers of increasing specialty. By delivering goods to neighboring cities and cooperating with neighboring towns, players are able to earn money to continue development and stars, which determine the ultimate winner of each Town Star game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2wwf.jpg', '2020-02-26', '{13}', 'IGDB', 93.3164128595601, 145327, 1, 72.99, '[{"id":188878,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":34311,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429409.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429410.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/429411.jpg"]', '{37419,51577,117717,34823,111187,26574,105011,101573,55689,17613}', '{}', 'Gala Games', '0', null, null), (1056, 'The Legend of Sword and Fairy', 'The Legend of Sword and Fairy is a role-playing video game developed by the Taiwanese company Softstar Entertainment and its subsidiaries. The game incorporates elements of wuxia, shenmo and fantasy. Since its release in 1995, the game has spawned a successful video game franchise in Taiwan and mainland China. It was also adapted into the 2005 Chinese television series Chinese Paladin.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co57ln.jpg', '1995-07-07', '{12}', 'IGDB', 93.3137721118778, 18928, 1, 22.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/51434.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/602222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104502.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104503.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104504.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104506.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104507.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104508.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1450051.jpg"]', '{5867,10297,22387,19404,96217,106987,115653,54775,7027,19164}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=si0Qyj0WMu8}', 'Softstar', '0', null, '{69}'), (1057, 'Metal Gear Solid: The Legacy Collection', 'Metal Gear Solid: The Legacy Collection is a video game compilation released exclusively for the PlayStation 3. It includes all the mainline Metal Gear games directed and designed by Hideo Kojima (including the VR Missions standalone expansion) that were released from 1987 through 2012. Bonus content include motion comic adaptations of the Metal Gear Solid graphic novels by Kris Oprisko and Ashley Wood and a 100-page booklet that catalogs numerous promotional posters, brochures and advertisement related to the games in the compilation.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co45jf.jpg', '2013-07-09', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 93.2565753021355, 20196, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":69012,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":47728,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":47727,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/846416.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/846417.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/846418.jpg"]', '{106805,87622,55038,105269,118218,19164,107318,103301,103210,76877}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5RZq7rD-gk}', 'Konami', '3', null, null), (1058, 'Pokémon Pokopia', 'Pokémon’s first life simulation game, Pokémon Pokopia, will release on Nintendo Switch 2 on March 5, 2026. Playing as a Ditto that has transformed to look like a human, you can collect wood, rocks, and other crafting materials to create a cozy home. Ditto can learn moves from other Pokémon and utilize those moves to help build your very own Pokémon paradise. For example, Ditto can use Bulbasaur’s Leafage to add greenery to the landscape or Squirtle’s Water Gun to hydrate plants. By creating a lush, welcoming environment, more Pokémon will visit.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobbur.jpg', '2026-03-05', '{13,31}', 'IGDB', 93.2145958374221, 366893, 1, 80.99, '[{"id":227670,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":227671,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":227672,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":224448,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":226229,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":230308,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":232324,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/196274.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257316.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/263027.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1638016.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1638017.jpg"]', '{105011,26574,106279,29348,37419,17379,10776,79134,103232,51577}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6_bYri9p1Uk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rR_4nsCu-IA}', 'Omega Force', '0', null, '{314}'), (1059, 'Persona 5', 'Persona 5, a turn-based JRPG with visual novel elements, follows a high school student with a criminal record for a crime he didn''t commit. Soon he meets several characters who share similar fates to him, and discovers a metaphysical realm which allows him and his friends to channel their pent-up frustrations into becoming a group of vigilantes reveling in aesthetics and rebellion while fighting corruption.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1r76.jpg', '2016-09-15', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 93.0913394683049, 9927, 1, 39.99, '[{"id":162741,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":162777,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":162765,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":23140,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":77585,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":192338,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":190474,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3800.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3801.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6095.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6096.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219064.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219065.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15665.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15666.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15663.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15664.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15662.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007801.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010681.jpg"]', '{9600,7276,6452,11292,11156,26845,12517,9577,7346,481}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w9MAhxxrNFk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0_tkyNFh8-4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oc_9r4wifFc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q9qVO4khoo0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VcQGMdqMoAc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Y5U8n4Ie3I,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oCWKcEsIedo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qKZtJmt85ns,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjSHjAoQty4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qlqkipD0TCk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d6EvCpSML3I,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tRLsHzCMEE4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0jm8nnHqx80}', 'Atlus', '0', null, '{552,9216}'), (1060, 'Superfighters Deluxe', 'Superfighters Deluxe is a multiplayer 2D action game where little flat-headed men fight to the death in small and highly destructible arenas. Surviving each round takes skill, strategy and luck.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1r61.jpg', '2018-11-30', '{4,5,8,32}', 'IGDB', 93.0062126158989, 10039, 1, 34.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25705.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9695.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9696.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9697.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302392.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302393.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302394.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302395.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302396.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302397.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1302398.jpg"]', '{32902,113895,43367,105269,107318,20342,55173,24426,111130,102868}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7VNsb78v7Kc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9YtiRsJWx6w,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SiVkuNoG-4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HN41_i6E5CI}', 'MythoLogic Interactive', '10', null, '{1344}'), (1061, 'Cult of the Lamb: Woolhaven', 'A lost God calls you from a mysterious mountain—rebuild the flock and reawaken winter to uncover the truth of the fallen lambs. Face the past before it consumes you in this full-length expansion for Cult of the Lamb.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coab02.jpg', '2026-01-22', '{15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93, 361888, 1, 85.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/188382.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/188383.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615283.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615279.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615280.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615281.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615282.jpg"]', '{111130,25311,35994,28182,106987,28309,113895,113402,25646,96217}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JziX-60OyCc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EehS0AGcLkc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FjpiHuwNxx4}', 'Massive Monster', '2', null, null), (1062, 'Palia: The Elderwood', 'Welcome to the Elderwood! Step into an ancient overgrown forest teeming with magic in the Elderwood Expansion — Palia’s biggest update to date! Explore the new Adventure Zone and discover powerful artifacts and relics, complete exciting new quests, meet mischievous (but cute!) critters, find loads of new collectibles, decor, and so much more!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9zqi.jpg', '2025-05-13', '{12,13,31}', 'IGDB', 93, 348035, 1, 89.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563744.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563745.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563746.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563747.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563748.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563749.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1563750.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1553489.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1553490.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1553491.jpg"]', '{81249,26574,103303,19164,17548,106987,37419,96217,47823,115653}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3hQMyYoXIxs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c6mCmzLZ2fU}', 'Singularity 6', '14', null, null), (1063, 'Kingdom Two Crowns: Norse Lands', 'Inspired by Norse Viking culture, Norse Lands is an all-new campaign setting expanding the world of Kingdom Two Crowns to explore and conquer. Unleash abilities drawn upon from the Norse gods, command mighty units, build Viking inspired armaments, solve puzzles, take on new Greed, and much more…', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3yvk.jpg', '2021-11-15', '{13,15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93, 175663, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":124272,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":134712,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":107495,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":124271,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":121280,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":134713,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/54538.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/660198.jpg"]', '{79134,109339,65827,25311,35994,19404,36269,31515,29348,87975}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g6HUD0E8XWo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tx0nlm-9zyo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8JpY81paH3U}', 'Raw Fury', '1', null, null), (1064, 'Slime Rancher: Plortable Edition', 'Slime Rancher is a charming, first-person, sandbox experience. Play as Beatrix LeBeau: a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the ‘Far, Far Range.’ Each day will present new challenges and risky opportunities as you attempt to amass a great fortune in the business of slime ranching. Collect colourful slimes, grow crops, harvest resources, and explore the untamed wilds through the mastery of your all-purpose vacpack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4yk9.jpg', '2021-08-11', '{13,31,32}', 'IGDB', 93, 163631, 1, 70.99, '[{"id":44796,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":78002,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":118001,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46021.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582300.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582301.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582302.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582303.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582304.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/582305.jpg"]', '{25311,26574,37419,11737,16287,105269,25300,35994,105011,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sHf_r-QHdM4}', 'Monomi Park', '11', null, '{7097}'), (1065, 'Sega Ages Virtua Racing', 'Take control of a formula one racing car and compete against the world’s best drivers in the first faithful reproduction of the arcade classic. Choose between the Normal Race mode that features four-to-five lap races, or put your endurance to the test by completing 20 laps in the Grand Prix Race. Your car’s performance is affected the longer you drive, so make sure you plan your pit stop strategy carefully so you can take the checkered flag!

Although Virtua Racing has been released on many different platforms before, this version of the game is a faithful implementation of the original arcade game released in 1992.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3un4.jpg', '2019-04-25', '{10,14,33}', 'IGDB', 93, 110062, 1, 40.99, '[{"id":24972,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":24973,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":95974,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/14303.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305384.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305382.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305380.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305378.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305379.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305381.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305377.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/305383.jpg"]', '{118871,15851,121036,119207,27378,120795,87728,43367,23314,47161}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g6v0sM-Clnk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Pd_GxVSS2o}', 'Sega of America', '11', null, '{5016}'), (1066, 'Chameleon Run: Deluxe Edition', 'Deluxe Edition features a handful of new courses, and even a fourth additional challenge to complete for each level.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co28wf.jpg', '2018-06-14', '{8,10,32,33}', 'IGDB', 93, 103198, 1, 59.99, '[{"id":39849,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":60852,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/16790.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214294.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214293.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214295.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214292.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/