Let’s enjoy the history of Psikyo and shooting game NOW!!!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/beoneo39u2b6ahda0xvz.jpg', '2018-02-15', '{5,33}', 'IGDB', 93, 86647, 1, 34.99, '[{"id":60685,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":119669,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":117797,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":99771,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/70582.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184374.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184372.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184373.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193037.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193038.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193036.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193034.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193040.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193039.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/193035.jpg"]', '{22799,43367,55038,105269,68286,107318,103301,121532,111846,113362}', '{}', 'ZeroDiv', '11', null, '{4814}'), (1069, 'Giana Sisters DS', 'Giana Sisters DS is a classic platformer. Giana is caught in a dream world and must now recover her lost diamonds and find a way to the mysterious castle. The game features more than 80 new levels (i.e. is not a one-to-one remake). There are also new special items that make use of the features of the DS. Giana can, for example, collect a bubble gum item that can be activated using the touch screen. The bubble enables Giana to fly and is controlled by blowing into the microphone. Another new feature is a world map that allows the player to select and replay levels.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ogx.jpg', '2009-04-03', '{8}', 'IGDB', 93, 80236, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":186705,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":64096,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":186703,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":186704,"rating_category":{"id":18,"rating":"0"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160126.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160131.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160130.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160132.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160129.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160127.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160133.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/160128.jpg"]', '{42842,55752,1191,125673,119199,19917,120184,395612,395163,393933}', '{}', 'Destineer', '0', null, '{565}'), (1070, 'Super Robot Taisen OG Saga: Masou Kishin - The Lord of Elemental', 'A remake of the original Masou Kishin game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co72fx.jpg', '2010-05-27', '{15}', 'IGDB', 93, 79343, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":128528,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{24620,13200,77597,34823,86558,13660,111187,102057,25311,8714}', '{}', 'Namco Bandai Games', '8', null, '{8657}'), (1071, 'KORG Gadget', 'Play Games. Make Music.
A Music Creation Studio That Feels Like a Game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kwn.jpg', '2018-04-26', '{7,13}', 'IGDB', 93, 77537, 1, 46.99, '[{"id":60820,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":31603,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12395.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212204.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212206.jpg"]', '{63933,87017,119207,101573,103315,119256,32688,17613,86847,36346}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cF3Wd4-tvRI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bnEVlQ4xolA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ogzCYOZ2z4Y}', 'Detune', '0', null, null), (1072, 'Petit Novel Series: Harvest December', 'A collection of all thirteen chapters from the Harvest December series of episodic visual novels for the Nintendo 3DS.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6ikq.jpg', '2015-12-10', '{31,34}', 'IGDB', 93, 59433, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":60514,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":40939,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/70506.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168498.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168500.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168497.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168501.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168502.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168504.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168503.jpg"]', '{19164,87622,111130,55984,103266,106987,62151,28309,96217,11458}', '{}', 'CIRCLE Entertainment', '0', null, '{3228}'), (1073, 'Star Trek: Rivals', 'Warp into the future of card battle games.A highly addictive, strategic, and FREE collectible card game featuring the characters and ships from Star Trek and Star Trek Into Darkness.TOP FEATURES * Easy to learn, difficult to master gameplay * Over 100 cards based on characters, aliens, and starships * Challenge friends or random rivals in turn-based card battles * Earn Federation Credits to buy packs of new cards * Collect XP to increase your level and earn gold-pressed Latinum rewards * Upgrade cards to stronger "Elite" versions Do you have what it takes to become the best in the galaxy?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7yni.jpg', '2013-05-16', '{15,35}', 'IGDB', 93, 24551, 1, 25.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/346668.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/346667.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/346669.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/346671.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/346670.jpg"]', '{32510,77597,17613,68045,112754,36346,65827,136558,24620,19404}', '{}', 'Elephant Mouse LLC', '0', null, null), (1075, 'Heroes of Might and Magic III: Complete', 'This compilation contains:

- Heroes of Might and Magic III: The Restoration of Erathia (base game)
- Heroes of Might and Magic III: Armageddon''s Blade (add-on)
- Heroes of Might and Magic III: The Shadow of Death (add-on)

When Erathia''s King Gryphonheart is murdered by traitors he is resurrected as an undead warlord who leads a ruthless invasion of his former Kingdom. Little resistance is met until his daughter Catherine, Queen of Enroth, returns to her homeland commanding an army of elite Enrothian warriors. Meanwhile the Necromancers raise large hordes of undead and advance towards the Erathian capitol. Queen Catherine receives the aid of her father''s survived generals and embarks on a crusade to reclaim her lost land.

You control the greatest heroes and fiercest creatures in a conflict of epic proportions, as Cathereine fights to restore her family''s rightful reign, uncover her father''s killers and free him from the dark prison of his undead body!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co218t.jpg', '2000-10-02', '{12,15,16}', 'IGDB', 92.9853834718498, 51820, 1, 9.99, '[{"id":94602,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":123556,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":104773,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":104776,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":131448,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":104775,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":107205,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/10559.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/416559.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/416558.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/416557.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/422408.jpg"]', '{13196,7615,19404,26845,9472,115653,112191,93694,111187,27092}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qVeBw3S020E}', 'The 3DO Company', '3', null, '{194}'), (1076, 'Super Bomberman 5', 'An evil Bomber named Emperor Terrorin who has the power of Time itself has freed various criminal Bombers from their prison cells in orbit around Planet Bomber. Setting them up in a warped time and space, Shirobon, Kurobon, and their Louie (Rui) companions must travel through stages and defeat them before going up against Emperor Terrorin himself. Super Bomberman 5, released by Hudson Soft in early 1997, was the final Bomberman game released on the Super Family Computer - the Japanese version of the SNES. The game was released in two variations: a standard cartridge and a gold cartridge, which was sold exclusively through CoroCoro Comic. The gold cartridge included extra maps in battle mode.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2w8i.jpg', '1997-02-28', '{9,15,24,33}', 'IGDB', 92.9506770192254, 38387, 1, 24.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/404498.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/404499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/404500.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/404501.jpg"]', '{56033,25905,90788,95340,25640,25646,19549,78550,34024,119156}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CufHKUo1V5s,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FXUMQK4OTnE}', 'Hudson Soft', '0', null, '{6848}'), (1077, 'Neko Atsume: Kitty Collector', 'Attract cats with food and then watch them romp with your toys! More than 40 varieties of cats—white and black, tabby and calico—might stop by. Rare cats are rumored to roam the neighborhood too, but you''ll need particular items to entice those elusive felines. Each visitor is logged in your Catbook. Become a master kitty collector and fill it up!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8y7t.jpg', '2014-10-20', '{2,13,32}', 'IGDB', 92.9045886892875, 15699, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":97497,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/90877.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/19354.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35975.jpg"]', '{37419,51577,34823,26574,65827,31515,36269,29348,18623,13189}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5CcOX1PPjow}', 'Hit-Point', '0', null, '{11470}'), (1078, 'Super Mario Odyssey', 'Explore incredible places far from the Mushroom Kingdom as you join Mario and his new ally Cappy on a massive, globe-trotting 3D adventure. Use amazing new abilities, like the power to capture and control objects, animals, and enemies to collect Power Moons so you can power up the Odyssey airship and save Princess Peach from Bowser’s wedding plans!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1mxf.jpg', '2017-10-27', '{8,31}', 'I