ion of Yoshi, new power-ups like the Cloud Flower, and the use of a guide within the game for beginner players.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21tl.jpg', '2010-05-23', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 92.7478929497266, 1078, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":220121,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":36446,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":47146,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":197002,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":197001,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":197003,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":98144,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6188.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195329.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195330.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195331.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195332.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195333.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195334.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/195335.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/258153.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383730.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383731.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383732.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383729.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383734.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383728.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383733.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383735.jpg"]', '{358,3349,2180,843,1075,1068,26758,1036,1029,1074}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Hu8lGw7RE0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5t3fV6ELNk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O7steQttNTo}', 'Nintendo', '0', null, '{240,6083}'), (1089, 'Mario & Luigi: Bowser''s Inside Story', 'Mario & Luigi: Bowser''s Inside Story is the third game in the Mario & Luigi series of games. Players control Mario and Luigi simultaneously in the side-scrolling platform environment of Bowser''s body, while also controlling the Koopa King himself in the top-down world of the Mushroom Kingdom. Similar to games like Earthbound, enemy encounters are seen as actual enemies that players can avoid or attempt to strike early. The actual battles are a combination of turn-based menu attacks, and timed reactions to enemies during battle. By watching the way an enemy reacts, you can anticipate their attack and avoid it or counterattack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21vr.jpg', '2009-02-11', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 92.719751920536, 3363, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":178932,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":166838,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":59614,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":47112,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":178929,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":178931,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":178930,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/27670.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164306.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164308.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164309.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164307.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164310.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164313.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164312.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/164311.jpg"]', '{3349,1078,3365,22387,19164,843,3351,533,3364,551}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6IzLzfXCZZM}', 'AlphaDream', '0', null, '{595}'), (1090, 'Medieval II: Total War - Gold Edition', 'Medieval II: Total War - Gold Edition is the compilation of the critically-acclaimed Medieval: Total War and its official expansion pack - Total War Kingdoms. Set in the turbulent Middle Ages, Medieval puts you in command of your own empire as you crush neighboring kingdoms and unify all of Europe, the Mediterranean, and the Middle East. Medieval: Total War Kingdoms features four entire campaigns centered on expanded maps of the British Isles, Teutonic Northern Europe, the Middle East, and the Americas. In Medieval II, you were only given a glimpse of South America, but in Kingdoms, vast tracts of land in both North and South America have been opened up for you to conquer.

All-new factions from the New World are also now fully playable, including the Aztecs, Apaches, and Mayans. In both games, you rule all aspects of your kingdom throughout centuries of medieval warfare. Lay siege to mighty fortresses and command vast armies across the battlefields of Europe and North Africa. This is Total War.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8hm8.jpg', '2007-08-28', '{11,13,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 92.7144085451945, 28983, 1, 22.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130220.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130219.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130218.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130221.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130222.jpg"]', '{36258,13196,102057,6985,10243,18623,31480,23345,107233,55590}', '{}', null, '0', null, '{48}'), (1091, 'Kingdom Come: Deliverance II', 'A thrilling story-driven action RPG, with a rich open world, set in 15th century Medieval Europe. Experience the ultimate medieval adventure - through the eyes of young Henry - as you embark on a journey of epic proportions.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8qmv.jpg', '2025-02-04', '{12,13,31}', 'IGDB', 92.7084609155447, 298526, 1, 89.99, '[{"id":226572,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":211377,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":198848,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":184619,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":198852,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":198850,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":198851,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176600.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176601.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/229125.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1308439.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/