-8QKDA}', 'Wube Software', '2', null, null), (1143, 'Xenotilt: Hostile Pinball Action', 'Lightning strikes again!! Xenotilt, the sequel to the cult hit, Demon''s Tilt. Get ready for another pinball fantasy. Xenotilt shreds the envelope with face-melting gameplay & graphics.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob7rt.jpg', '2024-11-12', '{5,13,30,32,33}', 'IGDB', 92, 233872, 1, 60.99, '[{"id":221222,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":224068,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":164050,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":164052,"rating_category":{"id":18,"rating":"0"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/97779.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970285.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970287.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970288.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970289.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970290.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970291.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/970292.jpg"]', '{25311,105269,43367,107318,37419,13200,55038,36553,35994,22799}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5IDcREDLlR4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b0n02n7K88U}', 'FLARB', '0', null, null), (1144, 'Unbeatable', 'Unbeatable is a rhythm-adventure game where music is illegal, and you do crimes. talk your way through trouble as you explore vibrant locales. Fight your way through exciting arcade-perfect rhythm setpieces, featuring an original soundtrack by Peak Divide.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9ozh.jpg', '2025-12-09', '{7,31,32}', 'IGDB', 92, 144859, 1, 94.99, '[{"id":222882,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/10205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/10241.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615907.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615908.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615909.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615910.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615911.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615912.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615913.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615914.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615915.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1615916.jpg"]', '{111130,106987,96217,28309,25646,80916,25311,105269,35994,30245}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j-xFczhoZb8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p67Lh63hrnA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xWNwFSNFw74,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cVNCSgLIlH4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tj3Wt6iaOYs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5L3czAXxhtI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vkvi71znX_Q}', 'D-CELL GAMES', '0', null, null), (1145, 'Orion Sandbox Enhanced', 'This is a 2D crafting survival sandbox game. You will be able to explore a huge 2D side-view world, building houses, crafting tools, weapons and armour from the resources you collect. There is a day/night cycle and each night many dangerous monsters can be found and defeated.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobpo2.jpg', '2018-09-21', '{12,31,32}', 'IGDB', 92, 109848, 1, 45.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/206393.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215585.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215586.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215587.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215588.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/227676.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/227677.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253791.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253790.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253793.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253796.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/253792.jpg"]', '{106987,28309,96217,80916,30245,105269,111130,25311,107318,35994}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1146, 'Rento Fortune Monolit', 'Rento is online multiplayer business dice game. Trade lands, build houses, win auctions, roll wheel of fortune, risk in Russian Roulette and most importantly - have fun.
Obtain monopoly over the game board and bankrupt the other players in order to win.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co30mm.jpg', '2017-07-14', '{15,32,35}', 'IGDB', 92, 105624, 1, 30.99, '[{"id":60899,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":97371,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":36466,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25500.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220422.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220425.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220423.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220424.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220420.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220421.jpg"]', '{29173,55888,19083,65827,35463,19404,31515,36269,18623,23345}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_fEpzMdkPUw}', 'LAN Games EOOD', '0', '{170741,298335}', null), (1147, 'Dragon Warrior Monsters 2: Tara''s Adventure & Cobi''s Journey', 'Join Tara or Cobi on their gigantic adventure!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobuwj.jpg', '2001-03-09', null, 'IGDB', 92, 85643, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157403.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157404.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157402.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157406.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157408.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157407.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157413.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157405.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157409.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157412.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157410.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/157411.jpg"]', null, '{}', 'Square Enix', '0', null, null), (1148, 'DCS World: A-10C Warthog', '"DCS World: A-10C Warthog" is a PC simulation of the U.S. premier Close Air Support attack aircraft. This is the second aircraft in the DCS series, following DCS: Black Shark, and raises the bar even higher in the DCS series. Warthog brings the most realistic PC simulation of a modern fixed wing combat aircraft in regards to flight dynamics, avionics, sensors, and weapon systems. You also have the option to play Warthog in "Game" mode for a casual game experience. Fly missions in the Caucasus region of the Black Sea against and with a wide array of air, land and sea forces with new and improved intelligence. Create your own missions and campaigns with the included Mission and Campaign Editors, and fly with and against friends online using the included online game browser.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co95nd.jpg', '2011-05-22', '{13}', 'IGDB', 92, 22649, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30336.jpg"]', '{8422,28751,58075,72715,68286,15536,65434,14758,76457,60270}', '{}', null, '1', null, '{3416}'), (1149, 'Need for Speed: Hot Pursuit - Limited Edition', 'The Need for Speed Hot Pursuit Limited Edition delivers six exotic cars; Alfa Romeo 8C Competizione, Ford Shelby GT500, Audi TT RS Coupé, Chevrolet Camaro SS, Porsche Cayman S and Dodge Challenger SRT8. The Alfa Romeo 8C Competizione and Ford Shelby GT500 are only available in the Limited Edition – and will not be available at any other time.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2h9t.jpg', '2010-11-16', '{10}', 'IGDB', 92, 21696, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":90306,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29479.jpg"]', '{118871,113895,172601,15229,2635,109292,103218,110411,114286,120487}', '{}', 'Criterion Games', '0', null, '{12}'), (1150, 'Triple Play 98', 'Triple Play 98 features all 30 major league stadiums, but not all 30 team rosters. This game was released prior to the expansion draft of the Arizona Diamondbacks and Tampa Bay Devil Rays. Their team logos are included and the rosters can be filled from a list of free agents. 
 
Six modes of play include: exhibition, season, playoffs, home run derby, all-star, and practice. Trading players and the ability to create your own are two available options. 
 
Many stats are tracked through season play and plenty of camera angles are available during gameplay. Play by play is provided with color commentary by announcers Jim Hughson and Buck Martinez. 
 
Triple Play 98 requires one to five memory card blocks to save a game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/xirtahqnqzxocuowguk6.jpg', '1997-05-30', '{13,14}', 'IGDB', 92, 20813, 1, 17.99, '[{"id":19642,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{119422,23464,20649,3621,44924,6241,118871,100359,116353,114285}', '{}', null, '0', null, '{2270}'), (1151, 'Carnage Heart', 'Carnage Heart is a video game for the PlayStation, developed by Artdink. Its gameplay is a mecha-based, turn-based strategy game, where the player takes the role of a commander in a war fought by robots. The robots, called Overkill Engines (OKEs), cannot be directly controlled in battle; they must be programmed beforehand to behave in a certain way under certain conditions using a flow diagram system.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4ql6.jpg', '1995-12-08', '{15}', 'IGDB', 92, 20733, 1, 27.99, '[{"id":227292,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":227293,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":60211,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233701.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233702.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233703.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233704.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233705.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/269936.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/269937.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/269939.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/269938.jpg"]', '{24620,13200,25311,34823,111187,102057,17130,13660,11666,16806}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=biKhBlCBrXY}', 'Sony Computer Entertainment', '0', null, '{8193}'), (1152, 'Echochrome II', 'Presenting a brand new take on the puzzle genre, echochrome ii introduces a unique twist on gameplay that lets players use pure imagination to solve puzzles by controlling light and shadows.

Utilizing the PlayStation Move motion controller and the PlayStation Eye camera, players can rotate levels and control light and shadows to change the way objects are viewed and the shadows they cast. The ultimate goal is to lead your character through the path from beginning to end, while learning how a variety of different objects can be combined with perspectives, angles and the use of light can be used to help solve the puzzle. Beware … much like echochrome, the possibilities are infinite and there is always more than meets the eye as every person can view each puzzle differently!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2c66.jpg', '2010-12-21', '{9}', 'IGDB', 92, 18240, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":189931,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":28789,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115567.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115564.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115565.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115563.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115566.jpg"]', '{55190,24426,56033,20342,9835,55173,28070,20329,55984,60044}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UpqhBDSpJyk}', 'SCE Japan Studio', '0', null, '{2697}'), (1153, 'Cyber Troopers Virtual-On Oratorio Tangram', 'Cyber Troopers Virtual-On: Oratorio Tangram is the first of three major revisions to Cyber Troopers Virtual-On: Oratorio Tangram, a sequel to Cyber Troopers Virtual-On. M.S.B.S. Ver. 5.2 was released for Sega Model 3 arcade hardware and is thought to have been exlusive to Japan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co45rz.jpg', '1998-12-31', '{4}', 'IGDB', 92, 9190, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":6291,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":80215,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":93400,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/905706.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/905707.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/905708.jpg"]', '{89550,55038,3772,25311,105269,26227,36739,27419,14704,28070}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GaE7vMAg6TQ}', 'Sega', '0', null, '{953}'), (1154, 'Deathrow', 'Enter a brutal fighting sport where only the fastest and toughest players are victorious. Deathrow combines the fast gameplay of third-person action games, the intensity of fighting games, and the cooperative team play and gritty roughness of rugby. The object of Deathrow is to win matches by any means necessary, either by scoring as many points as possible before time runs out or by severely injuring your opponents and removing them from the field of combat. Engage in fierce hand-to-hand combat against your friends, enemies, or intelligent AI opponents that don''t just get mad--they get even.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5ua8.jpg', '2002-10-18', '{4,14}', 'IGDB', 92, 5811, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":58178,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/942751.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/942752.jpg"]', '{89550,55038,107169,25311,105269,26227,107318,103301,101608,72605}', '{}', 'SouthEnd Interactive', '0', null, null), (1155, 'Uncharted 2: Among Thieves', 'In the sequel to Drake''s Fortune, Nathan Drake comes across a map that showcases the location of Marco Polo''s missing ships. It takes him on a journey to find the infamous Cintamani Stone, and uncover the truth behind it.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tnb.jpg', '2009-10-13', '{5,8,31}', 'IGDB', 91.9984837973181, 565, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":131936,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":131938,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":88748,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":131937,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":131935,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":189294,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4140.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4142.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4139.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4138.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4146.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4144.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4143.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4145.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4149.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4147.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/4141.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117182.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117179.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117180.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117181.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117183.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403686.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403687.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403688.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403689.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403690.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403691.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/403692.jpg"]', '{512,431,7331,471,105049,47823,19164,55038,8263,24426}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GXlat34jGFk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tzy2-UuFPJg}', 'Naughty Dog', '0', null, '{97}'), (1156, 'Kichikuou Rance', 'Kichikuou Rance (literally translating to "Brutal King Rance") is the seventh game in Alicesoft''s flagship Rance Series. It was released in Japan on December 19, 1996. It was the first Alicesoft game to be produced for Windows 95 operating systems, as well as the first game to use the company''s SYSTEM 35 engine and the territory conquest strategy gameplay used in several of its future releases.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3u55.jpg', '1996-12-19', '{12,15,31,34}', 'IGDB', 91.9976637502832, 132645, 1, 26.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/379773.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/379775.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/379774.jpg"]', '{74368,82857,89937,82750,115741,119119,146266,127338,82761,115735}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K2yYSN7sv2I}', 'Alicesoft', '0', null, '{2786}'), (1157, 'Receiver 2', 'Receiver 2 simulates every internal part of each firearm based on manufacturer schematics and gunsmithing resources. Learn exactly how each sidearm works, including how to load and unload them, clear malfunctions, and operate their safety features.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1uzv.jpg', '2020-04-14', '{5,13,32}', 'IGDB', 91.9910481419092, 127489, 1, 49.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/33936.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/353517.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/353515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/353519.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/353516.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/353518.jpg"]', '{37419,32902,113895,43367,103302,36553,105269,25311,35994,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dHj30kG6Et0}', 'Wolfire Games', '0', null, '{6127}'), (1158, 'Tekken 5: Dark Resurrection Online', 'The PlayStation 3 version of Tekken 5: Dark Resurrection. A few gameplay elements have been changed, including the addition of Jinpachi Mishima as a playable character after beating him in Arcade Mode. Stages from the original Tekken 5 can also be unlocked after completing the PS3 version five times.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co46rk.jpg', '2006-12-27', '{4}', 'IGDB', 91.9682460410957, 1234, 1, 25.99, '[{"id":65038,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":47823,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1126109.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1126110.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1126111.jpg"]', '{1244,1245,1243,1242,1247,1249,217590,1240,1555,8258}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IO7ACoqSrM}', 'NAMCO BANDAI Games Inc.', '11', null, '{275}'), (1159, 'RoadCraft', 'As the leader of a company specialized in restoring sites devastated by natural disasters, use your construction machinery to restart the local industry. Clear debris and faulty equipment, rebuild roads and bridges damaged by weather, and much more!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9tyt.jpg', '2025-05-20', '{13,31}', 'IGDB', 91.9671377477383, 314239, 1, 90.99, '[{"id":209693,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":197017,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170784.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170783.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170782.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384686.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384687.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384688.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384689.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384690.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384682.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384683.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384684.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384685.jpg"]', '{17130,107215,109129,23733,44242,16992,54842,82090,109550,20329}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0YxFJTFi0Os,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ajbx_1Sk1Wo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7ldax1af5Wk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LPmCz4ilKmk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N69C6m3k9OU}', 'Saber Interactive', '0', '{374731,374733}', null), (1160, 'Bustafellows', 'A new visual novel from the legendary eXtend! Mixing romance with murders and dangerous ikemen, BUSTAFELLOWS is a steamy noir mystery that will make you shiver but ask for more!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3h51.jpg', '2021-07-29', '{34}', 'IGDB', 91.9462416251053, 114536, 1, 58.99, '[{"id":68242,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":41752,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":56159,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12218.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427834.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427835.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427836.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/427838.jpg"]', '{55984,79994,117139,8968,21599,19075,14362,249545,12579,333190}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9ySJy2bqvU}', 'PQube', '0', null, '{8557}'), (1161, 'Street Fighter II'' Turbo', 'They''re back, and they''re badder than ever! Faster, stronger and with all new moves, twelve of the greatest fighters from across the globe are ready to battle. Choose your champion and get ready for the big brawl as they try to earn the right to battle M. Bison for the title. And just when you think you''ve mastered it all, crank it up a notch and go TURBO!

This home port of the Arcade game for the SNES includes most of the updates from the Arcade and additionally includes the ''Champion Edition'' game-play and characters as well as four selectable game speeds within ''Turbo mode.'' Many of these new features would also be included in ''Street Fighter II: Special Champion Edition'' for the Genesis/Mega Drive.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1w9x.jpg', '1993-07-11', '{4}', 'IGDB', 91.9279717892396, 18626, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":74141,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":98682,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":35649,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":8345,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174147.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/22400.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/22401.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174145.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174144.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174143.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174146.jpg"]', '{89550,42127,101608,14704,5867,109277,103369,114145,1741,76852}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=otPC3_bL-4Y}', 'Playtronic', '11', null, '{2879,219}'), (1162, 'Ogre Battle 64: Person of Lordly Caliber', '"Ogre Battle 64: Person of Lordly Caliber is a tactical RPG for the Nintendo 64.

Featuring a gripping storyline with multiple possible endings, and a genre-defining character class system, this strategic epic has rightly retained its place in the hearts of tactical RPG fans for over a decade.

The game tells the story of Magnus Gallant, a recently graduated officer of the Palatinean Army who is assigned to the troubled southern region of his native land. There he witnesses the plight of the lower classes – the victims of a tyrannical ruling elite whose only thought is for the preservation of their own lofty status. With civil war brewing, Magnus is faced with a terrible choice: to betray his own noble origins in the name of liberty, or turn a blind eye to the evils of his rotten society."', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co54xx.jpg', '1999-07-14', '{11,12,15,31}', 'IGDB', 91.9221244826157, 3568, 1, 9.99, '[{"id":99881,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":191118,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":49200,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/73451.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84748.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/95946.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167742.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167745.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167748.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167741.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167744.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167746.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167747.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/167743.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/619942.jpg"]', '{9805,26845,5550,6635,660,7027,9938,10388,1593,55199}', '{}', 'Atlus', '0', null, '{1313}'), (1163, 'Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic', 'Choose Your Path! Set 4,000 years before the Galactic Empire, you are the last hope for the Jedi Order and the Republic - can you master the ways of the Force to become their savior? Or will you fall to the dark side and achieve ultimate power? Hero, villain, peacekeeper, or chaos-bringer... you and your party will determine the fate of the galaxy!

Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic is a role-playing video game. Players will be able to create their own characters and be able to choose what gender, appearance, class, skills, attributes, and feats they have throughout the game - no two characters will be the same!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tmz.jpg', '2003-07-15', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8977859122091, 116, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":155,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":111301,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":92261,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":34061,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":124071,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":124072,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9409.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215608.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/215609.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1949.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1950.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1952.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1951.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1953.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309279.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309280.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309281.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309282.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309283.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309284.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309285.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309286.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309287.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309288.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309289.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309290.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309291.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309292.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1309293.jpg"]', '{118,74,533,19531,41,2031,11292,472,16,1593}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iYgpLIuKQPo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_D_v1jMzFj4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ne34WE_KCqE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-BXY4g-gplk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xNlWNTQzpBU}', 'LucasArts', '0', '{74551}', '{23}'), (1164, 'Rain World: Downpour', 'Rain World: Downpour is a DLC expansion of Rain World. Take control of five new characters with new abilities in this vast, redefined world. Slugcats have adapted to the harsh conditions alongside evolved predators! Survive new environmental conditions, dangers and explore uncharted territory.

Return to the unwavering wild in Downpour, where you explore new, harsh lands and survive new predators. As time passed, the slugcat has evolved. With five variants of the species - take advantage of various skills that they possess and explore their own personal tales.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co61ky.jpg', '2023-01-19', '{8,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.8931133936016, 194850, 1, 77.99, '[{"id":163228,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":127697,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":163229,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":117386,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":114354,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":88099,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/174361.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/810569.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/810570.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/810571.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005533.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005534.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005535.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005536.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005537.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005538.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1005539.jpg"]', '{17548,25300,28070,26574,80916,105269,25311,107318,10776,111130}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77z9Pi9crSE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4QmZRw8gbOU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p5ZFmwGy0oE}', 'Akupara Games', '2', null, '{11574}'), (1165, 'Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty', 'Phantom Liberty is a spy-thriller expansion for the open-world action RPG Cyberpunk 2077. The narrative centers on the aftermath of the President of the New United States of America''s orbital shuttle being shot down over Dogtown, one of Night City’s most dangerous districts. Players control V, a mercenary tasked with navigating a complex web of espionage and political intrigue.

The expansion introduces Dogtown, a heavily militarized, autonomous zone ruled by a strict and authoritarian leader. With support from NUSA sleeper agent Solomon Reed (voiced by Idris Elba) and returning character Johnny Silverhand (voiced by Keanu Reeves), players engage in a story involving shifting alliances and covert operations. Designed for next-generation hardware, Phantom Liberty features new gameplay mechanics, side activities, and a main storyline centered on themes of power, trust, and survival.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7566.jpg', '2023-09-26', '{5,12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8924774181084, 215769, 1, 70.99, '[{"id":142591,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":142592,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":148491,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":142590,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":148493,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":148492,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":162177,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/109721.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135642.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135643.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135644.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135645.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135646.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1135647.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212639.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212640.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212641.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212642.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212643.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212644.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1212645.jpg"]', '{1877,19164,55038,105269,107318,26574,47823,100413,81249,17548}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zrHb2p4YPT0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PbVKBoDuhZ0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FSCJ0xqH8L4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kfX9n_G0N2Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sJbexcm4Trk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zBrkG3aeWCc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=reABCMNGM3w}', 'CD Projekt RED', '2', null, null), (1166, 'Portal 2', 'Sequel to the acclaimed Portal (2007), Portal 2 pits the protagonist of the original game, Chell, and her new robot friend, Wheatley, against more puzzles conceived by GLaDOS, an A.I. with the sole purpose of testing the Portal Gun''s mechanics and taking revenge on Chell for the events of Portal. As a result of several interactions and revelations, Chell once again pushes to escape Aperture Science Labs.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1rs4.jpg', '2011-04-18', '{8,9,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8897634200001, 72, 1, 13.99, '[{"id":47685,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":47687,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":140774,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":32022,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":47684,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":188403,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":125644,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/36972.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/213418.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/729.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/727.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/728.jpg"]', '{16992,55190,56033,28070,55173,20329,28113,7350,1341,18167}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mC_u9ZwlIUc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9r0rlRqpkOw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qgl1otNanh0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SQb-e7p0KmQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uxSo1k2Y1Uk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SJ5JY-ll2HY}', 'Valve', '0', '{99969,114140}', '{87}'), (1167, 'Uncharted 4: A Thief''s End', 'Several years after his last adventure, retired fortune hunter, Nathan Drake, is forced back into the world of thieves. With the stakes much more personal, Drake embarks on a globe-trotting journey in pursuit of a historical conspiracy behind a fabled pirate treasure. His greatest adventure will test his physical limits, his resolve, and ultimately what he''s willing to sacrifice to save the ones he loves.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1r7h.jpg', '2016-05-10', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8843265825221, 7331, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":168706,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":225956,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192344,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192347,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":192348,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":188903,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":192345,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6304.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6303.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219504.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219507.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/219506.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11575.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11576.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/23584.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11578.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11577.jpg"]', '{11156,565,431,471,19441,512,26192,19560,7346,26758}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BcpbnNYh4Fg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kzXpLtCJ2E0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hh5HV4iic1Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=usIq3HaV9e4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=286d1-gkm_s,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G6ddhpgxMqQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpLCjy_u-7w,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M-OENu7VCbU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1JRbsxNurGg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SL50MitDbys,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oNDhSYeTiiI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y1Rx-Bbht5E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sB0xy74Zrj8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ow2cL-pp6p8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IOmPDvVz3MA}', 'Naughty Dog', '0', null, '{97}'), (1168, 'Discworld Noir', 'Ankh-Morpork is a city surrounded by darkness, where the cold river Ankh flows, where it always rains, and where dwarves and trolls co-exist with secret societies, religious fanatics, stupid police captains, and bar pianists. It is also where a bitterly sarcastic sharp-eyed private investigator named Lewton tries to earn a living solving bizarre cases. A mysterious woman named Carlotta hires him to find her lost lover. Wandering through the dark city and gathering evidence, Lewton has to solve the case, confront a sinister conspiracy, and once again become torn between love and despair.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3h5y.jpg', '1999-07-05', '{2,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8711774835647, 8293, 1, 19.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/83608.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7742.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7743.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15710.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/854844.jpg"]', '{13189,25222,19164,27725,68859,11367,81275,18011,18841,61}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BGDHlRalQFE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zLkg-S_FfXc}', 'Perfect Entertainment', '0', null, '{1115}'), (1169, 'Guacamelee!: Gold Edition', '"Guacamelee! is a Metroid-vania style action-platformer set in a magical Mexican inspired world.

The game draws its inspiration from traditional Mexican culture and folklore, and features many interesting and unique characters. Guacamelee! builds upon the classic open-world Metroid-vania style of games, by adding a strong melee combat component, a new dimension switching mechanic, and cooperative same-screen multiplayer for the entire story. The game also blurs the boundaries between combat and platforming by making many of the moves useful and necessary for both of these.

Travel through a mystical and mysterious Mexican world as a Luchador using the power of your two fists to battle evil. Uncover hidden wrestling techniques like the Rooster Uppercut, and Dimension Swap to open new areas and secrets."

Guacamelee! Gold Edition is a port of the PlayStation 3 and Vita version of the game and includes the DLC that was released for the game. An updated version of the game called "Guacamelee! Super Turbo Championship Edition" was later released that includes an expanded story, 2 new areas, and a new boss.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1twc.jpg', '2013-08-08', '{8,25,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.8686952846301, 19121, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":124027,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/200739.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101519.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101518.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101516.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/101517.jpg"]', '{106987,24426,96217,28070,19164,103168,19150,111130,20342,55173}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CpHN5_H4b08}', 'Drinkbox Studios', '0', null, '{1201}'), (1170, 'Return of the Obra Dinn', 'In this 1-bit first-person mystery game, a merchant ship called the Obra Dinn has appeared at a London harbor, years after being declared lost at sea. As an insurance adjuster, the player must examine the ship for clues.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co27j9.jpg', '2018-10-18', '{9,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.8667185075833, 9643, 1, 43.99, '[{"id":43533,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":110273,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":62893,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":88357,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":62895,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":109229,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15015.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11120.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11119.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11118.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257679.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257674.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257673.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257677.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257678.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257676.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257675.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/295861.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/295944.jpg"]', '{55190,56033,54678,36198,22387,9835,26223,24426,55173,28070}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ILolesm8kFY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AXT_9qs_ft8}', 'Warp Digital Entertainment', '0', null, null), (1171, 'SpongeBob SquarePants: Battle For Bikini Bottom', 'The evil Plankton has set in motion his most diabolical plot ever! The fate of Bikini Bottom has been put into the unsuspecting hands of SpongeBob. Explore a huge world filled with unexpected surprises, challenges, and familiar friends. Join SpongeBob and his friends in his fearless crusade to end Plankton''s evil scheme...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3iyp.jpg', '2003-10-31', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 91.866111832285, 2765, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":62459,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":65477,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":32513,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":62458,"rating_category":{"id":18,"rating":"0"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5064.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5062.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5061.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5063.jpg"]', '{20342,19164,5190,72,20858,119305,4059,55190,3045,56033}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NeJzJ3MaiVU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VNYQ6HpK-Gs}', 'THQ', '0', null, '{3114}'), (1172, 'The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Hearts of Stone', 'The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt – Hearts of Stone is the first major expansion for The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt, released in October 2015. It adds a new storyline set in the existing game world, where Geralt is hired to deal with Olgierd von Everec, a nobleman with a mysterious and cursed past.

The expansion introduces new characters, quests, enemies, and the Runewords system, which enhances gear with powerful effects. It emphasises narrative depth and moral choices, consistent with the tone of the main game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1t7q.jpg', '2015-10-12', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.844805953244, 12503, 1, 22.99, '[{"id":111572,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":126157,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":7623,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":10683,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":111571,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":111573,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170551.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/170550.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1971.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15000.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/14998.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/14995.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/15001.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/14999.jpg"]', '{81249,19164,55199,106987,96217,115653,17548,55038,105049,103168}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vyoi-aVU0mw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mTHvlito464}', 'CD Projekt RED', '2', null, '{62}'), (1173, 'Metroid Prime: Trilogy', 'In this compilation that bundles all three landmark Metroid Prime games, experience the danger and high-intense action of facing space alone as you play skilled bounty hunter, Samus Aran.

In Metroid Prime, explore the world of Tallon IV and witness the deadly experiments performed by the remaining Space Pirates. In Metroid Prime 2, investigate the hostile activities between twin planets Aether and Dark Aether, and learn of their shared energy source that is vital to their survival. In Metroid Prime 3, discover the dangers of a sentient virus that has almost obliterated the Galactic Federation''s network, and face the darkness within...', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co404a.jpg', '2009-08-24', '{5,8,9,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8407886755561, 1112, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":178916,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":178917,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}},{"id":14078,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/73489.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118845.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118848.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/118847.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/165535.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/165531.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/165532.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/165534.jpg"]', '{1105,1111,1108,19531,71,533,7351,1036,571,1078}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u8klx34R8m8}', 'Retro Studios', '3', null, '{243,6240}'), (1174, 'Neon Space', 'Neon Space is a fun and simple but at the same time highly addictive game.
The goal of the game is to drive your little space ship from one end to another, dodging numerous obstacles, solving puzzles, opening new passages with checkpoints and discovering unique game mechanics by yourself. There are 50 levels, and there is also a cool medal system so you can always try your best for that shiny gold medal. If the game becomes too hard you can make it easier with your two in-game abilities slow and blink.

Slow ability- allows for the player to slow down everything except for the player itself.
Blink ability- allows you to jump a short distance. If you manage to time it right, you can even jump through some of the obstacles in the game.

These cool little tricks will have to be used on some levels to push you a bit closer to that medal. To make sure the game doesn''t become too boring, new mechanics and tricks are being added to some levels, just to keep it spiced up through the entire play time.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co21dt.jpg', '2016-05-12', '{15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.8181818181818, 19325, 1, 45.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55657.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55655.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55653.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55654.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55656.jpg"]', '{25311,111130,35994,28182,106987,28309,26574,25646,96217,113402}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1124wsJ1mFY}', 'KupiKey', '0', null, null), (1175, 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster was released individually in the Japan and Asia regions. Outside of these regions, only Final Fantasy X has a physical release, but it includes a download code for Final Fantasy X-2. Those who pick up both Final Fantasy X and Final Fantasy X-2 on PlayStation Vita can swap saves between systems to transfer data between the standalone Vita version and the PlayStation 3 counterpart.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co30so.jpg', '2013-12-26', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.8011134666269, 21899, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":69600,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":190623,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/443744.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/443745.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/443746.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/443743.jpg"]', '{55038,106987,96217,81249,19164,105269,25311,55199,103168,27092}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mWYwmM23Sqs}', 'Square Enix Business Division 3', '9', null, '{9008,39}'), (1176, 'The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild - Expansion Pass', 'The expansion pass is the only way to purchase the DLC packs for the game.

The pass includes 2 DLC packs: The Master Trials and the Champion''s Ballad.

DLC Pack 1: The Master Trials.
Master mode, a new game mode which makes all monsters stronger adds powerful new enemies.
The Trial of the Sword is a new challenge where you start with no equipment, and has to fight through 45 rooms of enemies.
Hero''s Path allows you to see the path you''ve travelled.
Travel medallion is a new item which allows you to register your location as a travel gate on the map.
There are also several hidden items for you to find. The following items, which pay tribute to The Legend of Zelda series, can now be found scattered across Hyrule: Majora''s Mask, Midna''s Helmet, Tingle''s Hood, Tingle''s Shirt, Tingle''s Tights, Phantom Helmet, Korok Mask, Phantom Armor and Phantom Greaves.

DLC Pack 2: The Champion''s Ballad.
The Champion''s Ballad. Following the guidance of an unseen voice, Link encounters a new test: the Divine Beast Tamer''s Trial. Take hold of the One-Hit Obliterator to clear out monster encampments, discover new shrines, conquer a huge dungeon and more. Overcoming all these obstacles will earn you the power to call upon the Master Cycle Zero.
Nine hidden items for you to find. The following items, which pay tribute to The Legend of Zelda series, can now be found scattered across Hyrule: Island Lobster Shirt, Ravio''s Hood, Zant''s Helmet, Phantom Ganon Skull, Phantom Ganon Armor and Phantom Ganon Greaves. You can also find the Royal Guard Cap, Royal Guard Uniform and Royal Guard Boots, which were once worn by Hyrule''s royal guards. Ancient Horse Gear.
The Ancient Bridle and the Ancient Saddle are hidden in treasure chests somewhere in Hyrule, waiting to be found.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa24j.jpg', '2017-03-03', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.7837434148922, 41829, 1, 45.99, '[{"id":147775,"rating_category":{"id":29,"rating":"10"}},{"id":85938,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/177756.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/177757.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/177758.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/177755.jpg"]', '[]', '{106987,96217,81249,103303,103168,55038,101608,19164,28010,55199}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h1GakpHZFpg}', 'Nintendo', '3', null, null), (1177, 'Shovel Knight: King of Cards', 'This game is the final free campaign included in the main game, Shovel Knight, and its updated title, Shovel Knight: Treasure Trove. The game will also be available as a standalone title on PC, PS4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2gsw.jpg', '2019-12-10', '{8,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.7756776156394, 27241, 1, 44.99, '[{"id":124427,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":39365,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":26474,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/14174.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314399.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314403.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314400.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314397.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314401.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314402.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314398.jpg"]', '{55190,56033,22387,19150,36198,24426,55173,28070,106987,96217}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4WbDSCvS610}', 'Yacht Club Games', '4', null, '{3153}'), (1178, 'IL-2 Sturmovik: 1946', 'Oleg Maddox’s world famous IL-2 Sturmovik series of flight simulators continues to expand. The latest offering, IL-2 1946, adds 36 new planes, four new gigantic maps, over a hundred new ground objects, and nearly 200 new campaign missions. This new opus also includes all of the previous Il-2 series content. What years ago began as a one-aircraft study sim is now an astonishing anthology, with a whopping 229 flyable aircraft and over 300 aircraft total! Not to mention that players will have the opportunity to get a first glance at the future of the series arriving next year: Storm of War Battle of Britain via exclusive bonus videos.

IL-2 1946 includes all of the original IL-2 series content: IL-2 Sturmovik: Forgotten Battles, Ace Expansion Pack, Pacific Fighters and alternate history campaigns of year 1946.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co22aq.jpg', '2006-12-07', '{5,13,24}', 'IGDB', 91.680419761759, 5563, 1, 25.99, '[{"id":143224,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":143226,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":143227,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":81197,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":123301,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":143225,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/55684.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/45887.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/45888.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/45891.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/45890.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/45889.jpg"]', '{2165,36258,617,9477,8422,36553,17446,5647,9608,19549}', '{}', '1C-777', '0', null, '{179}'), (1179, 'Serial Experiments Lain', 'An adventure game where you follow the cybernetic journeys of a girl named Lain.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2x71.jpg', '1998-11-26', '{31}', 'IGDB', 91.6745488202934, 76448, 1, 16.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/374313.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/374312.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/374314.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/374315.jpg"]', '{44728,65118,37599,24426,28010,76742,61985,77498,1877,55984}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-uUiL1vkC0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mBFZ31iYLOA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pl8_g75Wl5w,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5udLKFs91uU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iraUmISBYoo}', 'Pioneer LDC', '0', null, null), (1180, 'The Talos Principle: Deluxe Edition', 'The Talos Principle is a philosophical first-person puzzle game from Croteam, the creators of the Serious Sam series, and written by Tom Jubert (FTL, The Swapper) and Jonas Kyratzes (Infinite Ocean). Players are tasked with solving a series of increasingly difficult and complex puzzles woven into a metaphysical parable about intelligence and meaning in an inevitably doomed world.

This definitive version contains the original puzzler in all of its glory and the ambitious expansion The Talos Principle: Road to Gehenna.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9diw.jpg', '2015-10-13', '{5,9,15,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.6409327888177, 23373, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":54535,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":40596,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/64784.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117044.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117046.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117045.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117047.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/117043.jpg"]', '{105269,25311,107318,28070,25646,55038,35994,103301,111130,20342}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WYub3NB4-Y4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s80FtzmO8mc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o2mlbKU-fFE}', 'Croteam', '0', null, null), (1181, 'Star Citizen', 'Star Citizen is a sandbox open-world MMO "SpaceSim" by Cloud Imperium Games. Explore the ''verse, fight, trade, and more when you play Star Citizen!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobtrt.jpg', '2013-08-30', '{5,12,13,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.613010160812, 1595, 1, 16.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203696.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/261132.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203697.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203698.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203642.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203644.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203659.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203660.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203661.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1679428.jpg","https://images.igdb.