him to trudge the entire state of San Andreas (based on California and Nevada) to rebuild his life.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2lb9.jpg', '2004-10-26', '{5,10,31}', 'IGDB', 91.5854695340083, 732, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":47916,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":190862,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":47915,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":47920,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":47917,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":47918,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":47919,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168661.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34971.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189151.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189152.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189150.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/679.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189153.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778550.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778551.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778552.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778553.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778554.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778555.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/778556.jpg"]', '{1020,733,731,3262,19441,564,533,3263,960,40}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vdlpWZpwOq0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XuUc08d7hyU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZaqpcybxUqs}', 'Rockstar North', '0', null, '{847}'), (1184, 'Sunflower Land', 'Farm, Gather, Cook, Raise Animals, Fish, Craft & Trade your NFTs in this Web3 RPG based farming simulator', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co521n.jpg', '2022-04-15', '{13}', 'IGDB', 91.5834797071487, 196770, 1, 70.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/73200.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/771328.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/772429.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/780044.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/780045.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/780046.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/780047.jpg"]', '{87210,101573,205586,9243,17613,36346,65827,31515,355479,234956}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BZxp_E-Np6E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m_JTsGY2JHM}', 'Thought Farm PTY LTD', '0', null, null), (1185, 'Pokémon FireRed Version', 'Pokémon FireRed Version and Pokémon LeafGreen Version are a pair of core series Generation III games that are set in the Kanto region. They were released in Japan on January 29, 2004, in North America on September 9, 2004, in Australia on September 23, 2004 and in Europe on October 1, 2004.

As the first remakes in the Pokémon franchise, the games revisit the original pair of Pokémon games, Pokémon Red and Green Versions, and so feature all of the characters, plot elements, and challenges of them, but with several important upgrades to bring them up to speed with other Generation III games.

The Game Boy Advance Wireless Adapter was initially included with the games when they were first released, eliminating the need for Game Link Cables when trading between the two games (and later Pokémon Emerald Version). In later copies, it was sold separately.

FireRed and LeafGreen went on to become the second best-selling games of the Game Boy Advance, only behind Pokémon Ruby and Sapphire Versions. They also received Nintendo''s Player''s Choice awards.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ziq.jpg', '2004-01-29', '{12,16,31}', 'IGDB', 91.57907723732, 1559, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":32099,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":230952,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":231239,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/20119.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/20118.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/20117.jpg"]', '{55038,106987,96217,115653,19164,1521,25311,81249,55199,105269}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XBmgAp_PlgI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1DGtXZreAw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qtUEb63Cla8}', 'Game Freak', '8', null, '{314}'), (1186, 'The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time', 'The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time is the fifth main installment of The Legend of Zelda series and the first to be released for the Nintendo 64. It was one of the most highly anticipated games of its age, and is listed among the greatest video games ever created by numerous websites and magazines. The gameplay of Ocarina of Time was revolutionary for its time, it has arguably made more of an impact on later games in the series than any of its predecessors even though they had the same cores of exploration, dungeons, puzzles and item usage. Among the gameplay mechanics, one of the most noteworthy is the time-traveling system. The game begins with the player controlling the child Link, but later on an adult Link becomes a playable character as well and each of them has certain unique abilities. Ocarina of Time also introduces the use of music to solve puzzles: as new songs are learned, they can be used to solve puzzles, gain access to new areas and warp to different locations. Dungeon exploration is somewhat more puzzle-oriented than in earlier games but they are not too complex.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3nnx.jpg', '1998-11-21', '{9,31}', 'IGDB', 91.5755411775274, 1029, 1, 13.99, '[{"id":8691,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":81440,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":50830,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":50831,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":3894,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":226949,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84524.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84525.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84526.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84522.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84528.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84523.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84521.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84527.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/84529.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172469.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172468.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172470.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/172471.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951643.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951644.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951645.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951646.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951638.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951639.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951640.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951649.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951650.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951648.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951641.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951642.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/951647.jpg"]', '{1036,1026,1035,7346,1030,1942,1020,2909,533,1074}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uUKZrH6R8oc}', 'Nintendo Entertainment Analysis & Development', '0', null, '{8993,106}'), (1187, 'Corru.Observer', 'Corru.Observer is a hard sci-fi visual novel, point-and-click adventure about a contractor hired by an intelligence agency to hack into an alien biological computing device dredged up from the bottom of the ocean.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co68yh.jpg', '2022-07-13', '{2,12,13,31,32,34}', 'IGDB', 91.5747311587349, 241239, 1, 60.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010947.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010946.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010945.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010943.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010944.jpg"]', '{25311,29348,80916,105269,109339,35994,81275,51528,18011,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dTKyFkHl90U}', 'Corru.Works', '0', null, null), (1188, 'Elden Ring: Shadow of the Erdtree', 'The Shadow of the Erdtree is a fully-fledged expansion that features an all-new story set in the Land of Shadow. It adds a whole new map with 70 new weapons, ten new shields, 39 new Talismans, 14 new sorceries, 28 new incantations, 20 new Spirit Ashes, 25 New Ashes of War, 30 new armour sets, and new consumables and craftables.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7sly.jpg', '2024-06-21', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.5618537149454, 240009, 1, 55.99, '[{"id":181399,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":182012,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/103109.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246054.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246050.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246052.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246051.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246053.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1248165.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1248164.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1248166.jpg"]', '{81249,19164,106987,96217,115653,55038,17548,103168,55199,101608}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M-Xh4vbs6go,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qLZenOn7WUo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6uT8wGtB3yQ}', 'FromSoftware', '2', null, '{10964}'), (1189, 'Sid Meier''s Alpha Centauri', 'Legendary designer Sid Meier presents the next evolution in strategy games, with the most addictive, compelling gameplay yet. Explore the alien planet that is your new home and uncover its myriad mysteries. Discover over 75 extraordinary technologies. Build over 60 base upgrades and large scales secret projects for your empire. Conquer your enemies with a war machine that you design from over 32,000 possible unit types.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3wp5.jpg', '1999-02-09', '{13,15,16}', 'IGDB', 91.526071768892, 863, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":6295,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176831.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176832.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176833.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/176834.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572324.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572325.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572326.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572327.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572328.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572329.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572330.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572331.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1572332.jpg"]', '{102057,10345,17111,33153,17130,10297,121731,866,19130,9789}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ll6z1FQTk-0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fhYSENX14Ck}', 'Electronic Arts', '0', null, '{3579}'), (1190, 'Eternum', 'Eternum is a choice-based visual novel made in Ren''py with tons of romance, mystery, humor, and much more!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co71vw.jpg', '2021-09-16', '{32,34}', 'IGDB', 91.5224948024948, 209628, 1, 70.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/161726.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001661.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001662.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001663.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001664.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001659.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1001660.jpg"]', '{41895,28465,16309,115735,9655,75797,43097,75900,51991,67166}', '{}', 'Caribdis', '0', null, null), (1191, 'S.T.A.L.K.E.R. G.A.M.M.A.', 'G.A.M.M.A. stands for Grok''s Automated Modular Modpack for Anomaly.

G.A.M.M.A. aims at providing a balanced survival, scavenging, cooking, crafting and repairing focused experience with a long progression and smooth gameplay.

The main motivation behind this project is to provide an easy to install, automatically updated and modular modding platform for Stalker Anomaly, with base parameters and gameplay mechanics setup to create a meaningful and enjoyable sense of progression.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5t7v.jpg', '2018-05-11', '{5,24,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.5099262406849, 227211, 1, 35.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/227136.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/937272.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/937273.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/937274.jpg"]', '{26574,17548,105269,25300,19561,10776,18290,111130,107318,17379}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ANNGWOhhJ4k}', 'Grok', '5', null, null), (1192, 'Figment 2: Creed Valley', 'Figment 2: Creed Valley is an encore to Figment. Dusty and Piper have restored peace in The Mind, however, a new adversary is threatening its balance. Our two heroes must travel to Creed Valley, where The Mind’s beliefs and ideals are formed, to face their most menacing and theatrical foe so far.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3m7p.jpg', '2023-03-09', '{7,9,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.4926837849493, 119801, 1, 79.99, '[{"id":127157,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":127160,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":137585,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":51578,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":50366,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":127159,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26070.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48188.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317718.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317719.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317720.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317721.jpg"]', '{20329,28070,24426,109129,77529,106987,96217,110503,19164,25646}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-mqzYAkvMEo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wp1WiIhA-_U,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-99iDuG4SWs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hWkF4C2T8Vc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BUZsJBI_Brg}', 'Bedtime Digital Games', '0', null, '{8771}'), (1193, 'Warframe: Heart of Deimos', 'Visit the grotesquely beautiful Cambion Drift in Heart of Deimos, the latest update in the ever expanding Origin System. Work with the Entrati to defend Deimos from the spreading Infestation that threatens to constrict the Heart of Deimos. Are you ready to meet the Entrati, Tenno?', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2frr.jpg', '2020-08-25', '{5,12,25}', 'IGDB', 91.4914831740756, 137295, 1, 68.99, '[{"id":188586,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":66889,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398063.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398064.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398065.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398066.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398067.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398068.jpg"]', '{55038,105269,19164,107318,54775,113109,81249,25300,90099,25311}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEXVesFvfbA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9_X4d1MzyjU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8FDPBr-hyN4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZriHdUG_Q4}', 'Digital Extremes', '14', null, '{7584}'), (1194, 'Orchard Odyssey: Chestnut Christmas', 'In Orchard Odyssey: Chestnut Christmas, you guide Aurora through a single vibrant orchard level to collect chestnuts in a Christmas-themed Orchard. You can run, jump, and unlock new abilities like double jump or enhanced map vision. The map is semi-procedural, being shuffled every time you enter the Orchard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobqi4.jpg', '2025-12-10', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 91.4824399260628, 391146, 1, 87.99, '[{"id":230323,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1780050.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1780051.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1780052.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1780053.jpg"]', '{20342,55173,24426,37001,28070,89597,395582,393624,390781,386297}', '{}', 'chroda.eu', '0', null, '{13030}'), (1195, 'Hades', 'A rogue-lite hack and slash dungeon crawler in which Zagreus, son of Hades the Greek god of the dead, attempts to escape his home and his oppressive father by fighting the souls of the dead through the various layers of the ever-shifting underworld, while getting to know and forging relationships with its inhabitants.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob9kr.jpg', '2020-09-17', '{12,25,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.469378456954, 113112, 1, 78.99, '[{"id":124852,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}},{"id":49354,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":190541,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":214148,"rating_category":{"id":31,"rating":"14"}},{"id":92339,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":109378,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":77546,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168649.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168650.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168652.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/6752.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56835.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56834.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/168648.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47341.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56836.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401132.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401134.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401135.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401131.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401133.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/401136.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/268559.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/268555.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/268557.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/268558.jpg"]', '{96217,106987,111253,19565,19150,24426,28168,36198,47823,26226}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZZFlcE0fWE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sr__hTXlDZk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=593xCDfumN0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bz8l935Bv0Y}', 'Supergiant Games', '0', null, '{8454}'), (1196, 'Final Fantasy X', 'Final Fantasy X is the tenth main installment in the FF series and the first title released on sixth-generation consoles. It was also the first game to feature fully three-dimensional areas rather than including pre-rendered backdrops, and the first to include voice acting. Final Fantasy X tells the story of a star blitzball player, Tidus, who journeys with a young and beautiful summoner named Yuna on her quest to save the world of Spira from an endless cycle of destruction wrought by the colossal menace Sin.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tr1.jpg', '2001-07-19', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.4611702972929, 418, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":227037,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":132790,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":6462,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2976.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2973.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2972.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2979.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2980.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2978.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2977.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2971.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2975.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2974.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2970.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/259220.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441151.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441152.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441153.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441154.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441155.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441156.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441157.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/441158.jpg"]', '{389,55038,384,55984,22387,14394,11292,1342,1802,359}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hWpz_KUkRuw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GMV8hlQjuj8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tGVlSl6v_7c,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TvCnN_f8AAU}', 'Square Electronic Arts', '0', null, '{39,9008}'), (1197, 'Space Quest IV: Roger Wilco and the Time Rippers', 'May the farce be with you! Get ready for a trek through time with everybody''s favorite intergalactic sanitation engineer and freelance hero, Roger Wilco. In their latest spaced-out space opera, the Two Guys From Andomeda take on science fiction (and just about everything else!) is a spoofy sendup that will leave you laughing.

Roger Wilco embarks on a topsy-turvy trip through space and time in this fourth chapter in the award-winning Space Quest series, Roger Wilco and the Time Rippers. From a nostalgic look at his past in Space Quest I to a terrifying visit to the future of Space Quest XII, Roger''s on the run again.

And hot on his ion trail are the Sequel Police, deadly crosstime assassins who are out to put an end to Roger and all of his Space Quest nonsense once and for all.

Once again it''s up to Roger Wilco to save his future- or is that his past?- of the Space Quest series, and keep the universe safe for fair play, bad jokes, and lots more Space Quest Games.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5v4t.jpg', '1991-01-01', '{2,31}', 'IGDB', 91.4464892267411, 31, 1, 18.99, '[{"id":78569,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/40620.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139736.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139732.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139734.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139733.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/139735.jpg"]', '{28277,32,19164,86657,236,55038,33,25222,25311,13189}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R6R8j8hzu2Y}', 'Sierra On-Line', '0', null, '{8}'), (1198, 'Defense of the Ancients', 'Defense of the Ancients (DotA) is a multiplayer online battle arena mod for the video game Warcraft III: Reign of Chaos and its expansion, Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne, based on the "Aeon of Strife" map for StarCraft. The scenario objective is for each team to destroy the opponents'' Ancient, heavily guarded structures at opposing corners of the map. Players use powerful units known as heroes, and are assisted by allied heroes and AI-controlled fighters. As in role-playing games, players level up their heroes and use gold to buy equipment during the mission.

The scenario was developed with the "World Editor" of Reign of Chaos, and was updated upon the release of its expansion, The Frozen Throne. There have been many variations of the original concept; the most popular being DotA Allstars, which eventually was simplified to DotA with the release of version 6.68. This specific scenario has been maintained by several authors during development, the latest of whom is the anonymous developer known as "IceFrog" who has developed the game since 2005.

Since its original release, DotA has become a feature at several worldwide tournaments, including Blizzard Entertainment''s BlizzCon and the Asian World Cyber Games, as well as the Cyberathlete Amateur and CyberEvolution leagues; in a 2008 article of video game industry website Gamasutra, the article''s author claimed that DotA was probably "the most popular and most-discussed free, non-supported game mod in the world". DotA is largely attributed to being the most significant inspiration for the multiplayer online battle arena genre. Valve Corporation acquired the intellectual property rights to DotA to develop a stand-alone sequel, Dota 2, which was released in 2013.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1r5l.jpg', '2003-12-31', '{12,24}', 'IGDB', 91.4464105018543, 2283, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/343844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/343846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/343845.jpg"]', '{57372,54775,25636,106987,113636,28309,96217,81249,115308,111835}', '{}', null, '5', null, '{556}'), (1199, 'Batman: Arkham Knight - Game of the Year Edition', 'Batman: Arkham Knight is an action-adventure game developed by Rocksteady Studios, released in 2015. It is the final installment in the Arkham series. Players control Batman as he faces Scarecrow, who unites Gotham''s criminals to destroy the Dark Knight. The mysterious Arkham Knight, a new adversary, aids Scarecrow in his plan.

The game features open-world exploration, stealth, combat, and puzzle-solving. A key addition is the Batmobile, used for traversal and combat. The story explores Batman’s psychological struggles and the collapse of his alliances as Gotham spirals into chaos.

The Game of the Year Edition includes:
- Catwoman’s Revenge DLC
- The four-mission Season of Infamy: Most Wanted DLC
- Batgirl’s Arkham Asylum prequel A Matter of Family DLC
- Robin’s A Flip of a Coin DLC
- And the brand new Batman v Superman Batmobile Pack', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xja.jpg', '2016-09-05', '{25,31}', 'IGDB', 91.4045971727758, 42929, 1, 32.99, '[{"id":29911,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":75183,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398506.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398507.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398508.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398509.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398510.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398511.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398512.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398513.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398514.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/108768.jpg"]', '{55984,19164,103266,81249,103168,26574,107614,19565,103054,19564}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8BHbzq9W_c}', 'Rocksteady Studios', '3', null, '{68}'), (1200, 'Divinity: Original Sin II - Definitive Edition', 'There can only be one God. The Divine is dead. The Void approaches. And the powers lying dormant within you are soon to awaken. The battle for Divinity has begun. Choose wisely and trust sparingly; darkness lurks within every heart. Master deep, tactical combat. Join up to 3 other players - but know that only one of you will have the chance to become a God, in multi-award winning RPG Divinity: Original Sin 2.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1y5o.jpg', '2018-08-31', '{12,15,31}', 'IGDB', 91.3718668027461, 103337, 1, 40.99, '[{"id":37444,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":96289,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":93027,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":111206,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":111207,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8475.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214096.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214095.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214101.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/214099.jpg"]', '{19404,27092,106987,113402,96217,103232,81249,13196,7615,115653}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xQKEp8bv_rw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhnrYv9U_dU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_K_vKMo7DEI}', 'Bandai Namco Entertainment', '14', '{172234,144597}', '{1024}'), (1201, 'The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth', 'The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth is a top down, procedurally-generated roguelike game, remade based on the original game The Binding of Isaac. You play as Isaac, a little boy who is chased to the basement by his mother who intends to kill Isaac for her savior. You explore different levels, collect items and try to defeat your mother.. and whatever other evil awaits you. If you die, you restart with none of your items you collected, and you must explore the basement and beyond again.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaare.jpg', '2014-11-04', '{5,9,12,31,32,33}', 'IGDB', 91.3705039573807, 7789, 1, 9.99, '[{"id":108917,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":32995,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":92229,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":90698,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":189524,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35022.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7008.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7011.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35727.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/35726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182679.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182677.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182678.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182676.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182680.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182681.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/182682.jpg"]', '{2132,533,3188,571,9498,20,21,11118,1035,2939}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z6_C2ppkdVc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1aBb0M8HRCQ}', 'Edmund McMillen', '8', null, '{12491}'), (1202, 'Cosmic Spacehead', 'Cosmic needs your help! He has no money, no car, and no respect from his fellow Cosmonaut''s! The trouble is, no one believed his tale of discovering a far away planet called "Earth" so it''s your job to help him get back there and take some handy snaps! Starting from his home town Old Lino Town, it''s Cosmic gameplay all the way in a unique blend of adventure and arcade action plus a whole galaxy of surprises thrown in!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3klf.jpg', '1993-12-31', '{8,31}', 'IGDB', 91.3676029791415, 12013, 1, 16.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/17581.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/16444.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593779.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593780.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593781.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593782.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593783.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593784.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593785.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593786.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593787.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/593788.jpg"]', '{28070,55038,105269,25311,107318,103301,20342,55173,24426,115283}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFf9Xgcu0N8}', 'Supersonic Software', '8', null, null), (1203, 'Bloodborne', 'An action RPG in which the player embodies a Hunter who, after being transfused with the mysterious blood local to the city of Yharnam, sets off into a "night of the Hunt", an extended night in which Hunters may phase in and out of dream and reality in order to thin the outbreak of abominable beasts that plague the land and, for the more resilient and insightful Hunters, uncover the answers to the Hunt''s many mysteries.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob99l.jpg', '2015-03-24', '{12,31}', 'IGDB', 91.3636180927383, 7334, 1, 26.99, '[{"id":31812,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192441,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":192442,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":213817,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":77560,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":192440,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":192439,"rating_category":{"id":21,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169231.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169232.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169233.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9532.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9530.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9533.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9534.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9531.jpg"]', '{105049,11133,36198,28168,10760,19164,18225,7331,8746,1593}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2UJxaWZoK6Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ga98zSE9Q3Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AXiUYQ8eunw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMxEpPCSH5A,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QEv7ZHytVAk}', 'FromSoftware', '0', null, null), (1204, 'Hades II', 'Battle beyond the Underworld using dark sorcery to take on the Titan of Time in this bewitching sequel to the award-winning rogue-like dungeon crawler.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaknx.jpg', '2025-09-25', '{12,25,31,32}', 'IGDB', 91.3521707661755, 228525, 1, 93.99, '[{"id":222247,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":222248,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":220108,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169236.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169237.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/169235.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/197809.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/196440.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/192811.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/261483.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/261964.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/261965.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/261966.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946346.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946347.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946348.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946349.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946350.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/946351.jpg"]', '{19150,96217,106987,111253,55199,105049,19560,24426,28168,47823}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WH3jT53hIYM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-iHDj3EwdI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Miu_akSity4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zz2OyVgnSxg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Gv0eQjJ-gY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U8lJRcUeEMs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-SnaCUsUF3E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-1n05w4-cE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppEKFy83w-o}', 'Supergiant Games', '0', null, '{8454}'), (1205, 'Rooftop Rascal: The Drizzle Cat', 'In "Rooftop Rascal: The Drizzle Cat," you control a clever cat navigating city buildings'' fire escape stairs to the rooftop.

The gameplay centers on jumps, and quick thinking.
Your goal is to climb as high as you can and reach the rooftop.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8srh.jpg', '2024-09-06', '{8}', 'IGDB', 91.3379310344828, 316176, 1, 56.99, '[{"id":185925,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/145375.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1396709.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1396710.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1396711.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1396712.jpg"]', '{27287,228174,79755,119199,337450,314678,297400,275810,185807,129546}', '{}', 'chroda.eu', '0', null, '{12821}'), (1206, 'Multi-Users in Middle-earth', 'MUME, Multi-Users in Middle-earth, is a DikuMUD based upon J.R.R. Tolkien’s Middle-earth that has been continuously running, enhanced, and remastered since fall of 1991. In MUME, players are encouraged to role-play as they live in this meticulously crafted world exploring the conflict leading into the War of the Ring during the late Third Age. The action takes place nearly 100 years prior to The Hobbit but long after the loss of the One Ring by Sauron. The key to Erebor has just been found by Gandalf in Dol Guldur and all the epic tales narrated in The Lord of the Rings may take place.

MUME covers 28,000+ original rooms from the mighty Dwarven Halls beyond the Gulf of the Lhûn in the West to the Mountains of Mirkwood in the East, and from the ruins of Fornost Erain in the North to the fortress of Isengard in the South.

Players can choose among several different races, each with some unique characteristics. The races are separated into three striving factions. Dwarves, Elves, Half-Elves, Hobbits and Men — among them are the shapeshifting Beornings — are eternally at war with the Orcs, Trolls and Black Númenóreans. Moreover, the orkish tribe of the Zaugurz is trying to expand its territory at the expense of the Tarkhnarb Orcs of Goblin Gate. Most of this conflict takes place to the east and south of the town of Bree, but rare raids or solitary agents of the Red Eye have made it to as far west as the Dwarven homes in the Blue Mountains.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2f30.jpg', '1992-12-31', '{12,25}', 'IGDB', 91.3375796178344, 136790, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396285.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396287.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396289.jpg"]', '{54775,115653,81249,115308,19164,103168,26574,113109,17548,37382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0qTj5XMCS04,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d-Ax1MZlDoE}', null, '0', null, null), (1207, 'Oddworld: Abe''s Oddysee', 'Oddworld: Abe''s Oddysee is the first game set in the fictional Oddworld universe. It is a platformer with puzzle-solving elements, focusing on the portrayal of a weak, underpowered character in a grim and hostile world, who has to rely on his cunning to outwit enemies and overcome hazards. The game has pre-rendered background graphics and uses CG movies of similar style to advance the story between the levels.

The main character Abe is almost completely helpless: he cannot use weapons and is usually instantly killed by his brutal enemies if he confronts them directly. For this reason, most of the game involves careful exploration, timed movement, sneaking, and outsmarting the foes through various means: throwing stones to confuse them, luring them into traps, etc. Abe can run, jump, climb, tiptoe, crouch, and roll; in most areas these actions are essential to his survival. A few stages involve Abe riding a large animal known as Elum.

Abe''s only special power is chanting, which he can use to stun certain enemies for a while or possess them. When Abe possess an enemy he gains his abilities: for example, possessing the body or a ferocious Slig allows the player to shoot from his machine gun, communicate with other creatures of his kind, and even commit suicide, clearing the way for Abe.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co89fk.jpg', '1997-09-18', '{8,9,31}', 'IGDB', 91.3274037229278, 999, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":78910,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":122984,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/95508.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552140.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552141.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552142.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552137.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552138.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/552139.jpg"]', '{1000,7342,533,1185,1006,1877,3025,5601,55190,1186}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jWCrg3jGCk8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bLT-hCj8bTA}', 'GT Interactive Software', '0', null, '{223}'), (1208, 'Black Ops', 'You are a black ops male agent, sent to eliminate DR. Gallagher, former member of the Black mesa science team, who is hiding in the Dead end night club. You aren''t able to find him, but in the warehouse, you hear a .357 Magnum being fired. It was DR. Gallagher, that commited suicide. You pick up the bomb (As seen in the case in Opposing Force, with 2 Black ops activating the bomb), Let yourself captured by the grunts, in the jail, go to a dirty rotten cell. you make your way out, get to Black mesa. When you set the bomb, you are shot by Adrian Shepard, but NOT killed. You see the G-man re-arming the bomb, you wake up, but you must get out of there.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5ji5.jpg', '2005-10-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 221904, 1, 10.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/905565.jpg"]', '{113362,105269,306,68286,55038,107318,103301,95340,27283,105482}', '{}', null, '5', null, null), (1209, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 7', 'Embrace the madness.

In Call of Duty: Black Ops 7, Treyarch and Raven Software are bringing players the most mind-bending Black Ops ever. The year is 2035 and the world is on the brink of chaos, ravaged by violent conflict and psychological warfare following the events of the fan-favorite titles Black Ops 2 and Black Ops 6. Wielding cutting-edge technology, the Black Ops team led by David Mason must fight back against a manipulative enemy who weaponizes fear above all else.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9xwv.jpg', '2025-11-14', '{5}', 'IGDB', 52.9016274636343, 348220, 1, 87.99, '[{"id":223537,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":224584,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":226000,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":226001,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":226002,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":226003,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":226004,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1554483.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1616205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1616206.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1616207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1616204.jpg"]', '{83727,68287,119177,106805,55038,105269,38030,68286,107318,103301}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dZdRDyYGoQg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9txkGBj_trg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OzY-IhW45DY}', 'Treyarch', '0', null, '{1956,107}'), (1210, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6', 'Developed by Treyarch and Raven, Black Ops 6 is a spy action thriller set in the early 90s, a period of transition and upheaval in global politics, characterized by the end of the Cold War and the rise of the United States as a single superpower. With a mind-bending narrative, and unbound by the rules of engagement, this is signature Black Ops.

The Black Ops 6 Campaign provides dynamic moment-to-moment gameplay that includes a variety of play spaces with blockbuster set pieces and action-packed moments, high-stakes heists, and cloak-and-dagger spy activity.

In a best-in-class Multiplayer experience, players will test their skills across 16 new maps at launch, including 12 core 6v6 maps and 4 Strike maps that can be played 2v2 or 6v6.

Black Ops 6 also marks the epic return of Round-Based Zombies, the fan-favorite mode where players will take down hordes of the undead in two brand-new maps at launch. Post-launch, players can look forward to even more exciting maps and groundbreaking experiences dropping into both Multiplayer and Zombies.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8zis.jpg', '2024-10-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 78.542565484353, 302156, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":177507,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":218450,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":184424,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":203677,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":203676,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":192240,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":226605,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/229226.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/229227.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1337932.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1337933.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339355.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339353.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339360.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339357.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339358.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339362.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339365.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339366.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339354.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1339361.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384643.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1384644.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414671.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414672.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414673.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1414674.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V08UPqchVgQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dqEvH7TBSnA}', 'Treyarch', '0', null, '{1956,107}'), (1212, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops is the seventh main Call of Duty game and the sequel to Call of Duty: World at War. The game differs from most previous installments, which would involve a usual three-country campaign, while Call of Duty: Black Ops features two playable countries (Russia and the USA) but only has an American campaign. Several new features are also introduced, such as dive-to-prone and the available use of a flashlight on certain weapons. Furthermore, the campaign''s playable characters now speak while being controlled by the player.

Extra game included within:

+ Zork (Apple II)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wkl.jpg', '2010-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 80.3750786906284, 545, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":226645,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":211138,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":211139,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":211136,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":73805,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":78237,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":189061,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/19292.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386800.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386801.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386802.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/386798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371278.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371276.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371277.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371279.jpg"]', '{979,623,2031,2033,1122,564,343,622,625,621}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cenzE-3C6NQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPTOVQFRggI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtRnpC7ddv8}', 'Activision', '0', '{22553,22636,22945,21859}', '{1956,107}'), (1213, 'Titans Black Ops', 'Titans Black Ops is a 2D jump n gun about mercenaries trying to save the world and then go home and take a well-deserved nap. Choose your gun, purchase an arsenal of powerful more guns and grenades then blow EVERYTHING up and save the world by the way. Lock and load!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co59c6.jpg', '2021-08-26', '{5,31,33}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 165596, 1, 79.99, '[{"id":52562,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":45382,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48400.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/596761.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/596764.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/596767.jpg"]', '{106805,43367,105269,87622,55038,19164,107318,103301,76877,75242}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1214, 'Vietnam: Black Ops', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co92x3.jpg', '2000-09-27', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 78703, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":70433,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384144.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384145.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384151.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384147.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384146.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384150.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/384149.jpg"]', '{95340,119177,106805,38030,87622,28751,32902,43367,55038,105269}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWlvORpbZtg}', 'ValuSoft', '0', null, '{10850}'), (1215, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III', 'The PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 versions of Call of Duty: Black Ops III were developed by Beenox and Mercenary Technology while the PlayStation 4, Xbox One, PC versions of the game were developed by Treyarch. Due to the last generation consoles'' inferior hardware, significant changes had to be made.

These changes include:

- The campaign is not available.
- Nightmares mode is not available.
- Ground War is not available.
- The Season Pass is not available
- Only the bonus Zombies map, The Giant and the Awakening DLC pack are available to download
- Reduced graphics quality and performance', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co60bm.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5}', 'IGDB', 72.0354510077677, 136212, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":169816,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":169817,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648569.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648570.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648571.jpg"]', '{113362,105269,306,68286,55038,107318,103301,95340,27283,105482}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2WUJbA3dSMw}', 'Treyarch', '11', null, null), (1216, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War', 'The iconic Black Ops series is back with Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - the direct sequel to the original and fan-favorite Call of Duty: Black Ops. Black Ops Cold War will drop fans into the depths of the Cold War’s volatile geopolitical battle of the early 1980s. Nothing is ever as it seems in a gripping single-player Campaign, where players will come face-to-face with historical figures and hard truths, as they battle around the globe through iconic locales like East Berlin, Vietnam, Turkey, Soviet KGB headquarters and more.

Beyond the Campaign, players will bring a Cold War arsenal of weapons and equipment into the next generation of Multiplayer and Zombies experiences. Welcome to the brink. Welcome to Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2n6j.jpg', '2020-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.1730046671528, 137001, 1, 55.99, '[{"id":189633,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":69551,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":125737,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":215946,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":215947,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":215948,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":108467,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46797.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398033.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398034.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398035.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398037.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/398036.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378021.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378022.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378023.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378024.jpg"]', '{119177,106805,38030,17446,83727,102868,64311,68287,95340,30229}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsBRGCabaog,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3G2JektAKW8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTS9n_m7TW0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mniWW2haNnY}', 'Activision', '0', null, '{1956,107}'), (1217, 'Syndicate Black Ops', 'The action takes place after the Dark ages (in a far future). You are a member from the Syndicate, a powerful criminal group specialist in assassination and delicate missions.

One of the more powerful mega corporation : Croon, contact you so that you "clean" their little error : Inadvertently they opened some hell''s gate and the Federation send its choc troops in order to pacificate all of these things and to bring some proofs against Croon.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6vad.jpg', '2004-09-30', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 259425, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104662.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104663.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104664.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104665.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104666.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104667.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104668.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104669.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104680.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104681.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104670.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104671.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104672.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104673.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104674.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104675.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104676.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104677.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104678.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1104679.jpg"]', '{113362,105269,306,68286,55038,107318,103301,95340,27283,105482}', '{}', null, '5', null, null), (1218, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4', 'Black Ops is back! Featuring gritty, grounded, fluid Multiplayer combat, the biggest Zombies offering ever with three full undead adventures at launch, and Blackout, where the universe of Black Ops comes to life in one massive battle royale experience featuring the largest map in Call of Duty history, signature Black Ops combat, characters, locations and weapons from the entire Black Ops series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wkf.jpg', '2018-10-12', '{5}', 'IGDB', 74.9726811728584, 83727, 1, 45.99, '[{"id":226609,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":62547,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":69671,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":23390,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":93709,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":125440,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":188875,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5647.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5648.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212779.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212632.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212635.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212631.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212629.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212630.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212633.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212634.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212636.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212638.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212637.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377997.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377998.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377999.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378000.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378001.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024,87622}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lNSL5IbA_4Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQ-vta0oFDw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJv-xtxKkQY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FyBVOEqMk4c,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wpC5qgHRmu0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3pyfKYwlGhQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BjiaMBk6rHk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i3ghyAAZFGs}', 'Treyarch', '0', null, '{1956,107}'), (1219, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II', 'Pushing the boundaries of what fans have come to expect from the record-setting entertainment franchise, Call of Duty: Black Ops II propels players into a near future, 21st Century Cold War, where technology and weapons have converged to create a new generation of warfare between old and new foes. In this conflict, the mechanized creations of men reign supreme, facing off against each other as their creators stay safe and unconflicted, and in the process grow ever softer. In this scenario an important question will be asked: What happens when an enemy steals the keys to your war? To understand such a possible future, you must understand where you have been.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wkv.jpg', '2012-11-12', '{5}', 'IGDB', 76.0919895397632, 1122, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":226665,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":32932,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":211423,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":190798,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":93478,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":96285,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":96511,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26784.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1257.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1260.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1259.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1258.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1256.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154190.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154188.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154191.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154189.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154192.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154193.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154194.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378019.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378020.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378016.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378017.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378018.jpg"]', '{2033,545,979,564,2031,622,5647,1006,960,621}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3tedlWs1XY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F6vOWbJ46XU}', 'Activision', '0', '{20154,21686,20854,20153,295255,295256}', '{1956,107}'), (1220, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III deploys players into a dark, twisted future where a new breed of Black Ops soldier emerges and the lines are blurred between our own humanity and the technology we created to stay ahead, in a world where cutting-edge military robotics define warfare. With three unique game modes: Campaign, Multiplayer and Zombies, providing fans with the deepest and most ambitious Call of Duty ever.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co20yw.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 72.141944901014, 9509, 1, 15.99, '[{"id":226666,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":99754,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":190362,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/22752.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9632.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9634.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9631.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9633.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9630.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378002.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378003.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378004.jpg"]', '{18968,7350,11544,564,5647,11646,1886,1939,25657,2033}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Y5VepXzMPs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A7Tx9k0C7Ic,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fQhDon2bVI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GM2m9LG35N0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=75CWhg8oBNA}', 'Activision', '0', '{19948,20291,20292,28413,290251,23727}', '{1956,107}'), (1221, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa3k0.jpg', '2010-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 343819, 1, 8.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024}', '{}', 'Treyarch', '11', null, '{107,1956}'), (1222, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops', 'The Nintendo DS version of Call of Duty: Black Ops has many new features like the Perks system for the six player online multiplayer. The player can tap an icon to switch the current weapon for a new one, like past DS games, or drag the weapon into an inactive button to add to their inventory without replacing the weapon they are using currently. An auto lock-on feature is available to use in the Recruit and Regular difficulties.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2adk.jpg', '2010-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 55.0646287458815, 135299, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":226646,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":226647,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":109182,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":126161,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46933.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46931.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414060.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414059.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414058.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024}', '{}', 'Activision', '11', null, '{1956,107}'), (1223, 'Rainbow Six: Black Ops', 'Black Ops is a standalone fan-made mod that ties all Rainbow Six titles that kinda use the same engine together. Instead of running Rogue Spear using RogueSpear.exe, you can use the latest Black Ops engine to run the game so it works on modern-day systems. All seven Rainbow Six parts merged into one game: Tom Clancy''s Rainbow Six (1998), Rainbow Six: Eagle Watch Expansion pack (1999), Rogue Spear (1999), Rogue Spear: Urban Operations (2000), Rainbow Six: Covert Ops Essentials (2000), Rogue Spear: Black Thorn (2001), Rainbow Six: TakeDown - Missions in Korea. Play Rogue Spear and other Rainbow Six parts with the latest 2.61 engine. It contains: all levels unlocked (Custom mission: Terrorist Hunt/Hostage Rescue/etc), unlocked/modded access to all Lone Wolf Missions, modded/fixed Rainbow Six / Eagle Watch levels - very few glitches remain, Vista/7 audio fix, X64 Registry, Win7 Registry fix, remapped a load of the game files to be able to work with Black Thorn, modded campaign - play 57 missions from Rainbow Six to Black Thorn, 53 Weapons in total to choose from, special unlocked terrorist weapons - Uzi, Dragunov, AK47, AK74, Skorpion; secondary weapons have been modded so the player can choose 2 primary weapons, default 6 grenades instead of 3, has its own registry paths - this version will not affect your current Rainbow Six installation, modded MP weapons so you can select all weapons as secondary. It''s a small game, easy for LAN-gaming.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co226s.jpg', '2014-12-26', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 132046, 1, 29.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{58095,95340,78770,393345,393215,392676,392415,391831,391328,390843}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R_hsdYS2C_M}', 'Red Storm Entertainment', '5', null, null), (1224, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II', 'Rooted in near-future fiction, Call of Duty: Black Ops II propels players into a visual landscape in an epic single player campaign highlighted by branching storylines and non-linear missions. The game is a re-imagined multiplayer that introduces players to some of the most cutting-edge weaponry and equipment that 2025 will have to offer, and punctuated with an all-new Zombies experience running in the multiplayer engine.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3aud.jpg', '2012-11-18', '{5}', 'IGDB', 81.5064822942896, 21865, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":126236,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":111306,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":109210,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":106337,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":126237,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46916.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46918.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413899.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413898.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29568.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,68287,106805,105269,55038,68286,520,107318,103301}', '{}', 'Activision', '11', null, '{107,1956}'), (1225, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - The Giant', 'Zombies returns in all of its undead glory with ''The Giant,'' a research facility featuring the weapon-upgrading Pack-a-Punch Machine. Re-live the chaos of Treyarch''s classic ''Der Riese'' Zombies map, picking up the Zombies story with Dempsey, Nikolai, Richtofen, and Takeo where Origins left off.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5e.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 290251, 1, 21.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{520,111130,95340,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,25646,43367}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qmliMQMnUj0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9styqi7r0M}', 'Mercenary Technology', '1', null, null), (1226, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Mobile', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Mobile is the spin-off version of Call of Duty: Black Ops for mobile phones. It features a different campaign set exclusively in Vietnam.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2adl.jpg', '2010-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135300, 1, 9.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414061.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414062.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414063.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Glu Mobile', '11', null, '{1956,107}'), (1227, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Zombies', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops – Zombies is a spin-off game of the Call of Duty series'' Zombies mode and the sequel to Call of Duty: World at War – Zombies.

Adapted from the best-selling console hit and built specifically for tablets and smartphones the game allows up to four-player multiplayer, and, as a new addition to both platforms, voice chat. It also features ranks based on Experience Points.

It includes the maps Kino der Toten, Ascension, and Call of the Dead: Director''s Cut as well as the unlockable Dead Ops Arcade.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xk7.jpg', '2011-12-01', '{5}', 'IGDB', 79.6147915959297, 77267, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":21783,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205551.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205550.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205553.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205552.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205554.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205555.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205556.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/205549.jpg"]', '{19561,87622,103301,56033,47823,17379,75242,36198,111130,44076}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7CuGVvQQIg}', 'Glu Mobile', '0', null, '{1956}'), (1228, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Zombies Chronicles', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Zombies Chronicles is a content expansion that delivers 8 remastered classic Zombies maps from Call of Duty: World at War, Call of Duty: Black Ops and Call of Duty: Black Ops II. Complete maps from the original saga are fully remastered and HD playable, within Call of Duty: Black Ops III.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7crx.jpg', '2017-05-16', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 28413, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":166871,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":166870,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":94785,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":166873,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":166872,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":58718,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":93171,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/64453.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/43547.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/43548.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/43549.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/43551.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/43550.jpg"]', '{106805,87622,105269,55038,76877,19164,107318,103301,75242,111130}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ni3pi3PJJvM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_uTDtbs2jZ4}', 'Treyarch', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1229, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Descent', 'Descent, the third DLC map pack for Call of Duty: Black Ops III, delivers an all-new mind-bending Zombies experience, along with 4 action-packed Multiplayer maps, which includes a re-imagining of the Call of Duty: Black Ops II classic, Raid.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ktk.jpg', '2016-07-12', '{5}', 'IGDB', 68.3333333333333, 20292, 1, 31.99, '[{"id":86221,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115249.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115250.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115251.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115253.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115252.jpg"]', '{58095,95340,78770,393345,393215,392676,392415,391831,391328,390843}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tSuKCFiNNyA}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1230, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 6', 'The Haunting returns with a vengeance in Season 06, bringing new Halloween-themed map variants and chilling LTMs across all three modes. Fight as and against iconic slashers and zombies and unlock a hearty helping of spooky rewards scattered throughout in-game events and the new seasonal Battle Pass.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coapai.jpg', '2025-10-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 373569, 1, 91.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/208234.jpg"]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hP_-SkzYbMk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kbNQySzrixs}', 'Raven Software', '7', null, '{1956,107}'), (1231, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Escalation', 'Escalation is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2010 game Call of Duty: Black Ops. It includes four new multiplayer and one new zombie map:

- Zoo (takes place at an abandoned Soviet zoo)
- Convoy (takes place near an abandoned convoy containing a big missile)
- Hotel (takes place in a resort in Cuba)
- Stockpile (takes place in a small village in Russia, with one of the houses containing a stockpile of weapons)
- Call of the Dead (the zombie map, taking place in an abandoned Siberian outpost near the coast)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4rvu.jpg', '2011-05-03', '{5}', 'IGDB', 57.099546230529, 22945, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":73809,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":189062,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/320702.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/320704.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/320703.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/320706.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/320705.jpg"]', '{83727,68287,119177,17446,106805,19561,38030,102584,13210,8422}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_Cx82OFXM0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mwbc0Aw1q3c,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KuYWRts7Qs4}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1232, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Collection', 'This Bundle contains:

- Call of Duty: Black Ops
- Call of Duty: Black Ops II
- Call of Duty: Black Ops III', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3asf.jpg', '2016-12-01', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136183, 1, 45.99, '[{"id":182771,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":182768,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":182769,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":182770,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":182767,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413866.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413867.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413868.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1233, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Eclipse', 'DLC 2 Eclipse for Black Ops 3 is available now featuring all new MP environments and Zombies content.

In the latest episode of the Zombies experience, the Origins characters head to ''Zetsubou No Shima'', a tropical island where experiments with Element 115 have created horrors beyond belief.

Battle your way through four stunning Black Ops III Multiplayer environments: Spire, Knockout, Verge and Rift.

Spire: Take MP combat to a futuristic sub-orbital airport terminal set high in the clouds.

Knockout: The Shaolin Temple with a retro twist contrasts exterior mid-range engagements and interior close quarters.

Verge: This reimagined classic Call of Duty: World at War map, Banzai, drops MP combat into the center of a distant post-apocalyptic future.

Rift: Head to the core of a harsh futuristic military complex, set above an active volcano.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ktj.jpg', '2016-04-19', '{5}', 'IGDB', 60, 20291, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":86222,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115254.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115255.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115257.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115256.jpg"]', '{58095,95340,78770,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,96396,57953}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ot8t0ih2acU}', 'Treyarch', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1234, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 7 - Season 1', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobbwk.jpg', '2025-12-04', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 378032, 1, 81.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220603.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/220604.jpg"]', '[]', null, '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5cb1bPaSV6I,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QUVj6nJUSV8}', 'Treyarch', '7', null, '{1956,107}'), (1235, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 4', 'Season Four, stylized as S04, is the fourth batch of post-launch content for Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 that was released on May 29th, 2025 and ended on August 7th, 2025.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coapag.jpg', '2025-05-29', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 362955, 1, 83.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189859.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1717250.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1717251.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1717252.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1717253.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I65a4O5U_5k}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1956}'), (1236, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 3', 'Season Three, stylized as S03, is the third batch of post-launch content for Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 that was released on April 2nd, 2025 and ended on May 29th, 2025.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coapad.jpg', '2025-04-02', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 362953, 1, 91.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1620234.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1717249.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BdXglUiQYSU}', 'Treyarch', '7', null, '{1956,107}'), (1237, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 5', 'Season Five, stylized as S05, is the fifth batch of post-launch content for Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 that was released on August 7th, 2025.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coapah.jpg', '2025-08-07', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 362956, 1, 88.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/189860.jpg"]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ycs4D-Menoo}', 'Raven Software', '7', null, '{1956,107}'), (1238, 'Call Of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 2', 'Season 02 is here, upending the new order of Avalon. Engage with a massive amount of new content, including five Multiplayer maps, more than six new weapons, a new Zombies map, limited time Valentine’s Day-themed modes, and more. Gear up and deploy to Season 02.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9cn5.jpg', '2025-01-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 330137, 1, 94.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,17446,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3LFrj6qe7Mg}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1956}'), (1239, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Season 1', 'Ready to wreak havoc? The Black Ops 6 era is here. Prepare for a vast new season of content with five Multiplayer maps plus a festive Nuketown variant, seven new weapons, a brand-new Zombies map, and full Call of Duty: Warzone integration along with a new Resurgence map.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co94rp.jpg', '2024-11-14', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 324925, 1, 68.99, '[{"id":194529,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":194528,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/159325.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/159324.jpg"]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sOFxZx5BrcM}', 'Treyarch', '7', null, '{1956,107}'), (1240, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Uprising', 'Uprising is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2012 game Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It includes four new multiplayer and one new zombie map:

- Vertigo (takes place on the top of a skyscraper in India)
- Encore (takes place at a music festival in London, England)
- Magma (takes place in a village struck by a volcano eruption in Japan)
- Studio (takes place in a Hollywood movie set)
- Mob of the Dead (the zombie map, taking place on Alcatraz Island and the Golden Gate Bridge)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3auj.jpg', '2013-04-16', '{5}', 'IGDB', 73.75, 20154, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":88822,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413886.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413887.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Treyarch', '1', null, '{107,1956}'), (1241, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Vengeance', 'Vengeance is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2012 game Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It includes four new multiplayer and one new zombie map:

- Buried (the zombie map, taking place in an underground western town)
- Cove (takes place on a small tropical island)
- Detour (takes placeon a bridge in New York City)
- Rush (takes place in a paintball outfit)
- Uplink (takes place at a satellite control facility in Myanmar)

It also contains the new weapon Ray Gun Mark II, useable only in the Zombies mode.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3auk.jpg', '2013-07-02', '{5}', 'IGDB', 73.3333333333333, 20854, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":88823,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29713.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413888.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413889.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1956}'), (1242, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops I & II Combo Pack', 'This bundle contains:

- Call of Duty: Black Ops I
- Call of Duty: Black Ops II', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3aua.jpg', '2015-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136028, 1, 26.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413841.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413842.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1243, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Declassified', 'Before the future could be won, history had to be written. Exposing that story exclusively on PlayStation Vita, Call of Duty: Black Ops Declassified explores original fiction in the Call of Duty Black Ops universe with an all-new campaign of Special Ops missions. Optimized for gamers on-the-go, Call of Duty Black Ops: Declassified delivers the most intense handheld Call of Duty experience to date, including both Special Ops Story mode and Multiplayer combat tailored for the PS Vita.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wlk.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 48.5280588626999, 8548, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":112894,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":112897,"rating_category":{"id":32,"rating":"16"}},{"id":112898,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":112895,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":112896,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":189087,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115245.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115248.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115247.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115246.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115244.jpg"]', '{68286,64311,8422,28751,57217,10964,15536,68287,7843,11171}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHIh4qn8xO8}', 'nStigate Games', '0', null, '{1956,107}'), (1244, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Care Package', 'The Care Package Edition includes:

- Nuketown Zombies
- Nuketown 2025
- Limited Edition Collectible Steelbook
- Limited Edition Challenge Coins
- Exclusive Weapon Camo
- Exclusive Player Card Backgrounds
- Official Game Soundtrack.
- Remote Controlled MQ-27 Dragonfire Drone
- Care Package', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ay9.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 80.0289913895573, 18352, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":88803,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130235.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413892.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413893.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,68287,105269,55038,68286,113362,107318,103301}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0WmtGCwEv-k}', 'Treyarch', '3', null, null), (1245, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Apocalypse', 'Apocalypse is the fourth and final downloadable content package available for Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It features four multiplayer maps (Pod, Takeoff, Frost, and Dig) and a new zombies map called Origins.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3aum.jpg', '2013-08-27', '{5}', 'IGDB', 65.7375222052622, 21686, 1, 13.99, '[{"id":88802,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29475.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413890.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413891.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gId6lQsCvYs}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1246, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Awakening', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Awakening is the first DLC pack for Call of Duty: Black Ops 3. Awakening includes four new Multiplayer maps: Skyjacked (a reimagining of "Hijacked" from Black Ops 2), Gauntlet, Splash, and Rise. Also included is the Zombies experience Episode 4: Der Eisendrache, the first chapter in an epic time-traversing odyssey.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ktm.jpg', '2016-02-02', '{5}', 'IGDB', 78, 19948, 1, 30.99, '[{"id":86219,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/140232.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/140233.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/141313.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/141312.jpg"]', '{58095,95340,78770,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,96396,57953}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-pml12FKaeY}', 'Treyarch', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1247, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Salvation', 'Salvation is here! Salvation, the fourth and final DLC pack for Call of Duty: Black Ops III, concludes the epic DLC season with four action-packed multiplayer maps and the long-awaited final chapter in the Origins Zombies saga.

The four multiplayer maps bring players to the ancient walls of a medieval fortress and a deceptively quaint backyard picnic, plus two familiar settings re-imagined to take advantage of Black Ops III''s vertical gameplay opportunities and momentum-based, chained movement system.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ktp.jpg', '2016-09-06', '{5}', 'IGDB', 77.5, 23727, 1, 32.99, '[{"id":86224,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648558.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648559.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648560.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,43367,28751,103302,520}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zyyBZjdNsFQ}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1248, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 - Digital Deluxe Edition', 'Digital Deluxe Edition includes:
- Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 game
- 2,400 Call of Duty Points**
- Digital Edition Bonus Items
- Digital Deluxe Bonus Items
- Black Ops Pass*, which includes:
--- "Classified," a Zombies Experience available at Launch
--- 4 Additional All-New Zombies Experiences
--- 12 Multiplayer Maps
--- 4 Exclusive Blackout Characters', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bua.jpg', '2018-10-12', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 118732, 1, 42.99, '[{"id":111685,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":111686,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":96601,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":84751,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":94905,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7224.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591212.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591216.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591218.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591225.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591227.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591229.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591231.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591232.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591233.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591234.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591235.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591236.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591237.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591238.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591239.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591240.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591241.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591242.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591243.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591244.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591245.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591246.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591247.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591248.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591249.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/591250.jpg"]', null, '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1249, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - First Strike', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - First Strike is a commercial DLC for Call of Duty: Black Ops. It adds four new multiplayer and one new zombie map.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4rwy.jpg', '2011-02-01', '{5}', 'IGDB', 74.1959965679814, 21859, 1, 21.99, '[{"id":73813,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":190100,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/113920.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/113923.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/113921.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/113922.jpg"]', '{83727,68287,119177,106805,17446,38030,19561,102584,13210,8422}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OMEeqWBWjv8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DEB0H90lt_M}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1956}'), (1250, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Gold Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops takes you behind enemy lines as a member of an elite special forces unit engaging in covert warfare, classified operations, and explosive conflicts across the globe. With access to exclusive weaponry and equipment, your actions will tip the balance during the most dangerous time period mankind has ever known.

Included with the Gold Edition is the first DLC pack "First Strike" contains 5 incredibly diverse maps spanning the globe, featuring 4 multiplayer maps and a new Zombie experience. This edition was available only in Europe via the PlayStation Store.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3b98.jpg', '2015-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 118925, 1, 14.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413860.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413861.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413862.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1251, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Revolution', 'Revolution is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2012 game Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It includes four new multiplayer and one new zombie map:

- Hydro (takes place on the Indus River in Pakistan)
- Downhill (takes place in the Alps in France)
- Grind (takes place in a skate park in Venice Beach)
- Mirage (takes place in the middle of the Gobi Desert)
- Die Rise (the zombie map, taking place in two broken down skyscrapers)

It also contains a new weapon, the Peacekeeper, and the new game mode Turned, in which players can become an zombie in the zombies mode.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3aul.jpg', '2013-01-29', '{5}', 'IGDB', 70.202216644484, 20153, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":88804,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/26799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413884.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413885.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1956}'), (1252, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Annihilation', 'Annihilation is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2010 game Call of Duty: Black Ops. It includes four new multiplayer and one new zombie map:

- Hangar 18 (takes place at Area 51)
- Silo (takes place at a missile plant in the U.S.S.R.)
- Hazard (takes place on a golf course)
- Drive-In (takes place at the terrain of an old Drive-In)
- Shangri-La (the zombie map, taking place at the mystic temple of Shangri-La in the middle of a jungle)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4rvr.jpg', '2011-06-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 74.9348697808403, 22636, 1, 28.99, '[{"id":189893,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":73807,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30318.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413847.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413846.jpg"]', '{83727,68287,119177,106805,17446,38030,19561,102584,13210,8422}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbcc4cXONso,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z34RTO2BKM4}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1253, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Rezurrection', 'Rezurrection is a downloadable content pack (DLC) for the 2010 game Call of Duty: Black Ops. It includes four remastered zombie maps and one new one:

- Nacht der Untoten (takes place at an abandoned bunker)
- Verrückt (takes place in the Wittenau Sanatorium, located in Berlin, Germany)
- Shi No Numa (takes place at the Rising Sun Facility, in Japanese territory)
- Der Riese (takes place in the secret Nazi facility, Waffenfabrik Der Riese)
- Moon (the new zombie map, taking place in Area 51 and on the moon)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4rwx.jpg', '2011-08-23', '{5}', 'IGDB', 50, 22553, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":73811,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":189138,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/30314.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413845.jpg"]', '{83727,68287,119177,106805,17446,38030,19561,102584,13210,8422}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2k8V7fF7v7s,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NXH381x4j24}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1956,107}'), (1254, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 - Pro Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 Pro Edition includes:

- Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 Game,
- Black Ops Pass,
- Steelbook,
- Pop Socket,
- 10 Specialist Patches,
- 3 Zombies Inspired Collectible Art Cards,
- 1,100 Call of Duty Points,
- “Classified,” a Zombies Experience available at Launch.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bu7.jpg', '2018-10-11', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136016, 1, 39.99, '[{"id":137085,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1044892.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128848.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128847.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,385988,362432}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6kqe2ICmTxc}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1255, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Season Pass', 'The Season Pass for Call of Duty: Black Ops III gets players access to four epic DLC packs. Each DLC pack contains four all-new multiplayer maps and one episode of the Zombies storyline.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5a.jpg', '2015-04-27', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 290246, 1, 12.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFe5u5JFt_g,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-pml12FKaeY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mcGTLwiy4uE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9styqi7r0M}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1256, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Nuketown 2025', 'Nuketown 2025 is a downloadable map released for Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It is a remake of Nuketown which first appeared in Call of Duty: Black Ops. While the original Nuketown went for more of a traditional 1950s theme, the new map is now in a 1960s retro-futuristic Mid-Century modern style meant to represent the "Home of the Future" for 2025.

It was available for free to anyone who pre-ordered the game, purchased a launch copy, or purchased the Hardened edition or the "Care Package" limited special edition of the game. It was later made available to download for free to everyone as well as being included in an update for Call of Duty: Black Ops II on Wii U.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co80ue.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 295256, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":171865,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1290471.jpg"]', null, '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XBTVkIxSx5o}', 'Activision', '1', null, null), (1257, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Gold Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III combines three unique game modes: Campaign, Multiplayer and Zombies. The Campaign has been designed as a co-op game that can be played with up to 4 players online or as a solo cinematic thrill-ride. Multiplayer will be the franchise’s deepest, most rewarding and most engaging to date, with new ways to rank up, customize, and gear up for battle. And Zombies delivers an all-new mind-blowing experience with its own dedicated narrative.

Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Gold Edition includes:
- the full base game
- Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Awakening DLC
- the Nuk3town Multiplayer Map', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7n.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 80, 29164, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":191100,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/146211.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/146209.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/146210.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/146212.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/146213.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', null, '3', null, null), (1258, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 - Vault Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 is signature Black Ops across a cinematic single-player Campaign, a best-in-class Multiplayer experience and with the epic return of Round-Based Zombies.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9e41.jpg', '2024-10-25', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 331251, 1, 76.99, '[{"id":199398,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":199399,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":199396,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":199395,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":199393,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":199394,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":199397,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154415.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461927.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461930.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461934.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461937.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461942.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461944.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1461947.jpg"]', null, '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1259, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Hardened Edition', 'The Hardened Edition contains:

- Call of Duty: Black Ops
- Steelbook case
- Black Ops medal
- Exclusive outfits for PlayStation Home / Xbox Live avatars
- 4 extra zombie co-op missions', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3b9c.jpg', '2010-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 47476, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":170806,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413863.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413864.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413865.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1260, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops - Prestige Edition', 'The Prestige Edition contains everything in the Hardened Edition:

- Call of Duty: Black Ops
- Steelbook case
- Black Ops medal
- Exclusive outfits for PlayStation Home / Xbox Live avatars
- 4 extra zombie co-op missions

as well as a remote-control vehicle modeled after the in-game RC-XD killstreak.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3b96.jpg', '2010-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 102079, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":88825,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413857.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413858.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413859.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0MjcEeTmEys,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OPTOVQFRggI}', 'Activision Publishing', '3', null, null), (1261, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season Six', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 6 reveals more than just Adler''s counterattack against Stitch. Fight through Adler''s broken memories in one of three new Multiplayer maps, and explore mysterious new World War 2 bunkers uncovered throughout Verdansk. Grab your gear and get ready for Season 6.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ytn.jpg', '2021-10-07', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 172674, 1, 68.99, '[{"id":46280,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/659987.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/659985.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/659986.jpg"]', '{83727,119177,38030,106805,102868,64311,68287,95340,17446,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FpOuVzm35no}', 'Activision', '7', null, null), (1262, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season One', 'Season 1 is the first batch of post-launch content for Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War. Revenge, Revolt, and Revelations rock the world of Black Ops Cold War and Warzone. Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 1 offers a massive expansion of free content including eight free maps, three free-to-acquire weapons, an innovative and rewarding Battle Pass system, and much more. Plus: drop into the new Rebirth Island Warzone map!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2mh3.jpg', '2020-12-16', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 141574, 1, 49.99, '[{"id":84873,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9665.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9666.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/424148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/424145.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/424147.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/424146.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFMUvKu-bZs}', 'Activision', '7', null, null), (1263, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Zombies Chronicles Deluxe Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III Zombies Chronicles Deluxe includes the full base game, Season Pass, Zombies Chronicles & additional bonus digital content including:

The Giant Bonus Map: Zombies returns in all of its undead glory with "The Giant". Re-live the chaos of Treyarch''s classic "Der Riese" Zombies map, picking up the Zombies story with Dempsey, Nikolai, Richtofen, and Takeo where Origins left off.

3 Personalization Packs: Fan favorite Cyborg & Weaponized 115 packs along with a new Black Ops 3 pack. Each pack comes with a weapon camo, reticles, and calling card.

The Zombies Chronicles content expansion which delivers 8 remastered classic maps from Call of Duty: World at War, Call of Duty: Black Ops and Call of Duty: Black Ops II.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5b.jpg', '2017-08-29', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 290248, 1, 37.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{58095,95340,78770,393345,393215,392676,392415,391831,391328,390843}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1264, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Hardened Edition', 'Hardened Edition includes:

- Limited Edition 2-Sided SteelBook
- 2 Collectible Challenge Coins
- Official Soundtrack by Jack Wall with Theme by Trent Reznor
- Exclusive PlayStation 3 Dynamic Multiplayer Theme
- Exclusive PlayStation 3 Dynamic Zombies Theme

In-Game Content

- Nuketown Zombies Bonus In-Game Content
- Nuketown 2025 Bonus Multiplayer Map
- Exclusive Weapon Camo
- Exclusive Multiplayer Player Card Background
- Exclusive Zombies Player Card Background', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ay8.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 27955, 1, 6.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130234.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413896.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413897.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,68287,106805,105269,55038,68286,520,107318,103301}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0WmtGCwEv-k}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1265, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season Two', 'The end begins. It’s a jungle out there. Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 2 takes players to the rainforests of Laos, where Woods and his strike team have tracked down Perseus through a vast cartel network. Drop in with the newest in Cold War guerrilla gear, including new weapons, Operator Skins, Legendary Blueprints, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2tzn.jpg', '2021-02-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 144050, 1, 66.99, '[{"id":33244,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9668.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9667.jpg"]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JzOrZVpuJH8}', 'Raven Software', '7', null, null), (1266, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Nuketown Zombies', 'Nuketown Zombies, also known as Nuketown in-game, is a Zombies map that is featured in Call of Duty: Black Ops II. It is based on Nuketown, a multiplayer map from Call of Duty: Black Ops and Call of Duty: Black Ops II.

The map was previously only available to players who purchased the Hardened, Care Package, or Digital Deluxe editions but was later made available to purchase in the system''s digital marketplace.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co80ud.jpg', '2013-03-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 295255, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":171864,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1290470.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,520,83727,111130,102868,64311,95340,68287}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzaVSj0omXo}', 'Activision', '1', null, null), (1267, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Hardened Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III Hardened Edition includes the Call of Duty: Black Ops III game as well as:

LIMITED EDITION SPECIALIST CONCEPT ART CARDS - Call of Duty: Black Ops III multiplayer introduces the new Specialist character system, allowing players to choose from 9 elite black operations soldiers - each with their own look, personality, and voice. Each Specialist is featured on their own art card that includes exclusive concept art, biography, and a description of their unique weapon and ability.

THE GIANT BONUS MAP - Zombies returns in all of its undead glory with "The Giant," a Nazi research facility featuring the weapon-upgrading Pack-a-Punch Machine. Re-live the chaos of Treyarch''s classic "Der Riese" Zombies map, picking up the Zombies story with Dempsey, Nikolai, Richtofen, and Takeo where Origins left off. COLLECTIBLE STEELBOOK - Limited edition steel game case featuring an exclusive design.

IN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: WEAPONIZED 115 - The Weaponized 115 Personalization Pack brings the popular Zombies theme to your favorite Multiplayer weapon. Customize your weapons with the fan favorite Origins-inspired camo, reticle, and animated calling card. IN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: CYBORG - The fan favorite Cyborg Personalization Pack returns in Call of Duty: Black Ops III, fully-loaded with an electrotech-themed weapon skin, uniquely-shaped reticle, and a calling card.

OFFICIAL CALL OF DUTY: BLACK OPS III SOUNDTRACK - Upgrade your playlist with a digital copy of the in-game score.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7t.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 41615, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":84752,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/109129.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648564.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648565.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1268, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Steelbook Edition', 'Includes Call of Duty: Black Ops III standard video game and an official SteelBook, an Amazon Exclusive. A SteelBook is a limited, high quality, premium metal case.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8ibf.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 8905, 1, 14.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648561.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648562.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648563.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1269, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season Four', 'Incoming! This new season of free content includes four Multiplayer Maps, five new weapons, new Points of Interests in Verdansk, and a new quest in Outbreak that sets the stage for the next free Zombies map during the season… Welcome to Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 4.

Everything will come crashing down... Jackal has arrived and Adler will do whatever it takes to get the job done.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co39xy.jpg', '2021-06-17', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 152117, 1, 78.99, '[{"id":41790,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489615.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/488108.jpg"]', '{83727,119177,106805,38030,102868,64311,68287,17446,95340,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IeVOqQ8Vg88,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5mSDOUjF0RU}', 'Activision', '7', null, null), (1270, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Juggernog Edition', 'The Call of Duty: Black Ops III Juggernog Edition is the ultimate Collector''s Edition for Black Ops fans. It comes loaded with a cache of collectible items:

JUGGERNOG MINI-FRIDGE - Store beverages in a fully functional Juggernog themed mini-fridge - modeled after the in-game Perk-a-Cola machine. The Juggernog mini-fridge features light and audio straight from the game. This mini-fridge holds up to (12) 12oz cans ensuring you will always have a cold perk nearby.

PERK-A-COLA COASTER SET WITH CUSTOM TIN - Get a set of coasters featuring Juggernog Soda, Revive! Soda, Speed Cola Soda, and Double Tab Root Beer emblems from Call of Duty: Black Ops III Zombies. The set includes a custom tin for storing your coasters.

SEASON PASS - The Call of Duty: Black Ops III Season Pass is your access to four exciting DLC packs.

LIMITED EDITION SPECIALIST CONCEPT ART CARDS - Call of Duty: Black Ops III multiplayer introduces the new Specialist character system, allowing players to choose from 9 elite black operations soldiers - each with their own look, personality, and voice. Each Specialist is featured on their own art card that includes exclusive concept art, biography, and a description of their unique weapon and ability.

THE GIANT BONUS MAP - Zombies returns in all of its undead glory with "The Giant," a Nazi research facility featuring the weapon-upgrading Pack-a-Punch Machine. Re-live the chaos of Treyarch''s classic "Der Riese" Zombies map, picking up the Zombies story with Dempsey, Nikolai, Richtofen, and Takeo where Origins left off.

COLLECTIBLE STEELBOOK - Limited edition steel game case featuring an exclusive design.

IN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: BLACK OPS 3 BONUS PACK - Join the battle with the official Black Ops III personalization pack. Pack includes a custom weapon camo, reticle, and calling card.

IN-GAME BONUS CONTENT: CYBORG - The fan favorite Cyborg Personalization Pack returns in Call of Duty: Black Ops III, fully-loaded with an electrotech-themed weapon skin, uniquely-shaped reticle, and a calling card.

OFFICIAL CALL OF DUTY: BLACK OPS III SOUNDTRACK - Upgrade your playlist with a digital copy of the in-game score.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7s.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 42948, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":84753,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/108745.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648566.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648567.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648568.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', 'Treyarch', '3', null, null), (1271, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season Five', 'There''s a spy in our ranks and a numbers game in Verdansk. Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 5''s offering of free content includes a first-in-the-franchise Double Agent mode in Multiplayer alongside new and classic Black Ops maps, in addition to new Zombies content and new Perks in Warzone that are set to shift the meta and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3lz3.jpg', '2021-08-11', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 165189, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":45068,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48190.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48191.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48192.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/594581.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/594580.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/594579.jpg"]', '{83727,119177,106805,38030,102868,64311,68287,17446,95340,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFp4jbhO7_Y,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dJ21NH_r7oo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QiyagNEzwkc}', 'Activision', '7', null, null), (1272, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season Three', 'The Cold War heats up in Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Season 3. Experience Verdansk in 1984 as Perseus'' brainwashing scheme is revealed. With Wraith, a cold and calculated Perseus spy joining the fray, you''re going to need plenty of backup. Fortunately, Season 3 delivers with new weaponry, Operator Skins, and Legendary Blueprints.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2yxt.jpg', '2021-04-22', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 146505, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":188679,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439082.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439081.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439076.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439077.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439083.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439079.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439084.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439080.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/439078.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0SX5MEvY-ek,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYp6o8n3dAM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kyp8Xkx8jFY}', 'Treyarch', '7', null, null), (1273, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 - Mystery Box Edition', 'The Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 Mystery Box Edition includes:

- A collectible Mystery Box
- 4 Exclusive Zombies Figpins
- An Exclusive Zombies Puzzle and a Darkhorse Zombies Comic with Exclusive cover.
- 3 Zombies lithographs
- A Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 Pop Socket
- A collectible Steelbook
- 10 physical Specialist Icon patches and additional digital content.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bu8.jpg', '2018-10-11', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135985, 1, 56.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128849.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128850.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128851.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1274, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 - Specialist Edition', 'Black Ops is back! Featuring gritty, grounded, fluid Multiplayer combat, the biggest Zombies offering ever with three full undead adventures at launch, and Blackout, where the universe of Black Ops comes to life in one massive battle royale experience featuring the largest map in Call of Duty history, signature Black Ops combat, characters, locations and weapons from the entire Black Ops series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bs7.jpg', '2020-11-09', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 102069, 1, 75.99, '[{"id":75172,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/212646.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128852.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128853.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128854.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1275, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Digital Deluxe Edition', 'Along with a downloadable copy of Call of Duty: Black Ops III, the Digital Deluxe Edition includes a Call of Duty: Black Ops III Season Pass giving you access to four epic DLC packs, access to The Giant Bonus Map for Call of Duty: Black Ops III Zombies, the downloadable Call of Duty: Black Ops III Personalization Pack, and the downloadable Weaponized 115 and Cyborg Personalization Packs.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5f.jpg', '2015-11-06', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 30717, 1, 18.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648555.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648556.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/648557.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1260375.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1276, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Digital Deluxe Edition', 'This Digital Deluxe Edition includes:

- Bonus Map: Nuketown 2025
- Bonus Map: Nuketown Zombies
- Weapon Camo
- Two Player Card Backgrounds
- Official Call of Duty: Black Ops II soundtrack
- Call of Duty: World at War', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ay3.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 81, 11202, 1, 27.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/130236.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413894.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413895.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,68287,106805,105269,55038,68286,520,107318,103301}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1277, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Nuketown 2025 Edition', 'Pushing the boundaries of what fans have come to expect from the record-setting entertainment franchise, Call of Duty: Black Ops II propels players into a near future, 21st Century Cold War, where technology and weapons have converged to create a new generation of warfare.

Call of Duty: Black Ops II - Nuketown 2025 Edition includes:
- a copy of the base game
- the multiplayer map Nuketown 2025', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ay4.jpg', '2012-11-13', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136074, 1, 26.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413900.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413901.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413902.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1278, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Game of the Year Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Game of the Year Edition released only in Japan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5j.jpg', '2017-06-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 202222, 1, 45.99, '[{"id":170002,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1279, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 - Spectre Rising Edition', 'Operation Spectre Rising is the fourth Operation within Call of Duty: Black Ops 4. It reintroduces Spectre from Call of Duty: Black Ops III, and adds characters Sarah Hall, Sergei Kozin, Danny "Blackjack" Li, and the 2025 version of Frank Woods to Blackout.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bs8.jpg', '2019-04-30', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 118547, 1, 47.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7204.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128855.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128856.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1128857.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1280, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Ultimate Edition', 'The iconic Black Ops series is back with Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - the direct sequel to the original and fan-favorite Call of Duty: Black Ops. Black Ops Cold War will drop fans into the depths of the Cold War’s volatile geopolitical battle of the early 1980s. Nothing is ever as it seems in a gripping single-player Campaign, where players will come face-to-face with historical figures and hard truths, as they battle around the globe through iconic locales like East Berlin, Vietnam, Turkey, Soviet KGB headquarters and more.

Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War - Ultimate Edition includes:
- Xbox One and Xbox Series X|S version of Black Ops Cold War
- Land, Sea and Air Pack
- Battle Pass Bundle
- Confrontation Weapons Pack
- Legendary Captain Price Operator Skin', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3k3a.jpg', '2020-12-16', '{5}', 'IGDB', 76, 139887, 1, 53.99, '[{"id":83110,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":190338,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":83111,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46988.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46987.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587845.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587840.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/587841.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mniWW2haNnY,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTS9n_m7TW0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zsBRGCabaog,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3G2JektAKW8}', null, '0', null, null), (1281, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Zombies Chronicles Edition', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III Zombies Chronicles Edition includes the full base game and the Zombies Chronicles content expansion.

Call of Duty: Black Ops III combines three unique game modes: Campaign, Multiplayer, and Zombies, providing fans with the deepest and most ambitious Call of Duty ever.

The Zombies Chronicles content expansion delivers 8 remastered classic Zombies maps from Call of Duty: World at War, Call of Duty: Black Ops and Call of Duty: Black Ops II. Complete maps from the original saga are fully remastered and HD playable within Call of Duty: Black Ops III.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5d.jpg', '2017-08-29', '{5,31}', 'IGDB', 60.2537151141718, 51378, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":110642,"rating_category":{"id":38,"rating":"R 18+"}},{"id":91838,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":110641,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":91697,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":189425,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7287.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199922.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199918.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199917.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199919.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199920.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199921.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199923.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199925.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/199924.jpg"]', '{106805,105269,55038,107318,103301,119177,38030,68287,87622,103292}', '{}', 'Treyarch', '3', null, null), (1282, 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III Game of the Year + Zombie Chronicles Bundle', 'Call of Duty: Black Ops III - Game of the Year + Zombie Chronicles Bundle released only in Japan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7v5n.jpg', '2017-06-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 290254, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":170003,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Treyarch', '3', null, null), (1283, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III', 'The game brings "open combat, " offering players more choices in approaching the single-player missions. Makarov returns as the chief villain of the new campaign.

The newly introduced Carry Forward system will let players keep their progression and inventory from Modern Warfare II. Multiplayer fans can expect 16 maps at the launch and at least 12 coming later. Zombies mode will also return and should offer the largest zombie map to date.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ctx.jpg', '2023-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 61.1639216039185, 260780, 1, 53.99, '[{"id":216756,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":191218,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":162894,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":162897,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":162896,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":162895,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/114515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/114514.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119092.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119093.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119094.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119095.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119096.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119099.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1119100.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITIcmA4Zwa8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UdvfkYt-8k4}', 'Activision', '0', null, '{1957,107}'), (1284, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare', 'Prepare to go dark, Modern Warfare is back!

The stakes have never been higher as players take on the role of lethal Tier One operators in a heart-racing saga that will affect the global balance of power. Call of Duty: Modern Warfare engulfs fans in an incredibly raw, gritty, provocative narrative that brings unrivaled intensity and shines a light on the changing nature of modern war.

Players will be thrust into an immersive narrative spanning the entire game. Experience the ultimate online playground with classic multiplayer or squad-up and play cooperatively in a collection of elite operations, accessible to all skill levels.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1rsg.jpg', '2019-10-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 79.8255963828078, 119177, 1, 30.99, '[{"id":190618,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":101859,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":162727,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":162728,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":91866,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":206338,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":162726,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/8271.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383081.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383083.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383082.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/383084.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314158.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314159.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377973.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377976.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377974.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377975.jpg"]', '{38030,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024,87622}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X8Do_zXNc_E,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V5MoJ0GEuGs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bH1lHCirCGI}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', null, '{1957,107}'), (1285, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 is a first-person shooter video game, developed by Infinity Ward and Sledgehammer Games (Treyarch for the Wii version), with Raven Software having assisted in development and published by Activision.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wkn.jpg', '2011-11-08', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 77.3554911188644, 979, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":226648,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":189431,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":91907,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":126324,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":126323,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":92063,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9755.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/204.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/203.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/201.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/202.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/938.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377989.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377990.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377991.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377992.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1377993.jpg"]', '{545,2033,343,623,2031,1122,1377,1985,622,621}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1xjCdN_rWCE,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hx6Cr1GAkLI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dNToodVM21M}', 'Raven Software', '0', '{194417,194416,194363,194367}', '{1957,107}'), (1286, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Mobilized', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Mobilized is the third Call of Duty video game developed for the Nintendo DS. It features the same first-person shooter gameplay found in its predecessors, and also includes new weapons and vehicles, new mini-games, such as cracking computer terminals, and taking control of UAV Recon Drones and an AC-130 gunship.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3cyl.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 64.544765411057, 21198, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":226659,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":63764,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":17187,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/28627.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632118.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632119.jpg"]', '{8744,15536,8422,28751,10964,64311,68286,564,5812,9538}', '{}', 'Activision', '11', null, '{107,1957}'), (1287, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 is a first-person shooter video game developed by Infinity Ward and published by Activision for the Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3 video game consoles and the Microsoft Windows operating system. Officially announced on February 11, 2009, the game was released worldwide on November 10, 2009. It is the sixth installment of the Call of Duty series and the direct sequel to Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare, continuing the same storyline, with Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 set to end the storyline.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3cwt.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 83.4547306991286, 559, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":226644,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":189238,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":93140,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":92672,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":5334,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/260493.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/260494.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1014.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1011.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1013.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1012.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1010.jpg"]', '{10964,2033,8422,352,6632,471,28751,11171,64311,7331}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TiFSSpYdPuc,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QE7Iiq3tQkM}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', '{154697,22971}', '{1957,107}'), (1288, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Defiance', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 – Defiance is a 2011 first-person shooter video game in the Call of Duty franchise, developed by n-Space for the Nintendo DS. The game takes place in about the same setting as Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 and features many elements of gameplay typical to the series, including the usage of iron sights, vehicular missions, and online play.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5x0h.jpg', '2011-11-08', '{5,24}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 134652, 1, 15.99, '[{"id":226663,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":63767,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":28457,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414064.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414065.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414066.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,19549,83727,102868,8422,64311,95340,10964}', '{}', 'n-Space', '11', null, '{107,1957}'), (1289, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 3', 'Leave no friend behind: The Konni Group has left its indelible mark on Fortune’s Keep and is now occupying another landmass — the infamous Rebirth Island comes back to Call of Duty: Warzone! Rally your squad and investigate this hottest of drops at the start of Season 3. Elsewhere in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, expect one of the biggest Multiplayer map drops ever, with six new Core 6v6 maps. Also included are four free base weapons; eight Aftermarket Parts; Ranked Play (including Resurgence on Rebirth Island); the arrival of Makarov and Snoop Dogg; and two brand-new Operators to the premium Battle Pass, Banshee and Hush.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co83yd.jpg', '2024-04-03', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 298563, 1, 76.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1290, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II drops players into an unprecedented global conflict that features the return of the iconic Operators of Task Force 141.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4sbw.jpg', '2022-10-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.7454744607538, 200165, 1, 78.99, '[{"id":216755,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":144097,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":105507,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":105506,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":105505,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":79460,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":189299,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/77194.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/77192.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/77196.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/77195.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/77193.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/809459.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/809460.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/809461.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/809462.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/809463.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378007.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378009.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378008.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ISc1orDBziY}', 'Activision', '0', null, '{1957,107}'), (1291, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7u8f.jpg', '2011-11-17', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 287021, 1, 23.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1253556.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1253557.jpg"]', '{119177,106805,38030,102868,83727,68287,64311,17446,95340,19549}', '{}', 'Activision', '11', null, '{1957}'), (1292, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 6', 'The Haunting returns and it’s more terrifying than ever! Introducing a horrific cast of Operators alongside the new "Drive Thru" Multiplayer map and six new map variants, the anything-goes Purgatory Limited Time mode, free Rift Runs in Zombies, plus new weapons, Aftermarket Parts, a frighteningly epic Battle Pass, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8vwk.jpg', '2024-09-18', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 318510, 1, 65.99, '[{"id":187700,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":187702,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":187701,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1406610.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,520,83727,111130,102868,64311,95340,68287}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2G13WEfuXpY}', 'Raven Software', '7', null, '{1957,107}'), (1293, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 5', 'Be a champion in Season 5 with two brand-new Core 6v6 maps and the arrival of wrestling royalty with WWE stars Rhea Ripley, “The American Nightmare” Cody Rhodes, and Rey Mysterio. Complete the final story mission for Modern Warfare Zombies and prepare for a clean up on aisle five in Call of Duty: Warzone with the return of the Superstore in Urzikstan.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8j3o.jpg', '2024-07-24', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 308961, 1, 69.99, '[{"id":181242,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356520.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356521.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356522.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356523.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356524.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356525.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356526.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1356527.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JbszDAPQ2Ms}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1294, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 4', 'A disturbing discovery can change everything. A mysterious DNA bomb has been found at Popov Power in Urzikstan, and it’s up to you and your squadmates to unlock the mystery behind this potentially devastating weapon and prevent catastrophe. While you obtain various DNA samples during the ominous Critical Countdown Event, you can also further explore the multitude of bunkers across Urzikstan, potentially unearthing new ways to exit.

The potential outbreak seeps into Multiplayer, with a worldwide assortment of core 6v6 maps, plenty of exhilarating modes, revered weapons, new perks, destructive killstreaks, and battle-ready recon and hazmat inspired gear throughout the Battle Pass, so you can stay protected while remaining deadly calm and effective. One slip-up could alter everything, so suit up, drop in, uncover the truth, and stop the threat!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8ays.jpg', '2024-05-29', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 304046, 1, 70.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331773.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331774.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331760.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331761.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331762.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331763.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331765.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331766.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331767.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331768.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331764.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331769.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331770.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331771.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1331772.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=29zrc9Sba0k,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dc231b2VT8o}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1295, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Reflex Edition', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare: Reflex Edition for Wii arms you with an arsenal of advanced and powerful weaponry and transports you to the most dangerous hotspots around the globe to take on a rogue enemy threatening the world. As both a U.S. Marine and British S.A.S soldier fighting through an unfolding story full of twists and turns, use sophisticated technology, superior firepower, and coordinated land and air strikes on a battlefield where speed, accuracy, and communication are essential to victory.

Modern Warfare - Reflex Edition was ported by Treyarch. The Wii version of Modern Warfare has fewer features than the other console versions. It does not support split-screen multiplayer, and the graphics are not as developed. IGN gave the Wii version of the game, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Reflex Edition, a score of 7.0, saying the visuals and pointer controls are not as polished as the Wii version of World at War, though they did mention the customization options and multiplayer are impressive.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2u59.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.1077737625271, 21199, 1, 17.99, '[{"id":226610,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":191351,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":24077,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154202.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154203.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154204.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154206.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/154205.jpg"]', '{564,8744,5812,649,9495,241,8422,2942,7579,623}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a7LRZQKSsFc}', 'Activision UK', '11', null, '{107,1957}'), (1296, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Force Recon', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Force Recon is a mobile game that can be downloaded for Verizon Wireless members.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3cyk.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135298, 1, 19.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414055.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414056.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414057.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Glu Mobile', '11', null, '{1957,107}'), (1297, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Vault Edition', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II drops players into an unprecedented global conflict that features the return of the iconic Operators of Task Force 141. Available on all platforms, the digital-only Vault Edition offers the most content of any version of Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II.

In addition to the base game – Cross-Gen Bundle version on consoles, Standard Edition on PC – and Early Access to the Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II Open Beta*, the Vault Edition includes the following bonus content:

- Red Team 141 Operator Pack: includes four playable Multiplayer Operators: Ghost, Farah, Price, and Soap. Each Operator comes equipped with a custom-made masked outfit themed around the legendary mercenary Ghost.
- FJX Cinder Weapon Vault
- One season of the Battle Pass and 50 Tier Skips (or its equivalent) at launch.
- Ghost Legacy Pack: Instantly unlock 12 Operator Skins for the Ghost Operator and 10 Assault Rifle Weapon Blueprints for use in Call of Duty: Warzone and Call of Duty: Modern Warfare (2019).
- Players who purchase the Vault Edition through the in-game store in Call of Duty: Warzone, Call of Duty: Vanguard, Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War, or Call of Duty: Modern Warfare will receive 10 hours of Double XP Tokens and 10 hours of Double Weapon XP Tokens for use in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II. XP Tokens will be waiting for you and available to use in-game at launch.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5bdi.jpg', '2022-10-28', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 218405, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":126136,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":101800,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":187782,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":102019,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":104340,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":109199,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/90604.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/884984.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ISc1orDBziY}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', null, null), (1298, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Veteran Package', 'The Veteran Package was a GAME exclusive edition that includes all the contents of the Hardened Edition, but also a "Soap" MacTavish ultra-premium ARTFX Statue sculpted by Kotobukiya and the full downloadable game Call of Duty Classic.

The statue has 3 sets of interchangeable weapons and arms, including: Dual ice-climbing pickaxes, Dual .45 caliber pistols, M14 Enhanced Battle Rifle (affixes to Soap''s back when not in use).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xnk.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 154707, 1, 12.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632103.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632104.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632105.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632106.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276464.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1299, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Trilogy', 'This Trilogy includes Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 and the Stimulus Package (DLC Collection 1), and Call of Duty: Modern Warfare3.

This Trilogy includes all 3 games from the Call of Duty: Modern Warfare franchise. Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare delivers the most thrilling combat action experience available and is the winner of more than 15 perfect score reviews and more than 50 combined Editor''s Choice and Game of the Year awards. Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 picks up immediately following the historic events of its predecessor. Its Stimulus Package includes five maps "Crash," "Overgrown," "Bailout," "Salvage," and "Storm." Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 is the third instalment and epic finale of the series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2eoq.jpg', '2016-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 85, 42975, 1, 36.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/108718.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414068.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/414069.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1300, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 Campaign Remastered', 'The Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 Campaign has been fully remastered with improved textures, animations, physically based rendering, high-dynamic range lighting, and much more. Experience classic missions including Cliffhanger, The Gulag, and Whiskey Hotel as you join Soap, Price, Ghost and the rest of Task Force 141 in the globe-spanning fight to restore order to the world.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2adp.jpg', '2020-03-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 76.4015578840003, 95062, 1, 49.99, '[{"id":109405,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":27588,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":93893,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":190563,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":190136,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47143.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47141.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/377537.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/377538.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/377539.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/377536.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/377540.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378012.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378013.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378010.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378011.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378015.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1378014.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x993FRC4rXA}', 'Activision', '9', null, '{107,1957}'), (1301, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season Six', 'Own the underground!
Dominate firefights as you battle for victory in Verdansk’s newly opened subway system.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2kxq.jpg', '2020-10-29', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140977, 1, 56.99, '[{"id":84874,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9550.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9551.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409493.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409497.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409496.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409495.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409494.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409492.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409491.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/409490.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfpVP9ds9_4}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{1957,107}'), (1302, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Collection', 'A bundle sold for PlayStation 3 that includes Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare and Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7l.jpg', '2010-11-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136209, 1, 25.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '3', null, null), (1303, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season One', 'This epic season of content includes powerful new weapons, exciting new Multiplayer maps and modes, thrilling new Special Ops experiences, and the return of fan-favorite classic content reimagined for Modern Warfare, such as the Crash Multiplayer map – all FREE for the entire community!

The event all introduces Call of Duty’s first ever Battle Pass, which is jam-packed with 100 Tiers of exciting new content to unlock that allows you to customize the way you play.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1z1f.jpg', '2019-12-03', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 129865, 1, 36.99, '[{"id":27099,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":27100,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363936.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363938.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363937.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363933.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363935.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363934.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6-0jkgvdrfs,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1PHAQ-Ij_sw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7jrcedC-bJY}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1304, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 2', 'Survive the decay: After Konni Group infiltrated a Mediterranean island, conducting nefarious experiments that have recently — and catastrophically — changed Fortune’s Keep forever, it’s up to you and your squad to survive the decay, battling and hunting down the undead infiltrating every part of Season 2’s colossal content offering! Help is at hand, as Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes from AMC’s The Walking Dead and CIA Station Chief Kate Laswell headline the Season 2 Battle Pass.

Expect a truly immense content offering, including new Multiplayer maps, four new weapons, Aftermarket Parts (including your own underbarrel chainsaw!), Ranked Play for both Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III and Call of Duty: Warzone, new Zombies Dark Aether Rift investigations, events, challenges, secrets, and a skeletal theme to BlackCell, led by the mysterious John Doe Operator.

CONTENT SUMMARY:

- A massive Multiplayer map offering! Four new Core 6v6 maps arrive across Season 2, including three brand-new 6v6 maps and a fan-favorite remaster.
- Two map variants: Ready up for Hordepoint and the Vortex Mid-Season Playlist, explore two otherworldly themed map variants based on Skidrow and Terminal.
- New War map: Assault a downtown Urzikstan skyscraper from the skies. Welcome to Operation Tin Man.
- Five game modes and a Vortex Playlist: Bring home a win in Team Gun Game; quickscope your way to victory in Snipers Only; enjoy the return of Hordepoint and Bounty; and battle rival Juggernauts in the Juggermosh pit!
- Season 2 Ranked Play: Claim the Ranked Play rewards you unlocked in Season 1, then continue the grind with a full season and all-new rewards to earn.
- New Ninja Vest: Favoring those knives only? Equip the Ninja Vest for silent running, as well as a bonus knife and throwing star ammo.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co83y9.jpg', '2024-02-07', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 285601, 1, 61.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233764.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233765.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233766.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233767.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233768.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233769.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233770.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233771.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233772.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233773.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233774.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233775.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233776.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233777.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233778.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233779.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233780.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233781.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233782.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1233783.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QedQVc-o5So}', 'High Moon Studios', '7', null, '{1957,107}'), (1305, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season Two', 'The Al-Qatala threat is growing. Put a halt to their devastating nuclear plans in Season Two, a thrilling new season for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare that is jam-packed with free content for all players.

Assemble your squad and fight across a mix of new maps, including two traditional Multiplayer maps, a new Ground War battleground, and an additional Gunfight map. Join the close-quarters firefight in Rust, a fan-favorite map making its return to Modern Warfare. Wreak havoc as Ghost, the iconic and intimidating Special Forces Operator, and load up two new functional Weapons with a new Assault Rifle and SMG available for all online players.

A stream of free content will arrive throughout Season Two, which overall includes: four Multiplayer maps, new in-game Challenges and Rewards, limited-time game modes and playlists, two functional Weapons, as well as a host of new Weapon Blueprints, Operator Skins, accessories, and much more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1z1i.jpg', '2020-02-11', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 129866, 1, 61.99, '[{"id":27101,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":27102,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363994.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363995.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363996.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363997.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/363993.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,106805,83727,102868,64311,95340,68287,17446,34024}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gvyz39z0-7A,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SczPkU9_aHs}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1306, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Season 1', 'Prepare for an incredible Season 1, bringing a massive drop of free and premium content, including five free weapons, four new Multiplayer maps, multiple modes, the next Zombies story mission, the arrival and integration of Call of Duty: Warzone and the new Urzikstan map, an all-new 100+ Tiers of Battle Pass content to earn, BlackCell, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co83ya.jpg', '2023-12-06', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 279645, 1, 56.99, '[{"id":161878,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/124740.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206727.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206724.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206729.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206728.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1206730.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1307, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Remastered', 'One of the most critically-acclaimed games in history. Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare is back, remastered in true high-definition, featuring enhanced textures, rendering, high-dynamic range lighting, and much more to bring a new generation experience to fans.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wla.jpg', '2016-11-04', '{5}', 'IGDB', 82.671261147575, 24920, 1, 30.99, '[{"id":92275,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":226655,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":108324,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":91863,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":58726,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":125199,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7235.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/32628.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34221.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34224.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34223.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371156.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371153.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371154.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371155.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371157.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371158.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371159.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371160.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371161.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371162.jpg"]', '{28751,68286,95340,64311,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,43367}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=frcic8ApwJ0,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-eMi1xJ2dM}', 'Certain Affinity', '9', '{168155}', '{107,1957}'), (1308, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 01', 'Get Ready for a New Era — Season 01 Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II and Call of Duty: Warzone 2.0 will deliver action on all fronts: the next iteration of the massive free-to-play Battle Royale experience featuring the much-anticipated DMZ mode, reimagined maps in Multiplayer, and an additional Special Ops mission prior to the first Raid Episode. There will be plenty of content across both games through all-new Battle Pass, football-themed event, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co5rg4.jpg', '2022-11-16', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 225441, 1, 78.99, '[{"id":189945,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924382.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924398.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924379.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924380.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924381.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924383.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924384.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924385.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924386.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924387.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924390.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924394.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924388.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924389.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924391.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924392.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924393.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924395.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924396.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/924397.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXNOOHvTqgA}', 'Activision Publishing', '7', null, null), (1309, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 05', 'When darkness falls, the shadows will rise.
Shadow Company and Task Force 141 face off in Season 05 of Call of Duty Warzone and MWII Which side will you choose?

Graves is alive.
Even if Task Force 141 successfully secured the warhead as part of their RAID, Farah lost her brother — and AQ asset — Hadir . . . but not before he revealed that a greater threat is on the horizon.
Unbeknownst to Price, Gaz, and the rest of 141, Farah and Alex head back into Urzikstan. A meeting has been set up with a former enemy who apparently wasn’t incinerated in his tank at the Fuerzas Especiales Headquarters in South America.
Three elite leaders pore over a map of Al Mazrah, where Graves has intel on a new ultranationalist threat now present in the AO, the same group Hadir could not speak of in his dying breaths:
The Konni Group.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6x9x.jpg', '2023-08-02', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 259766, 1, 69.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106468.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106469.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106471.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106473.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106476.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106477.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106479.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106478.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106474.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106475.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106470.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1106472.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GMNTkFv6iG8}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, null), (1310, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare', 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare differs from previous installments of the Call of Duty series. Previous Call of Duty games have a distinct three country-specific campaign style, while Call of Duty 4 has a more film-like plot with interlaced story lines from the perspectives of Sgt. Paul Jackson of the Marines 1st Force Recon and Sgt. ''Soap'' MacTavish of the British 22nd SAS Regiment.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1wko.jpg', '2007-11-05', '{5,13}', 'IGDB', 86.106674639975, 623, 1, 15.99, '[{"id":226642,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":91908,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":94776,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":43578,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":62497,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":187906,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9412.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/258081.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/654.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/653.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/651.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/655.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/652.jpg"]', '{622,545,979,625,621,343,2033,2031,241,277}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhuIjNSg7Gg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8e-i2D-2GAc}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', '{292781}', '{1957,107}'), (1311, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season Four', 'New Weapons. New Operators. New Game Modes. Plus a reloaded Battle Pass that introduces Captain Price to the fight.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2auz.jpg', '2020-06-14', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135220, 1, 60.99, '[{"id":28587,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":28588,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9112.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389273.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389274.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7N8VDutRs_U}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1312, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare', 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare Mobile is a spin-off game of the Call of Duty series and is a prequel to the main game. The game was developed by GLU Mobile and published by Activision for mobile phones.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2adc.jpg', '2007-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135294, 1, 25.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632130.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632131.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632132.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Glu Mobile', '11', null, '{107,1957}'), (1313, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 03', 'Weapons hot vaqueros.
Alejandro and Valeria face off in Season 03', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6c39.jpg', '2023-04-12', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 243777, 0, 57.99, '[{"id":132385,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1022653.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8WMiAAPOC-k,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C04Oj2yEynY}', null, '7', null, null), (1314, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 02', 'Gear up for Season 02 in Modern Warfare II and Call of Duty Warzone 2.0 and have you and your squad be victorious when the mist clears.
Resurgence Mode returns on a new battleground in Warzone 2.0 starting in Season 02.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co63ey.jpg', '2023-02-15', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 235080, 1, 72.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/975815.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/975816.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/975817.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y_Bn8Iw-iJk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dm7cJsTXm0g}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, null), (1315, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Dark Edition', 'This version includes:

- Call of Duty: Modern Warfare game
- Steelbook
- Night Vision Goggles
- Display Stand for Night Vision Goggles
- Custom in-game Tactical Knife (Digital Item)
- “All Ghillied Up” Operator Pack
- “Crew Expendable” Operator Pack
- “War Pig” Operator Pack
- Call of Duty Endowment (C.O.D.E.) Animated Calling Card', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8ibh.jpg', '2019-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 134229, 1, 47.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413881.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413882.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413883.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1316, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare', 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare is a game in the Call of Duty series franchise, developed specifically for the Nintendo DS. It was released on November 5, 2007. Like Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare for traditional consoles, the Nintendo DS version takes place in modern day and offers players modern weapons. The game features many elements of gameplay typical to the series.

The Nintendo DS version of the game allows the player to assume the roles of several anonymous soldiers, who are either affiliated with the British S.A.S. or American armed forces. Unlike the console and PC version of Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare, players do not directly impact the outcome of the war.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2adb.jpg', '2007-11-05', '{5}', 'IGDB', 57.3035670503836, 134651, 1, 26.99, '[{"id":226643,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":63760,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388156.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/388157.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'n-Space', '11', null, '{107,1957}'), (1317, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 04', 'Al Mazrah, Urzikstan, Ashika Island, Las Almas . . . and now, Vondel.
The waterfront district of a Baroque European city where centuries of old-world history blends with modern architectural developments, Vondel saw a complete evacuation due to an imminent attack threat, right as Operators descended into the darkness of the Al Mazrah Koschei Complex during a fierce sandstorm at the culmination of Season 03.
While Vondel is a brand-new locale for Operators to explore, the ensuing chaos is part of a plan activated by a familiar and infamous masked figure, whose forces are operating in both Al Mazrah and Vondel. Peer through the dust clouds, and you’ll recognize the apparent leader of these unknown forces:
His name is Nikto. And he’s ready to Run This Town.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6nh0.jpg', '2023-06-14', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 252460, 1, 50.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066879.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066880.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066881.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066882.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066883.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066884.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066885.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066886.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066887.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066888.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066877.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1066878.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ym1GUMxgmcI}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, null), (1318, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season Five', 'A new faction makes a bold first impression by opening up Verdansk Stadium and getting the Train Station rolling. Welcome to opening day.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2gpq.jpg', '2020-08-05', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136976, 1, 71.99, '[{"id":29516,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9349.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9348.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396616.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396619.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396620.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396617.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396618.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396623.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396621.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/396622.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xvjn6BopsV8}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1319, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Season Three', 'Join the Fight as One Worldwide Community!
All players, across Modern Warfare and Warzone, can unlock the following throughout the season for FREE:
• Three new functional weapons, including a versatile Marksman Rifle
• New, exciting game modes and playlists to experience with friends
• Updated Challenges to unlock free Operator Skins, Weapon Blueprints, and XP tokens

The Season Three Battle Pass is jam-packed with content that is fit for any situation, such as the pulse-pounding CQB of Multiplayer and Gunfight, to the long-range firefights of Warzone, and everything in between.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2a93.jpg', '2020-04-07', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 135219, 1, 61.99, '[{"id":28586,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":28585,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9111.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/9110.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389267.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389269.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389272.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389270.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389271.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389268.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uInQvulS-m8}', 'Activision', '7', null, '{107,1957}'), (1320, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Collection 1', 'Redeploying with an arsenal of content unlike any in franchise history, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3’s first downloadable “Collection” arrives stockpiled with not only four Multiplayer/Survival Mode Maps, but two Special Ops Missions—the first time Call of Duty has ever made Special Ops downloadable online.

Armed with just this one content pack, players can choose between heading to a militarized Central Park in Liberation, destroying scenic vistas in a seaside Italian getaway in Piazza, raining glass on New York passersby from 70-stories-up in Overwatch, and battling beside a downed Air Force One in Black Box.

As if that breadth of multiplayer variety wasn’t enough, fans of Special Ops can hop aboard snowmobiles to infiltrate a diamond mine in Black Ice or head to India, where Negotiator will leave the fate of hostages in their hands.

In a class of its own with half-a-dozen forms of content, Modern Warfare 3’s first downloadable “Collection” offers a range of combat and co-op the likes of which has never been seen before.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4kdi.jpg', '2012-05-08', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 90, 194363, 1, 5.99, '[{"id":62380,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":191095,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757415.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757416.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757417.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757418.jpg"]', '{106805,119177,38030,87622,55038,105269,118218,19164,19549,107318}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIaVtZetOa4}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '1', null, '{107,1957}'), (1321, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Collection 2', 'The second Modern Warfare 3 DLC Collection launches with all-new Multiplayer/Survival Mode Maps, Special Ops Missions and the debut of Face Off maps. Totally new to the franchise, Face Off distills all the fun and intensity of multiplayer into a new breed of 1 vs. 1 and 2 vs. 2 close combat. In addition to this all-new game-play experience, Collection 2 deploys with 3 multiplayer maps and 2 Special Ops Missions (Iron Clad and Kill Switch), offering fans new venues to test their Multiplayer and Special Ops skills.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4kdk.jpg', '2012-06-21', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 194367, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":191114,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":62366,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757422.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757419.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757420.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757421.jpg"]', '{106805,119177,87622,38030,118218,19164,55038,105269,103328,19549}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-4fgHGu0Ak}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1957}'), (1322, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Operator Edition', 'This version contains the base game and the Operator Pack. This pack consists in three bundles, All Ghillied Up, Crew Expendable and War Pigs, all of them based on Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ubl.jpg', '2019-10-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 119894, 1, 39.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139472.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139473.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139474.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', null, null), (1323, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Vault Edition', 'The Vault Edition includes:

- Cross Gen Bundle of Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III
- Available in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II and Call of Duty: Warzone:
-- Soap Operator Pack*
-- Zombie Ghost Operator Skin*
-- Soul Harvester Tracer Weapon Blueprint*
- Nemesis Operator Pack
- 2 Weapon Vaults**
- BlackCell (1 Season) + 30 additional Tier Skips***', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8qlj.jpg', '2023-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 276133, 1, 59.99, '[{"id":159058,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":159059,"rating_category":{"id":17,"rating":"Z"}},{"id":159061,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":159062,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":159060,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":159063,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":159064,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/122621.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/144534.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187787.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187788.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187789.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187790.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187791.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187792.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187793.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1187796.jpg"]', null, '{}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '0', null, null), (1324, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Precision Edition', 'Only available on GameStop. Contains the base game, Steelbook, KontrolFreek Call of Duty: Modern Warfare-branded Performance Thumbsticks and Controller Skin, and the in-game content from the Digital Operator Edition.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7r.jpg', '2019-10-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136342, 1, 39.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139478.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139479.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139480.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', null, null), (1326, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Resurgence Pack', 'The Resurgence Pack is a map pack for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare, it features five multiplayer maps, costs 1200 MS points for the Xbox 360, and US $14.99 for PS3 and PC. As with the Stimulus Package, this map pack was exclusive to the Xbox 360 for a limited time before being released for PC and PlayStation 3. Out of the included maps, two are from Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare, and three are brand new maps. Strike and Vacant return from the fourth installment of the series. Carnival, Trailer Park, and Fuel are the three new maps that are included.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3d9z.jpg', '2010-06-03', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 154697, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":88828,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/524778.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/524779.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/524781.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/524776.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/524777.jpg"]', '{100800,113895,57296,25636,57372,105233,95340,87728,65672,111835}', '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1327, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Stimulus Package', 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Stimulus Package is a commercial DLC for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2. It adds five new multiplayer-maps:

- Bailout (An apartment complex)
- Overgrown (A village with open fields; known from Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare)
- Crash (An urban area; known from Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare)
- Salvage (A snowy junkyard)
- Storm (A warehouse complex)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3d9f.jpg', '2010-03-30', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 22971, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":88829,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413836.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413835.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '1', null, null), (1328, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Prestige Edition', 'The Prestige Edition includes all content of the Hardened Edition, as well as fully-functional night vision goggles imprinted with the Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 logo and a sculpted head stand of "Soap" MacTavish.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3da6.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 154704, 1, 7.99, '[{"id":88827,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632191.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632192.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632193.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276463.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FMSS12iY1X0}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1329, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 - Hardened Edition', 'The Hardened Edition comes with the game disc (a different print, the MW2 green and black instead of the figure in the desert) and the manual, along with an art book, a steel case, and a code to download the original Call of Duty game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3da7.jpg', '2009-11-10', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 154705, 1, 18.99, '[{"id":88826,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632208.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632209.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/632210.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '3', null, null), (1330, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Hardened Edition', 'Activision Blizzard''s top-selling first-person shooter franchise marches on with Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3. Players must deal with the fallout from the devastating attacks on U.S. and British soil in a storyline that picks up where 2009''s Modern Warfare 2 left off. The single-player campaign has you battling Russian ultranationalists, led by Vladimir Markov, as members of the U.S. Delta Force and British SAS. You''ll battle across war-torn areas of New York City, London, Paris, Mogadishu, Dubai, and other regions as you prepare to end the global threat once and for all.

As with previous entries in the Call of Duty series, Modern Warfare 3''s campaign features a heavily scripted, cinematic experience with Hollywood-style special effects. One new mission, for example, has you involved in underwater travel with a sonar-equipped submersible watercraft. You''ll then fight inside an enemy-controlled submarine before guiding an inflatable raft across turbulent waters while a naval battle rages nearby. Other sequences have you firing mounted guns, driving vehicles, and more while explosions light up the landscape.

Returning to the game is the cooperative Spec Ops mode that features a series of standalone missions on different maps. New to Spec Ops is a survival option that has you and either a friend or a computer partner battling waves of enemy forces. Shooting down enemies earns you cash, which can be used to purchase new perks, items, weapons, and other upgrades. You''ll also be able to earn bonuses by working together as a team and maintaining kill streaks.

The heart of the game is once again the 18-player online component, which introduces all-new maps and a variety of enhancements to the format introduced in Modern Warfare 2. Popular features such as kill-streak awards, experience points, weapons-based achievements, and perks return, allowing you to customize your character as you progress. An optional subscription service entitled "Call of Duty Elite" will allow players to track detailed statistics such as win-loss records, kill-death ratios, time played, most successful maps, favorite weapons, and much more.

Hardened Edition bonus items include a Steelbook case, collectible field journal, special ops juggernaut outfit for your Xbox Live avatar, premium membership to Call of Duty Elite, and special founder status on Call of Duty Elite. Call of Duty Elite''s premium membership includes all future downloadable content (DLC) for Modern Warfare 3, of which there are 20 pieces of DLC expected within the first nine months following the game''s release.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7p.jpg', '2011-12-08', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 47425, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":111634,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":111635,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":111633,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":111636,"rating_category":{"id":16,"rating":"D"}},{"id":125877,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":167098,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47542.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47540.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413875.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413876.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413877.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '0', null, null), (1331, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Ultimate Edition', 'This version includes all content released for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4a7u.jpg', '2013-12-31', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 99951, 1, 16.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413878.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413879.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/413880.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Sledgehammer Games', '3', null, null), (1332, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Tech Luxe Pro Pack', 'Get Call of Duty Points* and in-game content for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III and Call of Duty: Warzone.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobrq0.jpg', '2024-01-24', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 291077, 1, 65.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265102.jpg"]', '{100800,113895,57296,25636,57372,105233,95340,87728,65672,111835}', '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1333, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Cyberjunkie: Pro Pack', 'Get Call of Duty Points* and in-game content for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III and Call of Duty: Warzone.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobrpz.jpg', '2024-04-12', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 298224, 1, 60.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1306206.jpg"]', '{100800,113895,57296,25636,57372,105233,95340,87728,65672,111835}', '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1334, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Collection 3: Chaos Pack', 'With its third DLC Collection, Modern Warfare 3 drops a combat-heavy care package of Special Ops Chaos mode, 4 new Special Ops missions (Arctic Recon, Light ''Em Up, Special Delivery, and Vertigo), and 3 Face Off maps (Intersection, U-Turn, and Vortex) for the ultimate trifecta in solo and co-op gameplay. High-altitude Special Ops challenges put tactical skills to the test, with players navigating armed drones above a Russian destroyer and evading RPGs from the roof of a helicopter-swarmed hotel. Upping the ante further, Face Off firefights pit players head-to-head on a six-lane stretch of desert highway, at an abandoned crossroads near a New York overpass, and near the path of a violent tornado.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4kfw.jpg', '2012-09-13', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 194416, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":62399,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":187892,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757529.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757528.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757527.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757526.jpg"]', '{106805,119177,87622,38030,118218,19164,55038,105269,103328,19549}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efVszi4CoYg}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1957}'), (1335, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare - Operator Enhanced Edition', 'This version includes:

- Custom In-Game Tactical Knife
- All Ghillied Up Operator Pack
- Crew Expendable Operator Pack
- War Pig Operator Pack
- 3,000 Call of Duty Points
- Prestige Token in Call of Duty: Black Ops 4
- Classic Captain Price Character in Blackout for Call of Duty: Black Ops 4
- 5 Reserve Cases in Call of Duty: Black Ops 4', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ubk.jpg', '2019-10-25', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 119895, 1, 38.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139475.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139476.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1139477.jpg"]', '{95340,38030,32902,119177,106805,87622,103302,43367,95308,520}', '{}', 'Infinity Ward', '0', null, null), (1336, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II - Season 06: The Haunting', 'Prepare for frightening thrills, the shambling undead, squad hunts to take down grotesque monsters, and those infamous jump-scares as The Haunting returns to Call of Duty! The Hellmouth has opened, spilling unearthly creatures from the underworld, and a creeping terror is slowly swallowing all souls as it infects the entirety of Al Mazrah, reaching the bloodred canals of Vondel, and beyond!

It appears a clandestine group known as the Dark Ritual Operators have located and opened a terrifying Hellmouth. After the gate’s seals were ripped apart, a cacophony of otherworldly gurgling resounded, before a veritable panoply of the grotesque poured forth from their opened prison…

All Operators should ready themselves for “Operation Nightmare” and prepare to battle and repel these aberrant threats!

Fortunately, in the ensuing chaos, the Dark Ritual Operators left the gate open in time for backup to arrive in the form of Spawn, the hellacious antihero who is now tasked with sending these monsters and their ilk back to the underworld.

The Haunting event officially begins at mid-season, bringing Halloween-themed maps, modes, events and more across both games. Prepare for spine-chilling scares and ferocious battles ahead at launch with the release of four new Multiplayer maps, a Battle Pass stocked with devilishly entertaining new Operators and Weapon Blueprints, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co792i.jpg', '2023-09-27', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 272531, 1, 77.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dz1yRa0LzyU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fIcIw7UH6Rg}', 'Infinity Ward', '7', null, null), (1337, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Remastered - Variety Map Pack', 'The Variety Map Pack DLC for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Remastered includes four remastered multiplayer maps from the original game.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6ig9.jpg', '2017-04-20', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 168155, 1, 38.99, '[{"id":87310,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":138692,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":167091,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":167093,"rating_category":{"id":33,"rating":"18"}},{"id":146387,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":167092,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/83584.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/612112.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/612113.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/612114.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,83727,102868,95340,64311,34024,68287,17446}', '{}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{107,1957}'), (1338, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Warhammer 40K Crossover Pack', 'As part of the Season 2 Reloaded update for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, three new Warhammer 40,000 Store Bundles are on the way. The first pack is inspired by the Space Marines, and includes Scout armour Operator Skins from the Ultramarines and Blood Angels 10th Companies, along with melee weapons inspired by the iconic chainsword as well as Weapon Blueprints with unique Warhammer tracers.

Tracer Pack: Warhammer 40,000 Sisters of Battle lets you armour up in the regalia of the Adepta Sororitas, complete with two Warhammer-themed Weapon Blueprints, custom tracers, and a host of other customisation items for your profile. Lastly, don the distinctive green-and-tan camouflaged armour of the Kasrkin with the final pack, including a Munitorum-issued blade, tracers that make your weapons look like they’re firing las bolts, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coahaj.jpg', null, '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 302211, 1, 79.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137372.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137371.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137370.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137369.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/137373.jpg"]', '[]', '{68287,119177,38030,106805,78770,105269,55038,68286,107318,103301}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OMUtkkm0ew}', null, '13', null, null), (1341, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Collection 4: Final Assault', 'Saluting Modern Warfare 3''s Season of Content, the fourth and final DLC collection deploys with five all-new Multiplayer Maps. Surrounded by mountains, "Gulch" sends combatants into a forgotten mining town with only mine shafts and equipment sheds for cover. The Jersey coast awaits in "Boardwalk," where fun in the sun means facing enemies on the beach. Players must earn their sea legs in "Off Shore" and "Decommission," where deadly oceanic oil rigs and a maze of rotting ocean liners provide the perfect setting for shoreline-based combat. Rounding out the collection is a trip to New Orleans’ war-torn French Quarter, where "Parish" pits players against one another amid the city''s rubble.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4kfx.jpg', '2012-10-10', '{5,24,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 194417, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":62401,"rating_category":{"id":12,"rating":"18"}},{"id":187903,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757530.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757531.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757532.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/757533.jpg"]', '{106805,119177,87622,38030,118218,19164,55038,105269,103328,19549}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wxr5KlRSvTA}', 'Activision', '1', null, '{1957,107}'), (1343, 'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III - Tracer Pack: Nuptial Nightmare Ultra Skin Pro Pack', 'Get Call of Duty Points and in-game content for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III and Call of Duty: Warzone.

Pack includes:

- 2400 Call of Duty Points
- Operator Skin
- 2x Weapon Blueprints
- Emblem
- Weapon Sticker
- Large Decal
- Loading Screen', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coag4h.jpg', '2024-09-25', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 317728, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1399903.jpg"]', '{100800,113895,57296,25636,57372,105233,95340,87728,65672,111835}', '{}', 'Activision', '13', null, null), (1344, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare - Variety Map Pack', 'The Variety Map Pack includes four new multiplayer maps featuring a variety of locations.

“Creek,” a wide-open village ravaged by combat where concealment is the difference between life and death; “Broadcast,” fight throughout an enemy communications building with confined corridors and wide-open parking lots; “Chinatown,” a foggy downtown district, lit only by a full moon and the neon glow of the city; and “Killhouse,” featuring a desolate training warehouse filled with a variety of building mock-ups and soft and hard cover points.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xne.jpg', '2008-04-04', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 292781, 1, 11.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276456.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276457.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276458.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1276459.jpg"]', '{38030,119177,106805,58095,83727,102868,64311,68287,398382,385988}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NgAUGs5JkL0}', 'Infinity Ward', '1', null, null), (1345, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare - Game of the Year Edition', 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare differs from previous installments of the Call of Duty series. Previous Call of Duty games have a distinct three country-specific campaign style, while Call of Duty 4 has a more film-like plot with interlaced story lines from the perspectives of Sgt. Paul Jackson of the Marines 1st Force Recon and Sgt. ''Soap'' MacTavish of the British 22nd SAS Regiment.

The Game of the Year Edition includes a code for the Variety Map Pack, adding 4 new multiplayer maps: Broadcast, Creek, Chinatown and Killhouse.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7vo7.jpg', '2008-04-01', '{5,13}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 290723, 1, 18.99, '[{"id":190810,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}},{"id":170218,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":170214,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":170215,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":170216,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":170217,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1262723.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1262724.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1262725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1262726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1262727.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,68287,106805,103302,112078,8422,83727,102868,10964}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhuIjNSg7Gg}', 'Activision', '3', null, null), (1346, 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare - Limited Collector''s Edition', 'Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare differs from previous installments of the Call of Duty series. Previous Call of Duty games have a distinct three country-specific campaign style, while Call of Duty 4 has a more film-like plot with interlaced story lines from the perspectives of Sgt. Paul Jackson of the Marines 1st Force Recon and Sgt. ''Soap'' MacTavish of the British 22nd SAS Regiment.

This limited collector''s edition includes:

- Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
- Bonus DVD with making-of scenes, a documentary of the British S.A.S., a level walk-through by the developer, and some campaign trailers. (Europe-only)
- Poster featuring the cover art of the game.
- Hardcover art book narrated by the developers and artists, with concept, development and final in-game artwork. (Xbox 360 & European Windows-only)
- Digital copy of the Brady Games official strategy guide (Windows-only)', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7r6y.jpg', '2007-11-05', '{5,13}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 286606, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":166677,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":166679,"rating_category":{"id":26,"rating":"19+"}},{"id":166678,"rating_category":{"id":22,"rating":"18"}},{"id":166680,"rating_category":{"id":37,"rating":"MA 15+"}},{"id":166676,"rating_category":{"id":11,"rating":"16"}},{"id":189681,"rating_category":{"id":6,"rating":"M"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1239995.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1239997.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1239994.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1239996.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1239998.jpg"]', '{119177,38030,68287,106805,103302,112078,8422,83727,102868,10964}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LhuIjNSg7Gg}', 'Activision', '0', null, null), (1347, 'Disgaea 1 Complete', 'A version of Disgaea: Hour of Darkness, including the added content in Afternoon of Darkness and Disgaea PC, was released for Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4 on October 9, 2018, retitled as Disgaea 1 Complete. Some elements of the game were updated, including adding new higher resolution sprites in the same style as Disgaea 5, changing character art images with the Disgaea 5 artstyle, as well as retroactively replacing some generic humanoid and monster classes that did not appear since Disgaea: Hour of Darkness with classes that do appear in later games in the series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2xcl.jpg', '2018-07-26', '{12,13,15,16,24,31}', 'IGDB', 80.3619422778841, 82373, 1, 56.99, '[{"id":28660,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":97217,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}},{"id":25500,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":92995,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12121.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389783.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389782.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/210746.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/210747.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/210748.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389784.jpg"]', '{19164,26845,25311,13196,35994,14394,27092,26574,24426,27209}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EFB1Xhu5n8I,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NP1EbU75qU,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nS9eHIeBGVk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tpvvBv86pqI}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '9', null, '{987}'), (1348, 'Disgaea: Afternoon of Darkness', 'Disgaea is a tactical role playing game. Battle gameplay takes place on a map divided into a square grid. The player controls a squad of humanoid units and monsters, which each occupy a single square of the grid and do combat with a group of enemies. Depending on the character and attack selected, the player will be able to deal damage to a specific enemy unit or a designated region of the map. Combat ends when all enemy units or all of the player''s units are destroyed.
Humanoid characters may lift and throw other units across the map in order to allow allies to move further or force enemies to keep their distance. This even allows the player to capture enemies by throwing them into the base panel; these enemies then become allies, and can be used on subsequent maps. The chance of capturing an enemy in this manner depends on several factors. Failure to capture the enemy will result in the death of all characters inside the base panel, and the enemy will survive.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2nl8.jpg', '2006-11-30', '{12,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 85.0312244249104, 22528, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":28655,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":28656,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389772.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389767.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389771.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389770.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389768.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389769.jpg"]', '{13196,19164,26845,7615,27209,27092,24426,28010,28182,19404}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EFJB6wMYBCM}', 'NIS America', '10', null, '{987}'), (1349, 'Disgaea 2: Dark Hero Days', 'In the peaceful world of Veldime, humans rarely encountered monsters. That was until Overlord Zenon cursed the land and all who reside within. With the curse in place, the humans became monsters and ravaged the world. It is up to Adell, the last remaining human, to oppose Overlord Zenon''s tyranny and restore peace and harmony to Veldime. In Disgaea 2, players will take on the role of a young fighter named Adell and travel the Netherworld to defeat the evil overlord Zenon. Battles will take place on a 3D grid-based field. During combat, players will take turns with the enemy to move and attack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1pn4.jpg', '2009-03-26', '{12,15,16}', 'IGDB', 80.0973597359736, 21851, 1, 20.99, '[{"id":28665,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":79867,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":28666,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/306971.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/306973.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/306972.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389843.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389842.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389844.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389846.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389845.jpg"]', '{19164,13196,7615,27209,27092,24426,28010,28182,19404,26268}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qn4qqguYpQA,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pqFqyQDWyQ8,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N3OpCJjWtfs}', 'NIS America', '10', null, '{987}'), (1350, 'Disgaea 7 Complete', 'A complete edition of Disgaea 7: Vows of the Virtueless containing all existing downloadable content and bonus items, plus a new bonus story, new characters, and new post-game elements.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobq1v.jpg', '2023-10-03', '{12,15}', 'IGDB', 83, 295622, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":218294,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":231543,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":231544,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257340.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257341.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/257342.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292936.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292937.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292938.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292939.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292940.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1292941.jpg"]', '{19404,113402,103232,119598,13196,7615,77597,68393,109339,111187}', '{}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '10', null, null), (1351, 'Disgaea DS', 'Players will initially take on the role of Overlord Laharl, a young demon prince who has just woken from a two-year long nap and finds out that his father, who was the king, has passed away. In order to regain his rightful title as King of the Netherworld, Laharl sets off on a demonic adventure, but must do so with a back stabbing servant, love stupid angel, and a few disgruntled penguins who are looking for trouble.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6mf4.jpg', '2008-06-26', '{12,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 79.145453614184, 21056, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":28657,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":28658,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/28541.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156571.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156570.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156569.jpg"]', '{13196,26845,7615,27209,27092,24426,28010,28182,19404,26268}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tTeJAFQLcQs}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '11', null, '{987}'), (1352, 'Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny', 'The first new Disgaea game in six years is here! Meet Zed, a zombie that has risen above them all except one - a God of Destruction!

Can a mere Netherworld zombie rise up and destroy a god? Find out in the newest installment of the Disgaea series! Features such as Super Reincarnation, 3D visuals (a first for this series), and adjustable gameplay settings make this the perfect game for both new and old Disgaea fans!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3bd4.jpg', '2021-01-28', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 138953, 1, 66.99, '[{"id":56283,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":97236,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":119683,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":37399,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12015.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400375.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400376.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400371.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400372.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400373.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/400374.jpg"]', '{13196,19404,7615,19164,111187,26845,28010,27092,119598,24426}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OVwk-uPoa5I}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1353, 'Disgaea D2: A Brighter Darkness', 'Disgaea D2: A Brighter Darkness is a tactical RPG in the Disgaea series. The game is a sequel to 2003''s Disgaea: Hour of Darkness for the PlayStation 2, where the respective main characters of that game will again be the focus. Gameplay in Disgaea D2 remains the same as other core Disgaea games in the series. Monster Mounting is a new feature that replaces Magichange from Disgaea 3 and Disgaea 4. Characters can also build relationships with each other and their compatibility is determined by a heart scale of 1 to 5. Another feature is the Cheat Shop, which allows the player to modify certain attributes such as lowering the gain rate of something like experience, to raise the gain rate of something else, like Hell.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co25nx.jpg', '2013-03-20', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 76.4645098869491, 7299, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":188620,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":33500,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2137.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2136.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2135.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2134.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11907.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11906.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11908.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11910.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11909.jpg"]', '{14394,660,9938,2365,22387,19164,27092,7027,13196,24426}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EiL-lfDFczo}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1354, 'Disgaea RPG', 'A departure from the grid-based tactics gameplay of the main series, the game uses teams of 5 characters, from throughout the series, to fight waves of enemies in turn-based battles.
Characters can have star ratings from 2 to 6, that have various level caps with the end goal of a 6 star character being upgraded to level 9999.
The game is region locked in Japan.

Originally released in March 2019 with bugs and server issues, the game was taken offline to work on fixes and improve the game. it was re-launched in November 2019.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1vy0.jpg', '2019-03-19', '{12,15,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 115271, 1, 48.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/66083.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349741.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349740.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349744.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349742.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349743.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349739.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/349738.jpg"]', '{27092,106987,96217,81249,19164,55038,25311,55199,120564,35994}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SLoZJearzHo,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=riYT9lhHZzw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zBkNZCH9Rc}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1355, 'Disgaea 3: Absence of Detention', 'Disgaea 3 is a sequel to Disgaea, a hardcore, turn-based strategy RPG. The game follows the exploits of Mao, the most honored student at Evil Academy, a school where the tardiest, laziest, and rudest demons receive the highest marks. The son of the school chairman, Mao has never once attended class nor opened a textbook. He longs to overthrow his father and assume the title of Overlord, which he decides he must become a hero to achieve. Join him on his zany adventure filled with witty dialogue, exciting events, and thrilling strategy battles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2h0n.jpg', '2011-12-17', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 88.2774068589823, 18370, 1, 6.99, '[{"id":29400,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":29401,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115460.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115462.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115461.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115458.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115459.jpg"]', '{660,26845,22387,10297,19164,14394,9938,2365,27092,7027}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vlARRglAC4M,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Av0DTPSfSTI}', 'NIS America', '11', null, '{987}'), (1356, 'Disgaea 2 PC', 'When Adell and his family accidentally kidnap the Princess of the Netherworld, all hell breaks loose. Adell races to return the Princess to her home, where he hopes to defeat the Overlord and break the curse on his world.

A port of the game for PCs titled Disgaea 2 PC was released on January 30, 2017, and includes all content from the PS2 and PSP versions, along with an updated interface and support for mouse and keyboard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tvx.jpg', '2017-01-30', '{12,16,24,31}', 'IGDB', 79.4734259285904, 32294, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":28667,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":26077,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29696.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52896.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52900.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52897.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52898.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/52899.jpg"]', '{19164,24426,27209,28010,106987,96217,115653,26845,22387,55038}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gal1U1jyilg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sl_iNQ2tn9M}', 'Ilinx Corporation', '11', null, '{987}'), (1357, 'Disgaea: Hour of Darkness', 'Disgaea: Hour of Darkness is a tactical role-playing video game and the first game in the Disgaea series. Battle gameplay takes place on a map divided into a square grid. The player controls a squad of humanoid units and monsters, which each occupy a single square of the grid and do combat with a group of enemies. Depending on the character and attack selected, the player will be able to deal damage to a specific enemy unit or a designated region of the map. Combat ends when all enemy units or all of the player''s units are destroyed.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4ps9.jpg', '2003-01-30', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 87.4167227126817, 11610, 1, 24.99, '[{"id":67264,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":58132,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2097.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2095.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2096.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2099.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389753.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389757.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389756.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389754.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389755.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389759.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389761.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389758.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/389760.jpg"]', '{26845,11694,119171,11292,9927,2365,7297,6635,832,1280}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOsvsyIElRI}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1358, 'Disgaea PC', 'A version of Disgaea: Hour of Darkness, including the added content in Afternoon of Darkness, was released for Microsoft Windows via Steam on February 24, 2016, retitled as Disgaea PC. The initial release was panned by critics on launch due to its many bugs, which included persistent crashes, save file loss, and poor performance, even on high-end PCs. A patch was released soon afterwards that fixed many of the bugs. Another patch was released for the game later that added the four characters previously exclusive to Disgaea DS. Players who bought the game during the 2016 Steam Summer Sale would also earn free in-game cosmetic items for Valve’s first person shooter game Team Fortress 2.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tvw.jpg', '2016-02-24', '{12,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 89.0709702503526, 34392, 1, 48.99, '[{"id":28659,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/29759.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78911.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78908.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78907.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78910.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/78909.jpg"]', '{13196,19164,26845,7615,27209,27092,24426,28010,14394,28182}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D07AgDm4Vmk}', 'NIS America', '11', null, '{987}'), (1359, 'Disgaea 2: Cursed Memories', 'Disgaea 2: Cursed Memories is a tactical role-playing game and the sequel to Disgaea: Hour of Darkness. It was re-released for the PlayStation Portable as Disgaea 2 Portable in Japan and as Disgaea 2: Dark Hero Days in North America and Europe. Fifteen years ago, a powerful Overlord by the name of Zenon appeared in Veldime and cursed its human population. Since then, all its inhabitants have become demons and are to remain that way if the curse was not broken. However, a young man named Adell was the only human unaffected by the curse. Wanting to save his family and return them back to their true form, Adell decides to seek out Overlord Zenon and defeat him. The gameplay in Disgaea 2 builds directly upon that of Disgaea: Hour of Darkness; players control a party of characters to do battle on a 3D isometric grid map.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1tw1.jpg', '2006-02-23', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 84.6584466028634, 11694, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":7296,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":105363,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2116.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2115.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2117.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2118.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2119.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2120.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2121.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11901.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11905.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11904.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11902.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11903.jpg"]', '{26845,22387,9938,10297,14394,7297,2365,10388,19133,660}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Axtb4hBtYnc}', 'Koei', '0', null, '{987}'), (1360, 'Disgaea 3: Absence of Justice', 'Disgaea 3: Absence of Justice is the third video game in the Disgaea series by Nippon Ichi. The game takes place in a Netherworld school called the Evil Academy. In this demon school, a good student is one who engages in evil activities such as truancy, never showing up to class, and getting in fights with others. Disgaea 3 is a tactical RPG; most of the game involves battles on isometric maps upon which the player controls a group of characters. Maps often feature "geo blocks" with statistical effects on the battlefield, that, unlike in previous games, can be stacked or stood upon. Many objects in the environment, including these blocks, and characters themselves, can be lifted, thrown, or destroyed.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2pxf.jpg', '2008-01-31', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 77.1937361896743, 7297, 1, 10.99, '[{"id":32454,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":188599,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2122.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2123.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2124.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2125.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11511.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11514.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11515.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11513.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11512.jpg"]', '{26845,5652,2365,10297,7298,14394,11694,660,7027,13196}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wrP9IqkeEls,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ntHRAueqm3E}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1361, 'Disgaea 5: Alliance of Vengeance', 'Disgaea 5: Alliance of Vengeance is a tactical role-playing video game. The evil demon emperor Void Dark devastates numerous Netherworlds after coming to power, with the help of an army of over one million soldiers known as The Lost. Following this, the Overlords of the Netherworlds under Void Dark''s rule attempt to rise up and take revenge. The game involves the player traveling across different Netherworlds in an attempt to bring the Overlords and heirs of each different world to join forces together to fight against Void Dark. The game will feature new systems not seen within prior titles in the Disgaea series. In addition, the number of characters displayable on-screen has increased to 100, compared to 10 characters on the earlier PlayStation 3 titles.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6h3i.jpg', '2015-03-26', '{12,13,15,24}', 'IGDB', 84.4128382998702, 11594, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":191323,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":92426,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":75155,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/62169.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11498.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11497.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11496.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11499.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11500.jpg"]', '{25311,58075,35994,8422,26574,17379,24765,57372,103232,36553}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9loIZxhnmco,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=obHduLC2cEA}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1362, 'Disgaea 4: A Promise Revisited', 'Disgaea 4: A Promise Revisited is a port of Disgaea 4: A Promise Unforgotten on the Playstation Vita. It contains all of the downloadable content made available in the original PS3 game and also features newly added game content. However some content was also cut out, such as the old SD sprites and voice acting for certain scenes.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2pxg.jpg', '2014-01-30', '{12,13,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 42697, 1, 21.99, '[{"id":31477,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":58668,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115467.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115464.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115463.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115465.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/115466.jpg"]', '{26845,13196,26268,7615,111187,14394,102057,112191,36258,26940}', '{}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '11', null, null), (1363, 'Disgaea 4: A Promise Unforgotten', 'Disgaea 4: A Promise Unforgotten is a tactical role-playing game and the fourth in the Disgaea series by Nippon Ichi Software. The game tells the story of Valvatorez, a former tyrant leading a party to rebel against the president of the Netherworld. The game was ported to the Playstation Vita and released under the name Disgaea 4: A Promise Revisited in the west.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1s6n.jpg', '2011-02-24', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 80.9149795679029, 7298, 1, 13.99, '[{"id":94611,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":34060,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":188608,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2127.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2130.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2126.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2131.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2133.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2132.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2128.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/2129.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11508.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11506.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/11507.jpg"]', '{7297,26845,22387,1280,9938,10388,14394,2365,11694,5652}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IQhPwROEKkw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qzoD5HzOgpY}', 'NIS America', '0', null, '{987}'), (1364, 'Disgaea 7: Vows of the Virtueless - Complete Edition', 'Includes the following:
- Disgaea 7 game
- Cosmetic Set
- Special Weapons Set
- Starter Support Set
- Season Pass', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7nbp.jpg', '2023-10-03', '{12,15,16,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 270296, 1, 74.99, '[{"id":154824,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/119508.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220611.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220609.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220610.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220608.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220612.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220613.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220614.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220615.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220616.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220617.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220618.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220619.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1220620.jpg"]', '{28010,27092,27209,106987,24426,28182,96217,115653,81249,13196}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aLlk74apf2Q}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1365, 'Disgaea Mayhem', 'Disgaea Mayhem is a brand-new 3D action RPG from an all-star team consisting of director Shunsuke Minowa, character designer Takehito Harada, and composer Tenpei Sato.

In this game, players will be able to experience the exhilaration of defeating enemies with overwhelming power that defies convention—unleashing flashy techniques with simple controls, completionist elements like leveling characters up to 9,999 and “reincarnating” them to grow even stronger, and developing overpowered stats that let them deal over a billion damage.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobntq.jpg', '2026-01-29', '{12}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 335576, 1, 82.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/198477.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1644624.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1644622.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1644626.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1644623.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1644625.jpg"]', '{25636,57372,111835,113636,54775,106987,28309,115280,81249,96217}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OeiijXYpkrM,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3wFCYS_ZL2Q,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oq_DQ4hnErQ,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJNRLUvEMH4}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, '{987}'), (1366, 'Disgaea Infinite', 'Disgaea Infinite takes the lovable characters and game world of the legendary Disgaea series and throws them into a fresh new "visual novel" game style, offering a thrilling mystery to solve, clues to hunt, and a suspect to track down. You are given full control over the story, including the ability to travel back and forth in time and choosing how characters will act, making for an exciting new experience in the Disgaea universe!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2hj0.jpg', '2009-11-01', '{31}', 'IGDB', 60, 21742, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":71513,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{115374,55282,111130,87975,34218,395197,394279,393629,393222,393195}', '{}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '0', null, null), (1367, 'Disgaea 6 Complete', 'Can a mere Netherworld zombie rise up and destroy a god? Find out in the newest installment of the Disgaea series! Features such as Super Reincarnation, 3D visuals, and adjustable gameplay settings make this the perfect game for both new and old Disgaea fans!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4hjc.jpg', '2022-06-16', '{12,15,24}', 'IGDB', 80, 191497, 1, 67.99, '[{"id":106652,"rating_category":{"id":25,"rating":"15+"}},{"id":81920,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/67870.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738785.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738786.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738787.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738788.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738789.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738790.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738791.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738792.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738793.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738794.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738795.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738796.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738797.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738798.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738799.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738800.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/738801.jpg"]', '{13196,19164,28010,27092,19404,24426,57372,54775,16391,106987}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u2RTl-ypzns}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '10', null, '{987}'), (1368, 'Disgaea 5 Complete', 'Full story of the original with eight new scenarios, four fan favorite characters, and three character classes from the Disgaea series.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6jcb.jpg', '2017-03-03', '{12,15,16,24}', 'IGDB', 87.3791078469113, 26768, 1, 31.99, '[{"id":97216,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":191121,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":28085,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12878.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156562.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/44222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156559.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156558.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156564.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156561.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156560.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156563.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156565.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156566.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156567.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/156568.jpg"]', '{13196,7615,26845,19404,26268,9472,115653,112191,111187,93694}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vDT8iTFPLeg,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YQ7iXz_xxs}', 'Nippon Ichi Software', '10', null, '{987}'), (1369, 'Disgaea 4 Complete+', 'When the Corrupternment threatens to disrupt the way of life in Hades, Valvatorez finds himself at the helm of a fiery revolution. The former tyrant will need to call upon new allies, recruit a formidable army, and learn a thing or two about political unrest if he hopes to take down the corrupt regime and bring salvation to all Prinny-kind!

Dive into a tale of revolution and redemption, woven throughout a dark and hilarious realm of vampires, werewolves, and other devilish denizens. Engage in immersive and in-depth tactics-based gameplay brimming with over-the-top destructive action, and unload a horde of special features to take your Netherworldly adventures to another level. Brace your belt pouches and grab your sardines; the ultimate HD Disgaea game has arrived, dood!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1r4x.jpg', '2019-10-28', '{12,15}', 'IGDB', 85.3642984414842, 119506, 1, 53.99, '[{"id":190702,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":25958,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":97218,"rating_category":{"id":13,"rating":"A"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/12128.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317283.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317282.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317285.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317284.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317287.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317286.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/317288.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/314668.jpg"]', '{57372,25311,35994,28010,27092,28182,16391,24426,57296,26574}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-RbmhyisO4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r0toUyID0lo}', 'NIS America', '11', null, '{987}'), (1370, 'Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny - Desco', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7or7.jpg', '2021-07-27', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 238319, 1, 59.99, '[{"id":122105,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/102093.jpg"]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1371, 'Disgaea 7: Glasses Costumes Set', 'Adds a set of 7 unique character costumes (glasses).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload