The Forza Horizon 4 Deluxe Edition digital bundle includes the Car Pass and the Formula Drift Car Pack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ec1.jpg', '2018-10-02', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 111318, 1, 59.99, '[{"id":93864,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":91801,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":111923,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":29098,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":188802,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48225.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/48224.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394388.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394389.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394390.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394391.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394392.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394393.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394394.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394395.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394396.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394397.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,55192,104983,27553,105011,27378,37419,51577}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '0', null, '{2810}'), (1404, 'Forza Horizon 4: Ultimate Edition', 'Dynamic seasons change everything at the world’s greatest automotive festival. Go it alone or team up with others to explore beautiful and historic Britain in a shared open world. Collect, modify and drive over 450 cars. Race, stunt, create and explore – choose your own path to become a Horizon Superstar.

The Forza Horizon 4 Ultimate Edition digital bundle includes the full game and Car Pass, VIP Membership, Formula Drift Car Pack, Best of Bond Car Pack, and the Fortune Island and LEGO Speed Champions game expansions.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ec2.jpg', '2018-09-28', '{10}', 'IGDB', 82.4322919851223, 110392, 1, 53.99, '[{"id":91777,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":111642,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":191300,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":93079,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":29099,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47189.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/47191.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394398.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394399.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394400.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394401.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394402.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394403.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394404.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394405.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394406.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394407.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,55192,104983,27553,105011,27378,37419,51577}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '3', null, '{2810}'), (1405, 'Forza Horizon 5: Premium Edition', 'Your Ultimate Horizon Adventure awaits! Explore the vibrant and ever-evolving open world landscapes of Mexico with limitless, fun driving action in hundreds of the world’s greatest cars. The Premium Edition includes early access to the full game, allowing you to play four days early beginning November 5, 2021. Also included are the Welcome Pack, Car Pass, VIP Membership, and two game expansions when they become available.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co45k9.jpg', '2021-11-04', '{10,14}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 171270, 1, 60.99, '[{"id":50553,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":93736,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":91550,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":50552,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":110897,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56891.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56890.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672185.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672184.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672186.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672187.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672188.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672189.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672190.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672191.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672192.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672193.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672194.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672195.jpg"]', '{116353,118871,113105,119161,116667,120126,78511,117855,114286,105011}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FYH9n37B7Yw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPgUk3NZcbI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7fytkGUU7jk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d_20X1YM28U}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '3', null, '{2810}'), (1406, 'Forza Horizon: Rally', 'Experience the thrill and danger of rally in epic new stages that push you and your cars to the limit as your co-driver alerts you to severe terrain changes and hazards ahead. Race 5 new iconic rally cars or create your own dirt-eating machines with new rally upgrades that can be applied to any car in your Forza Horizon garage.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7ste.jpg', '2012-12-18', '{10}', 'IGDB', 80, 22201, 1, 23.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246698.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246694.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246695.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246697.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246700.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246699.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1246696.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265276.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,114432,27553,27378,323851,261884,123184,115838}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t0OT2lVjIhM}', 'Playground Games', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1407, 'Forza Horizon 4: Fortune Island', 'Seek your fortune in the most treacherous Horizon expansion yet, where you will conquer extreme terrain, lightning storms, and perilous roads in search of hidden treasure. Embark on a new campaign, solve Treasure Hunt riddles, and carve your own path in new Trailblazer PR Stunts. Tackle the island’s twisting mountain switchbacks, ocean cliffside roads and rough terrain in 10 exciting new cars including the 2019 Lamborghini Urus, 2017 Ram Rebel TRX Concept, and the 2018 BMW M5.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2e1c.jpg', '2018-12-13', '{10}', 'IGDB', 72.0178616018837, 112024, 1, 30.99, '[{"id":29019,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":93889,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":29020,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":91782,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/24147.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393827.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393828.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393829.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393830.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393831.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393832.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393833.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393834.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393835.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,55192,104983,27553,105011,27378,37419,51577}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1408, 'Forza Horizon 5: Deluxe Edition', 'Your Ultimate Horizon Adventure awaits! Explore the vibrant and ever-evolving open world landscapes of Mexico with limitless, fun driving action in hundreds of the world’s greatest cars. The Deluxe Edition includes the full game and Car Pass.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co45k6.jpg', '2021-11-09', '{10,14}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 171269, 1, 51.99, '[{"id":91582,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":50554,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":93853,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":188388,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":111060,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56889.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/56888.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672171.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672172.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672173.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672176.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672174.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672175.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672177.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672178.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672179.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672180.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672181.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/672182.jpg"]', '{116353,118871,113105,119161,116667,120126,78511,117855,114286,105011}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FYH9n37B7Yw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPgUk3NZcbI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7fytkGUU7jk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d_20X1YM28U}', 'Playground Games', '0', null, '{2810}'), (1409, 'Forza Horizon', 'Forza Horizon is an action racing game set on the epic open roads of Colorado with a thrilling music festival backdrop. Combining stunning graphics and cutting-edge music with legendary Forza authenticity and a superb collection of cars to drive, Forza Horizon is an open-world automotive playground that puts a spotlight on speed, style, and the freedom of the open road. This is where cars belong!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co228y.jpg', '2012-10-23', '{10}', 'IGDB', 82.9251283611313, 3047, 1, 19.99, '[{"id":223651,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":151386,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":190000,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/75005.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3334.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3333.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/3335.jpg"]', '{3193,98,97,101,99,524,100,105,1006,3068}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7aDIDZKnH4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xy8JA4pqrI4}', 'Playground Games', '0', '{22201,132825}', '{2810}'), (1410, 'Forza Horizon 4: Expansions Bundle', 'Get two game expansions at a reduced price! This bundle gives you access to the Fortune Island and LEGO® Speed Champions game expansions. This add-on requires Forza Horizon 4.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2ec4.jpg', '2018-10-02', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 136391, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":29102,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":29101,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/46778.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394413.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394414.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394415.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394416.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394417.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394418.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394419.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394408.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394409.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394410.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394411.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394412.jpg"]', '{109292,105011,44178,80382,37419,27553,51577,27378,117717,55192}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '3', null, '{2810}'), (1411, 'Forza Horizon 3', 'You’re in charge of the Horizon Festival. Customize everything, hire and fire your friends, and explore Australia in over 350 of the world’s greatest cars. Make your Horizon the ultimate celebration of cars, music, and freedom of the open road. How you get there is up to you.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2e25.jpg', '2016-09-27', '{10}', 'IGDB', 86.2176059647315, 19539, 1, 41.99, '[{"id":13018,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":190908,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":115568,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":115567,"rating_category":{"id":35,"rating":"PG"}},{"id":115569,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/59103.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25167.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25166.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25168.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25165.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/25164.jpg"]', '{36872,26709,13205,11570,19541,11156,18320,11186,19130,19554}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GnuAgRdTtHM}', 'Turn 10 Studios', '0', '{349675,349679,140367,140368,140380}', '{2810}'), (1412, 'Forza Horizon 6', 'Discover the breathtaking landscapes of Japan in over 550 real-world cars and become a racing Legend at the Horizon Festival. Start your journey as a tourist and explore a world full of hit music and Japanese culture. Build a Valley Estate, acquire awe-inspiring homes, and display your prized car collection in fully Customizable Garages. Cruise the roads with your friends and join Car Meets around Japan, unleash your imagination with EventLab and build together in Horizon CoLab.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobc5n.jpg', '2026-05-19', '{10,13,14,33}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 348330, 1, 84.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/200393.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/200394.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/259177.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746198.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746199.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746200.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746201.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746205.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746203.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746202.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746206.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746204.jpg"]', '{118871,37419,105011,27378,26574,47161,15851,114285,113360,112078}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VXedKqX5Wa4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWw-UENvdTw}', 'Playground Games', '0', null, '{2810}'), (1413, 'Forza Horizon 2', 'Race through a massive wide-open world featuring dramatic weather and day-to-night cycle in Forza Horizon 2. Instantly connect with friends in the ultimate celebration of speed, style, and action-packed driving. Explore beautiful and exotic locations in more than 200 of the world’s greatest cars, all created with precise detail in stunning 1080p.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2f5s.jpg', '2014-09-30', '{10,13}', 'IGDB', 84.5799510068089, 7326, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":67364,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":188858,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":170686,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5663.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5662.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/5664.jpg"]', '{3047,78511,10965,3193,97,105011,3068,99,98,113360}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KSgyJqecz-4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7dtulnt6Xt4,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yIML0Xjhrcc}', 'Microsoft Studios', '0', null, '{2810}'), (1414, 'Forza Horizon 4', 'Dynamic seasons change everything at the world’s greatest automotive festival. Go it alone or team up with others to explore beautiful and historic Britain in a shared open world. Collect, modify and drive over 450 cars. Race, stunt, create and explore – choose your own path to become a Horizon Superstar.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2e1a.jpg', '2018-10-02', '{10,14,31}', 'IGDB', 86.3303158268083, 82090, 1, 56.99, '[{"id":93177,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":30615,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":111390,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":94817,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":188544,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/7216.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/218323.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393816.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393817.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393818.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393819.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393820.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393821.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393822.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393823.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393824.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393825.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402315.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402316.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402317.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402318.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402319.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402320.jpg"]', '{23733,81680,119298,76263,17000,78511,119161,103329,25076,54842}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S6CKWsNeDu8}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '0', '{144415,144414,153718,153703,153719,153705,153709,365712,140292,153720,153712,153721,153726,153701,153714,153710,153722,153725,140285,153706,153708,365709,153715,153727,153707,153717,153711,140365,153724,153704,153723}', '{2810}'), (1415, 'Forza Horizon 5', 'Your Ultimate Horizon Adventure awaits! Explore the vibrant and ever-evolving open-world landscapes of Mexico with limitless, fun driving action in hundreds of the world’s greatest cars.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3ofx.jpg', '2021-11-09', '{10}', 'IGDB', 89.396441786975, 141503, 1, 77.99, '[{"id":83420,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":110518,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":215589,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":215590,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":215591,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}},{"id":215592,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":93258,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/39779.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/224614.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489228.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489229.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489230.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489231.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489232.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489222.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489223.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489224.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489225.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489226.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/489227.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/551553.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371146.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371148.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371149.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371150.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1371151.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402231.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402232.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1402233.jpg"]', '{119161,78511,105011,101211,19164,37419,3772,118218,81249,113114}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7fytkGUU7jk,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FYH9n37B7Yw,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eitSF5rVAOI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d_20X1YM28U,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPgUk3NZcbI,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W-SpP-Z0Uu8}', 'Playground Games', '0', '{208448,204679,293918,361777,361779}', '{2810}'), (1416, 'Forza Horizon 4: VIP', 'The VIP DLC provides players with exclusive benefits, including a unique VIP garage, which allows for faster car collection and management. It also includes a 10% increase in credits earned from racing and events, as well as a 10% increase in experience points earned from racing and events. Additionally, players receive a special VIP car, the 2016 Pagani Huayra, and access to a special VIP-only event series. The VIP DLC was a free update for players who purchased the game''s Ultimate Edition or Season Pass, and was also available for purchase separately.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9d6h.jpg', '2018-10-02', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 153720, 1, 56.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/502698.jpg"]', '{109292,55192,104983,44178,80382,27553,107227,102023,27378,396794}', '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1417, 'Forza Horizon 3: VIP', 'Forza Horizon 3 VIP members receive five exclusive VIP cars, the 2016 Lamborghini Aventador LP750-4 SV, 2016 Koenigsegg Regera, 2015 Ferrari F12tdf, 2015 Ultima Evolution Coupe 1020, and 2015 Ford Falcon GT F 351. VIPs will receive additional benefits, including double Wheelspin earnings, access to exclusive online events, community gifts, and more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa6ll.jpg', '2016-09-23', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 349679, 1, 39.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1418, 'Forza Horizon 4: Car Pass', 'Get 49 extra cars at one low price! All cars included in the Car Pass grant you a one-time only, free addition of each car to your Forza Horizon 4 garage, with no additional in-game credit cost. The Forza Horizon 4 Car Pass is included with Forza Horizon 4 Deluxe and Ultimate Editions, and the Ultimate Add-Ons Bundle.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaesm.jpg', '2018-10-02', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 365709, 1, 55.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, null), (1419, 'Forza Horizon 5: Car Pass', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co9d6d.jpg', '2021-11-09', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 293918, 1, 65.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1420, 'Forza Horizon 3: Hot Wheels', 'Forza Horizon 3 Hot Wheels takes players to six new themed islands located off the coast of Australia; all connected by a network of Hot Wheels tracks – positioned hundreds of feet in the air – featuring classic Hot Wheels configurations like loops, corkscrews, and more. This is stunt driving at its most extreme, where you can master tracks by performing brand new Hot Wheels skills that make use of boost pads, high-bank turns, half-pipes, insane jumps, and even giant mechanical dinosaurs. If you’re looking to get creative, check out the new Stunt Swap feature to modify stunt track sections and dare your friends to try them.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co3wmy.jpg', '2017-05-09', '{10}', 'IGDB', 79.2640624246128, 28542, 1, 53.99, '[{"id":85043,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127571.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127574.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127572.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127573.jpg"]', '{109292,105011,44178,80382,37419,27553,27378,297462,278395,269096}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1421, 'Forza Horizon 3: Car Pass', 'The Car Pass brings you six monthly car packs (7 cars each) beginning in October 2016, ending March 2017. That’s 42 amazing new cars total, all waiting to be collected, customized, and raced, for one low price.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa6lj.jpg', '2016-09-23', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 349675, 1, 32.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1422, 'Forza Horizon 5: Hot Wheels', 'Forza Horizon 5: Hot Wheels introduces players to the visually stunning, exhilarating new Horizon Hot Wheels Park in the clouds high above Mexico, the ultimate playground of creative fun for all players.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co4ztx.jpg', '2022-07-19', '{10,14}', 'IGDB', 75.5805640683228, 204679, 1, 77.99, '[{"id":103877,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":86396,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":103733,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":131993,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/92764.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811115.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811117.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811120.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811118.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811119.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/811116.jpg"]', '{116353,116667,113105,118871,120126,109292,116352,117855,119161,114286}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Idg18QJCbXU}', 'Playground Games', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1423, 'Forza Horizon 5: Hide & Seek', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8pli.jpg', '2024-09-01', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 314386, 1, 59.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1385311.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1385313.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1385312.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z32r8ECNNiA}', 'Sumo Nottingham', '14', null, '{2810}'), (1424, 'Forza Horizon 2: Storm Island', 'Storm clouds are gathering; a fierce tropical storm is about to break. Several of the world’s most iconic off-roaders are lined up, poised to spring with a punch of the gas pedal. Thunder crashes in the distance, an omen of the dangerous terrain and extreme elevation changes that await. Drivers grip their steering wheels, ready to tackle the epic challenges ahead. Welcome to a new land of extremes with the Forza Horizon 2: Storm Island expansion!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/imt1rk9fjj6pitkuuhrx.jpg', '2014-12-16', '{10}', 'IGDB', 84.5, 20307, 1, 14.99, '[{"id":85041,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127570.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/27164.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127567.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127569.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127568.jpg"]', '{109292,105011,44178,80382,37419,27553,27378,297462,278395,269096}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfEZiBLMCr0}', 'Microsoft Studios', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1425, 'Forza Horizon 4: Welcome Pack', 'The Forza Horizon 4 Welcome Pack comes with 8 stunning, pre-tuned cars and a quintessential British House. Included with this pack are specially pre-tuned Welcome Pack editions of the 1996 Ferrari F50 GT, 2017 Ford GT, 1960 Porsche 718 RS 60, 2016 Hoonigan Gymkhana 9 Ford Focus RS RX, 1993 Toyota #1 T100 Baja Truck, 2012 Lamborghini Aventador LP700-4, 2016 Subaru #199 WRX STI VT15R Rally Car, and the 1976 Jeep CJ5 Renegade. The Welcome Pack grants you a one-time only, free addition of each car to your Forza Horizon 4 garage, with no additional in-game credit cost.

Also included are the Sunflower Meadows Player House and Horizon Promo Feature Unlock.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coaesq.jpg', '2020-07-29', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 365712, 1, 54.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JKnfKfrWsY}', 'Playground Games', '1', null, null), (1426, 'Forza Horizon 5: Summer Party', 'It''s summertime in Mexico and you don''t wanna miss this party! The Summer Party update brings longer night cycles, the new Icons of Speed story and new summer props to bring the chill over to EventLab.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co6rvm.jpg', '2023-07-20', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 256985, 1, 62.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1090230.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1090231.jpg"]', '{37419,81249,103303,105011,19164,118871,113895,234481,176672,109292}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '14', null, '{2810}'), (1427, 'Forza Horizon 6: Deluxe Edition', 'Forza Horizon 6 Deluxe Edition includes the full game, Welcome Pack and Car Pass (30 cars delivered to your game, one per week).', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobca3.jpg', '2026-05-19', '{10,13,14,33}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 386816, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746717.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746718.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746719.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746720.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746721.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746712.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746710.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746713.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746708.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746709.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746716.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746711.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746714.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746715.jpg"]', '{118871,27378,47161,15851,112078,114285,348330,114432,103218,119207}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '0', null, null), (1428, 'Forza Horizon 3: Deluxe Edition', 'The Forza Horizon 3 Deluxe Edition includes the full game of Forza Horizon 3, VIP Membership and cars, and the Motorsport All-Stars Car Pack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/gxymj6spregzxjzta9uw.jpg', null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 85132, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1429, 'Forza Horizon 6: Premium Edition', 'Forza Horizon 6 Premium Edition includes the full game with Early Access - Play 4 days early starting May 15, and VIP Membership, Welcome Pack, Time Attack Car Pack, and Car Pass (30 cars delivered to your game, one per week), as well as the Italian Passion Car Pack and two Premium Expansions coming post-launch.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobca4.jpg', '2026-05-15', '{10,13,14,33}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 386817, 1, 83.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746725.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746733.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746723.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746732.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746724.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746727.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746726.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746728.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746729.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746734.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746736.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746735.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746731.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1746730.jpg"]', '{118871,37419,105011,27378,348330,26574,47161,15851,114285,112078}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '0', null, null), (1431, 'Forza Horizon 5: Rally Adventure', 'Your Forza Horizon 5 Rally Adventure is here! Drive purpose-built rally monsters and conquer the rugged Sierra Nueva. Join three rally teams and attack Horizon’s most thrilling routes ever in Timed Rally and Multi-Car Races. Feel the intensity of massive dust trails and deformable roads in 10 new cars and experience the bursting flames of anti-lag. Explore dramatic craters, an abandoned quarry and an entirely smashable palm forest.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co97ah.jpg', '2023-03-29', '{10}', 'IGDB', 89.2822353213564, 195375, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":141413,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":141485,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007669.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007670.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007671.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007672.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007673.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007674.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007675.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1007676.jpg"]', '{37419,105011,81249,19164,118871,119161,26574,110411,113895,119207}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ajFf2RaiZu4}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1433, 'Forza Horizon 5: Fast X Car Pack', 'This blockbuster DLC includes iconic vehicles like the 1970 Dodge Charger, 1966 Chevrolet Impala Super Sport, 1973 Datsun 240Z, 2022 Dodge Charger SRT Hellcat Redeye Widebody, and the 2022 Flip Car 2.0 to drive and race in the Horizon Festival.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i0.jpg', '2023-12-05', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 279314, 1, 65.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1204740.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '13', null, null), (1434, 'Forza Horizon 3: Ultimate Edition', 'You’re in charge of the Horizon Festival. Customize everything, hire and fire your friends, and explore Australia in over 350 of the world’s greatest cars. Make your Horizon the ultimate celebration of cars, music, and freedom of the open road. How you get there is up to you.

Forza Horizon 3 Ultimate Edition includes the full game of Forza Horizon 3, Early Access, the Forza Horizon 3 Car Pass, VIP Membership and cars, Forza Hub App, and the Motorsport All-Stars Car Pack, which gives you the chance to take 10 of the hottest modern race cars off the track and out on the open road.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/zuhdagohkj600ssot1xb.jpg', '2016-09-27', '{10}', 'IGDB', 90, 41609, 1, 38.99, '[{"id":187799,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184487.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184485.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184483.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184484.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184486.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184488.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184482.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184489.jpg"]', '{36872,37001,75244,55072,109292,18167,19541,11137,44178,11186}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1435, 'Forza Horizon 3: Porsche Car Pack', 'The Porsche Car Pack is a DLC for Forza Horizon 3, released on April 12, 2017, that adds seven Porsche vehicles ranging from classic to modern models. It was sold separately and not included in the Car Pass. The pack was removed from sale after the game''s delisting in 2020, but remains accessible to players who purchased it before that date.

The pack''s release debuted as part of a celebration towards Turn 10 and Porsche entering a 6 year collaborative partnership.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co30zl.jpg', '2017-04-12', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140367, 1, 45.99, '[{"id":30793,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405542.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405543.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405544.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405545.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405546.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405547.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405548.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405549.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405534.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405535.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405536.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405537.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405538.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405539.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405540.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405541.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dy8Rw3KRrJA}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1436, 'Forza Horizon 3: Hoonigan Car Pack', 'The Hoonigan Car Pack is a downloadable car pack that was available for the PC and Xbox One releases of Forza Horizon 3 on August 15, 2017.

The Hoonigan Car Pack is available for both Forza Horizon 3 and Forza Motorsport 7. For players who have preordered the digital copy of Forza Motorsport 7, the Hoonigan Car Pack will be gifted to players at no additional cost for Forza Horizon 3 and Forza Motorsport 7.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co30zi.jpg', '2017-08-15', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140380, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":30804,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405663.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405664.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NpaLvqHovuI}', 'Microsoft', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1438, 'Forza Horizon 2: Porsche Expansion', 'The Porsche Expansion is a downloadable content pack released on June 6, 2015 for the Xbox One release of Forza Horizon 2 .
The expansion adds ten Porsche cars to the game along with various Porsche themed events and achievements. On July 16, 2015, the free Porsche Bonus Car Pack was released that added two additional Porsche cars, but was removed from the Xbox Games Store on July 24, 2015.

Since October 1, 2018, following the title''s end-of-life-status, it can be no longer purchased from the Microsoft Store.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2upv.jpg', '2015-06-06', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 144421, 1, 23.99, '[{"id":85040,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/425522.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,105011,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlxuglTIFTY}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1440, 'Forza Horizon 3: Blizzard Mountain', 'The Blizzard Mountain expansion for Forza Horizon 3 brings snow, ice, extreme elevations, and blizzards to challenge players in their quest to become King of the Mountain. Explore this extreme alpine playground in eight new cars and trucks including the 2016 Ford GYMKHANA 9 Focus RS RX. Compete in thrilling new mountain race events like Hill Climb, Descent, and Blizzard Races. Discover new Bucket List Blueprints, Rivals events, Xbox Live Achievements, a new barn find car, and more. This add-on is available separately, or as part of the Forza Horizon 3 Expansion Pass.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1h5g.jpg', '2016-12-13', '{10}', 'IGDB', 86, 26495, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":85042,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/34960.jpg"]', '{105011,109292,44178,37419,119161,80382,115653,81249,19164,27378}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1441, 'Forza Horizon 5: Expansions Bundle', 'The Forza Horizon 5 Expansions Bundle includes two expansions. Each expansion will introduce a new location, vehicles, and gameplay.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i6.jpg', '2021-11-08', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 200693, 1, 68.99, '[{"id":127879,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":86395,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{109292,55192,104983,44178,80382,27553,107227,102023,27378,397875}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '3', null, null), (1444, 'Forza Horizon 5: JDM Jewels Car Pack', 'Four cars of different styles, sizes, and uses arrive at the Horizon Festival from Japan! Modify, drive, and collect four emblems of the Japanese Market with the JDM Jewels Car Pack.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa0wk.jpg', '2024-07-16', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 350686, 1, 71.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1733716.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1733717.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1733718.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1733719.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1733720.jpg"]', '{116667,118871,44178,120126,117855,116136,29348,89444,87975,27378}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '13', null, null), (1447, 'Forza Horizon - December IGN Car Pack', 'This pack includes 7 new cars: 2011 Ford F-150 SVT Raptor: Halo Edition; 2008 Aston Martin DBS; 2012 Ferrari F12berlinetta; 2006 Ford GTX1; 2006 Hummer H1 Alpha Open Top; 1993 McLaren F1; 1971 AMC Javelin-AMX.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co23vv.jpg', '2012-12-04', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 132825, 1, 16.99, '[{"id":89324,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":188005,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1448, 'Forza Horizon 5: 2019 Nissan 370Z Nismo', 'Forza Horizon 5 2019 Nissan 370Z Nismo', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i4.jpg', '2022-07-07', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 208448, 1, 78.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/831700.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '1', null, null), (1450, 'Forza Horizon 4: Formula Drift Car Pack', 'This add-on includes 7 new Formula Drift cars for you to collect, drive and customize in Forza Horizon 4.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2j2q.jpg', '2018-10-02', '{10,13}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140285, 1, 40.99, '[{"id":30767,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405002.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405003.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405004.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405005.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405006.jpg"]', '{44178,27378,37419,40470,105011,116667,118871,101573,120126,261401}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vP-FQbwdb8E}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1451, 'Forza Horizon 2 Presents Fast & Furious', 'The next great automotive adventure begins with the Forza Horizon 2 Presents Fast & Furious standalone expansion for Xbox One and Xbox 360! For the first time ever, the Forza experience of thrilling driving and amazing cars is combining with the unstoppable Fast & Furious movie franchise to create an original adventure filled with adrenaline-fueled automotive action.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co1ygh.jpg', '2015-03-27', '{10,13}', 'IGDB', 79.9032750575232, 74159, 1, 22.99, '[{"id":67362,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":48514,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}},{"id":14709,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127553.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127552.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127554.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/127555.jpg"]', '{78511,44178,80382,27378,17130,22953,19376,118871,40470,11639}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uPbDdUHg1QE}', 'Microsoft Studios', '4', null, '{2810}'), (1452, 'Forza Horizon 4: LEGO Speed Champions', 'Forza Horizon 4: LEGO Speed Champions, the second major expansion for the award-winning Forza Horizon 4, presents a wonderous new LEGO Valley to race and explore. Amass your own Brick Collection and construct a Master Builder’s House with a garage of amazing LEGO Speed Champions cars including the McLaren Senna, Ferrari F40 Competizione and 1967 Mini Cooper S Rally.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2e1e.jpg', '2019-06-13', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 121517, 1, 34.99, '[{"id":29021,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":93093,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":29022,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":91552,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/36203.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393836.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393837.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393838.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/393839.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394356.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394357.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394358.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394359.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394360.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394361.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/394362.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,80382,55192,104983,27553,105011,27378,37419,51577}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OCMCLLgU6uE}', 'Playground Games', '2', null, '{2810}'), (1453, 'Forza Horizon 5: Acceleration Car Pack', 'Step on the gas and start running with the four speed legends included in the Acceleration Car Pack: 1967 Shelby GT 500, 2021 McLaren Sabre, 2022 Ford #4 Pro Electric Supervan and the 2019 Ginetta G10 RM.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90hy.jpg', '2024-03-26', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 294009, 1, 60.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1283693.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '13', null, null), (1455, 'Forza Horizon 4: Best of Bond Car Pack', 'This add-on includes ten iconic cars from 50 years of James Bond films. Included with Forza Horizon 4 Ultimate Edition and Ultimate Add-Ons Bundle. Not included with Forza Horizon 4 Car Pass.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2j2v.jpg', '2018-09-28', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140292, 1, 29.99, '[{"id":30770,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405011.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405012.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405013.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405014.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405015.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405016.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405017.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405018.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1456, 'Forza Horizon 5: Apex Allstars Car Pack', 'Run through Mexico''s finest roads in the 2018 BMW #1 BMW M Motorsport M8 GTE, 2015 Cadillac #3 Cadillac Racing ATS-V.R, 2020 Chevrolet #3 Corvette Racing C8.R, 2020 Lexus #14 VASSER SULLIVAN RC F GT3, and three more Apex All-Stars!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90hx.jpg', '2024-04-23', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 305531, 1, 58.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340101.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340102.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340103.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340104.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '13', null, null), (1457, 'Forza Horizon - 1000 Club Expansion Pack', 'This game expansion adds new challenges for every car available to drive in Forza Horizon, over 1000 challenges in all. Every completed challenge awards you a gold medal. The more medals you collect, the faster you dominate friends on the 1000 Club leaderboard.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7xid.jpg', '2013-04-16', null, 'IGDB', 70, 20851, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":188239,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":89322,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/28273.jpg"]', null, '{}', null, '2', null, null), (1458, 'Forza Horizon 3: Mountain Dew Car Pack', 'The Forza Horizon 3: Mountain Dew Car Pack is a DLC released in June 2017, featuring 7 unique cars, including the Ferrari F50 GT, Lotus 3-Eleven, and Mitsubishi Eclipse GSX. It was not included in the Car Pass and had to be bought separately. The pack was delisted in September 2020, and it’s no longer available for purchase, but existing owners can still access it.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co30zj.jpg', '2017-06-06', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 140368, 1, 54.99, '[{"id":30794,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405550.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405551.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405552.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405553.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405554.jpg"]', '{296072,252601,246158,194153,185204,184046,180883,152240,91465,37419}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vw8mrywB0fc}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1460, 'Forza Horizon 4: Barrett-Jackson Car Pack', 'The Barrett-Jackson Car Pack is a DLC for Forza Horizon 4, released on April 9, 2019 as part of Update 8. It adds seven Barrett-Jackson edition vehicles, mostly classic American models. The pack is included with the Car Pass and Ultimate Add-Ons Bundle, but can also be purchased separately.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2upf.jpg', '2019-04-09', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 144415, 1, 42.99, '[{"id":33508,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":33509,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/425470.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XEUWbeZjiuo}', 'Playground Games', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1461, 'Forza Horizon 5 Nissan Heritage Car Pack', 'Explore Nissan''s automotive heritage with the Forza Horizon 5 Nissan Retro Rides Car Pack featuring 4 classic vehicles from the iconic Japanese brand.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coag1k.jpg', '2025-04-24', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 361777, 1, 85.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/233189.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1637437.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1637438.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1637440.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1637441.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1637439.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '1', null, null), (1463, 'Forza Motorsport 7 and Forza Horizon 3 Bundle', 'Get two incredible games for one low price! Whether it’s on the track or off the beaten path, get your fix with two of the best-rated racing games ever made. This bundle includes the award-winning Forza Motorsport 7 and Forza Horizon 3 games for both Xbox One and Windows 10 PCs.

FORZA MOTORSPORT 7
Experience the thrill of motorsport at the limit with the most comprehensive, beautiful and authentic racing game ever made. Enjoy gorgeous graphics at 60fps and native 4K resolution in HDR. Collect and race more than 700 cars across 30 destinations, where race conditions change every time you return to the track.

FORZA HORIZON 3
You’re in charge of the Horizon Festival. Customize everything, hire and fire your friends, and explore Australia in over 350 of the world’s greatest cars. Make your Horizon the ultimate celebration of cars, music, and freedom of the open road. How you get there is up to you.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ayip6gwogzvxxjy7yt8l.jpg', '2018-01-01', null, 'IGDB', 90, 83742, 1, 59.99, '[{"id":189045,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/184546.jpg"]', '{66429,92266,72895,76139,66423,66419,20956,5767,79945,71607}', '{}', null, '3', null, null), (1464, 'Forza Motorsport 6 and Forza Horizon 2 Bundle', 'Now you can experience the best-selling, highest-rated racing series on Xbox One for one low price.

From the world’s greatest tracks to the freedom of the open road, Forza games combine unprecedented visuals with the industry’s leading simulation engine, giving everyone the opportunity to truly feel what it’s like to own, race and customize the cars of their dreams.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8or3.jpg', '2015-12-22', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 311355, 1, 15.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '3', null, null), (1465, 'Forza Horizon 2: 10th Anniversary Edition', 'The Forza Horizon 2 Standard Edition includes the full game of Forza Horizon 2, the official Forza Hub app for Xbox One, and the Ten Year Anniversary Car Pack, which features 10 specially tuned and liveried cars, including the 2009 Ferrari 458 Italia, the 2015 Lamborghini Hurácan and the 2013 McLaren P1™. With Forza Hub, players can collect their monthly Forza Rewards, check out the latest news from the Forza Motorsport world, vote on their favorite community creations, and much more.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/ljnk6uhcbwixekwklfcs.jpg', '2015-08-18', null, 'IGDB', 90, 83743, 1, 11.99, '[{"id":189051,"rating_category":{"id":4,"rating":"E10+"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150504.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150505.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150506.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150507.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/150508.jpg"]', null, '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1466, 'Forza Horizon: Limited Collector''s Edition', 'Combining the traditional Forza with a music festival vibe, Horizon promises to take freedom of the open road to the next level. Explore vast and varied driving playgrounds. Team up or compete with friends and rivals online. Show off your unique driving skills and become the star of the world''s most rocking motorsport party.

Limited Collector''s Edition includes VIP Membership, VIP Car Pack, Day 1 Add-on Pack, Horizon Accelerator Token Pack, 5 Additional Car Pack Liveries and a limited edition Steelbook case.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/nity3bgxk7thpitasdov.jpg', '2012-11-23', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 41594, 1, 8.99, '[{"id":89328,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":191308,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '[]', '[]', '{109292,55192,104983,44178,80382,27553,107227,102023,27378,396794}', '{}', null, '0', null, null), (1469, 'Forza Horizon 5 Universal Icons Car Pack', 'Take these five icons from your favorite movies and TV shows for a spin across the Horizon Festival featuring Knight Rider''s K.I.T.T., Jurassic Park''s 1992 Jeep Wrangler, and all 3 versions of the Time Machine from the Back to the Future trilogy!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobrrf.jpg', '2024-06-18', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 361779, 1, 56.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795780.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795781.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795782.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795783.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795784.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795785.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1795786.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', null, '1', null, null), (1470, 'Forza Horizon 5: Italian Exotics Car Pack', 'Collect 7 Italian new-to-Forza cars: 2023 Lamborghini Huracán Tecnica, 2022 Ferrari 296 GTB, 2020 Ferrari Roma, 2020 Lamborghini Essenza SCV12, 2020 Lamborghini SC20, 2019 Italdesign DaVinci Concept and 2018 Lamborghini #63 Huracán Evo.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i3.jpg', '2023-08-15', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 261851, 1, 49.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1118126.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '13', null, null), (1471, 'Forza Horizon 4: Hot Wheels Legends Car Pack', 'The Hot Wheels Legends Car Pack is a DLC for Forza Horizon 4, released on February 22, 2021 after Update 32. It includes six vehicles from the 2018 and 2019 Hot Wheels Legends Tours, featuring both winners and finalists. The pack is not part of any bundle or special edition and must be bought separately.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2upm.jpg', '2021-02-22', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 144414, 1, 55.99, '[{"id":33503,"rating_category":{"id":9,"rating":"7"}},{"id":33502,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/51419.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/51420.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/425469.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=22FKgnZLrkE}', 'Turn 10 Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1472, 'Forza Horizon 4: Mitsubishi Motors Car Pack', 'The Mitsubishi Motors Car Pack was introduced in Forza Horizon 4 on January 15, 2019 via Update 5. It includes seven Mitsubishi vehicles and was released as a free DLC available to all players, without requiring any additional purchase.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co2j6i.jpg', '2019-01-15', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140365, 1, 50.99, '[{"id":30791,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405520.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jmSuH1LdXRg}', 'Microsoft Studios', '1', null, '{2810}'), (1476, 'Forza Horizon 5: American Automotive Car Pack', 'All-American all-stars are bringing the muscle to the Horizon Festival. Make the Festival rumble with the 2020 Chevrolet Silverado LT Trail Boss, 2023 Czinger 21C, 2017 Saleen S7 LM, and the 1961 DeBerti Ford Econoline ''Shop Rod''.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90hz.jpg', '2023-11-07', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 275616, 1, 67.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1184979.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Xbox Game Studios', '13', null, null), (1478, 'Forza Horizon 5: Chinese Lucky Stars Car Pack', 'Collect and drive a curated collection of three Chinese superstar cars and a VW that stole this country’s heart. The Chinese Lucky Stars Car Pack brings everything from SUVs to hot hatches with the 2022 Lynk & Co 05+, 2023 MG Cyberster, 2012 Volkswagen Santana and the 2022 Wuling Hongguang Mini EV', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i2.jpg', '2024-01-30', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 291076, 1, 70.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265098.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265099.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265100.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265101.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1265097.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '13', null, null), (1480, 'Forza Horizon 5: European Automotive Car Pack', 'The European Automotive Car Pack showcases some of the best work of car manufacturers from Across the Atlantic. It includes the 1987 Mercedes-Benz AMG Hammer Wagon, 2021 Bentley Continental GT Convertible, 2020 Automobili Pininfarina Battista, and the 2019 Jaguar XE SV Project 8.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co90i1.jpg', '2024-02-27', '{10,13,14,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 293442, 1, 61.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1280265.jpg"]', '{118871,105011,25311,35994,47161,116667,116376,114285,120126,111130}', '{}', 'Playground Games', '13', null, null), (1484, 'Forza Horizon 3: Motorsports All-Stars Car Pack', 'Motorsport All-Stars Car Pack is a downloadable car pack made available for the PC and Xbox One releases of Forza Horizon 3.
It was made included with the Deluxe Edition and Ultimate Edition releases of Forza Horizon 3, and was released as a standalone pack on September 27, 2016.

It is not included as part of the Car Pass for Forza Horizon 3.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coa6li.jpg', '2016-09-26', '{10}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 140366, 1, 55.99, '[{"id":30792,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405526.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405527.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/405528.jpg"]', '{109292,44178,297462,278395,269096,185150,176565,135811,116391,80382}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMc4v6oFK7U}', 'Microsoft Studios', '13', null, '{2810}'), (1486, 'Forza Horizon 5: 1969 Chevrolet Camaro Jordan Luka 3', '', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co8pll.jpg', '2024-09-10', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 314391, 1, 73.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dKK2vJNi0cc}', null, '13', null, null), (1489, 'Forza Motorsport and Forza Horizon 5 Premium Editions Bundle', 'Get the Forza Motorsport Premium Edition and Forza Horizon 5 Premium Edition in one unmissable bundle. Includes Race Day Car Pack, Forza Horizon 5 Rally Adventure and Forza Horizon 5: Hot Wheels, as well as Car Pass, VIP Membership, and Welcome Pack for both games.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co7f56.jpg', '2023-11-16', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 277243, 1, 77.99, '[{"id":159986,"rating_category":{"id":28,"rating":"L"}},{"id":159987,"rating_category":{"id":8,"rating":"3"}},{"id":159988,"rating_category":{"id":34,"rating":"G"}},{"id":159984,"rating_category":{"id":23,"rating":"ALL"}},{"id":159983,"rating_category":{"id":3,"rating":"E"}},{"id":159982,"rating_category":{"id":14,"rating":"B"}},{"id":159985,"rating_category":{"id":19,"rating":"6"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/123171.jpg"]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '3', null, null), (1491, 'string', 'string', 'string', '2026-04-18', 'string', 'string', 80, 1231, 0, 0, 'string', 'string', 'string', 'string', 'string', 'strin