usic icons in history. In this time rewind, Snoop D-O-double-G heads up the Agency, the rap god Eminem sets up shop in the Grotto, hip hop princess Ice Spice lays claim to Shark Island, and the remix hits the finale with a celebration and tribute to the legend and icon, Juice WRLD. Push play, turn up the volume, and open up the vault in Fortnite Battle Royale Chapter 2 Remix!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co907g.jpg', '2024-11-02', '{5}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 321386, 1, 55.99, '[{"id":192212,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":192211,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":192213,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}}]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416747.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416748.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416749.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416750.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416751.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416752.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416753.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416754.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416755.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1416756.jpg"]', '{95340,68287,38030,119177,32902,106805,87622,43367,28751,103302}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zJK2qBcSYs}', 'Epic Games', '7', null, null), (1552, 'Fortnite Festival: Changes', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 366373, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1553, 'Fortnite Festival: Shelter', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 375401, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1554, 'Fortnite Festival: Givenchy', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 367580, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1555, 'Fortnite: Infinite Drift Pack', 'Combat is the name of the game for this team. P