 18, 2025, before shutting down on November 1, 2025, and having many of its core mechanics ported to LEGO Fortnite Odyssey', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cobcng.jpg', '2025-06-18', '{5,12,31}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 387000, 1, 93.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/240949.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1748198.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1748199.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1748200.jpg"]', '{19164,55038,105269,107318,47823,105049,76877,18225,106987,96217}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hMOPVQSHIic}', 'The LEGO Group', '14', null, null), (1563, 'Fortnite Festival: Season 3', 'You’ve seen her in a crown, now see her in Fortnite. Award-winning artist Billie Eilish is the Icon of Fortnite Festival Season 3!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co85au.jpg', '2024-04-23', '{7}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 299445, 1, 64.99, '[{"id":186385,"rating_category":{"id":10,"rating":"12"}},{"id":186384,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}},{"id":186388,"rating_category":{"id":24,"rating":"12+"}},{"id":186386,"rating_category":{"id":15,"rating":"C"}},{"id":186389,"rating_category":{"id":30,"rating":"12"}},{"id":186390,"rating_category":{"id":36,"rating":"M"}},{"id":186387,"rating_category":{"id":20,"rating":"12"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/136207.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/136208.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/136206.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1386609.jpg"]', '{63933,77720,18981,331127,331011,330988,266558,239849,233959,167281}', '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEHsE53KG_c,https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ztOjZdyuUQ}', 'Epic Games', '7', null, null), (1564, 'Fortnite: Transformers Pack', 'Roll out, Rise up, or Beep Beep with the Fortnite Transformers Pack! Physical copies of this Pack will roll out at retail starting Octob