Band members Noodle, 2D, Russel Hobbs, and Murdoc Niccals are the Icons of Fortnite Festival Season 10. Watch out for this dream line-up making their Festival debut on August 26!', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/coacow.jpg', '2025-08-26', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 363607, 1, 84.99, '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/190630.jpg"]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1622735.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1622736.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1622737.jpg"]', null, '{}', 'Epic Games', '7', null, null), (1581, 'Fortnite Festival: Funny Song', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 368449, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1582, 'Fortnite Festival: Lean Back', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 366196, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1583, 'Fortnite: Checkered Past Pack', 'Much like her trusty Thudthumper, Veronika is blunt and to the point. Includes an Outfit, a Back Bling, a Pickaxe, a Wrap and 600 V-Bucks.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/co96zm.jpg', '2022-11-09', null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 305610, 1, 58.99, '[]', '[]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1340337.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/1441870.jpg"]', null, '{}', 'Epic Games', '13', null, null), (1584, 'Fortnite Festival: Ruby Soho', '', null, null, null, 'IGDB', 75.5, 366650, 1, 79.99, '[]', '[]', '[]', null, '{}', null, '13', null, null), (1585, 'Fortnite Festival: Season 12', 'Singer, actress, global star, and now Festival Season 12 Icon, LISA comes to Fortnite with her music and Outfits! Use the mic to sing absolute bangers. The Music Pass includes Jam Tracks like LISA’s “FUTW (Vixi Solo Version)” and kinetic tracks from other artists.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob7cw.jpg', '2025-11-29', '{7}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 384111, 1, 83.99, '[{"id":227580,"rat