Adds the biggest, most varied collection of Jam Tracks so far. Perform your best show yet on the Main Stage, make new mixes on the Jam Stage and in Battle Royale, and choose your background music when you get a Victory Royale or drop out of the Battle Bus.', 'https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_cover_big/cob7cd.jpg', '2025-10-09', '{7}', 'IGDB', 75.5, 384110, 1, 92.99, '[{"id":227579,"rating_category":{"id":5,"rating":"T"}}]', '["https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235227.jpg","https://images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_1080p/235226.jpg"]', '[]', null, '{https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYuzPCirqb0}', 'Harmonix Music Systems', '7', null, null), (1589, 'Fortnite: Gilded Elites Pack', 'They''ve got one thing in common and it happens to be the one thing they all adore. Includes 3 Outfits (with LEGO Styles), 3 Back Blings and 3 Pickaxes.

